var book = {
	"name": "Jeremiah",
	"numChapters": 52,
	"chapters": {
		"1": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">1 </span>The words of Jeremiah son of Hilkiah, one of the priests at Anathoth<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18948A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18948A\"></sup> in the territory of Benjamin.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>The word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18949B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18949B\"></sup> to him in the thirteenth year of the reign of Josiah<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18949C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18949C\"></sup> son of Amon king of Judah,",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>and through the reign of Jehoiakim<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18950D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18950D\"></sup> son of Josiah king of Judah, down to the fifth month of the eleventh year of Zedekiah<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18950E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18950E\"></sup> son of Josiah king of Judah, when the people of Jerusalem went into exile.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18950F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18950F\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>The word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to me, saying,",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>“Before I formed you in the womb<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18952G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18952G\"></sup> I knew<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18952H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18952H\"></sup> you,before you were born<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18952I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18952I\"></sup> I set you apart;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18952J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18952J\"></sup>I appointed you as a prophet to the nations.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18952K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18952K\"></sup>”",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>“Alas, Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,” I said, “I do not know how to speak;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18953L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18953L\"></sup> I am too young.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18953M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18953M\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>But the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> said to me, “Do not say, ‘I am too young.’ You must go to everyone I send you to and say whatever I command you.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Do not be afraid<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18955N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18955N\"></sup> of them, for I am with you<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18955O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18955O\"></sup> and will rescue<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18955P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18955P\"></sup> you,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18955Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18955Q\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Then the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> reached out his hand and touched<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18956R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18956R\"></sup> my mouth and said to me, “I have put my words in your mouth.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18956S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18956S\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>See, today I appoint you over nations<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18957T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18957T\"></sup> and kingdoms to uproot<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18957U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18957U\"></sup> and tear down, to destroy and overthrow, to build and to plant.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18957V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18957V\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>The word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to me: “What do you see, Jeremiah?”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18958W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18958W\"></sup>“I see the branch of an almond tree,” I replied.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> said to me, “You have seen correctly, for I am watching<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18959X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18959X\"></sup> to see that my word is fulfilled.”",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>The word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to me again: “What do you see?”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18960Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18960Y\"></sup>“I see a pot that is boiling,” I answered. “It is tilting toward us from the north.”",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> said to me, “From the north<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18961Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18961Z\"></sup> disaster will be poured out on all who live in the land.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>I am about to summon all the peoples of the northern kingdoms,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.“Their kings will come and set up their thronesin the entrance of the gates of Jerusalem;they will come against all her surrounding wallsand against all the towns of Judah.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18962AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18962AA\"></sup>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>I will pronounce my judgments<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18963AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18963AB\"></sup> on my peoplebecause of their wickedness<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18963AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18963AC\"></sup> in forsaking me,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18963AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18963AD\"></sup>in burning incense to other gods<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18963AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18963AE\"></sup>and in worshiping<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18963AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18963AF\"></sup> what their hands have made.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18963AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18963AG\"></sup>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>“Get yourself ready! Stand up and say<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18964AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18964AH\"></sup> to them whatever I command you. Do not be terrified<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18964AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18964AI\"></sup> by them, or I will terrify you before them.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Today I have made you<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18965AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18965AJ\"></sup> a fortified city, an iron pillar and a bronze wall to stand against the whole land—against the kings of Judah, its officials, its priests and the people of the land.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>They will fight against you but will not overcome<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18966AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18966AK\"></sup> you, for I am with you<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18966AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18966AL\"></sup> and will rescue<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18966AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18966AM\"></sup> you,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>."
		},
		"2": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">2 </span>The word<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18967A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18967A\"></sup> of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to me:",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“Go and proclaim in the hearing of Jerusalem:“This is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says:“‘I remember the devotion of your youth,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18968B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18968B\"></sup>how as a bride you loved meand followed me through the wilderness,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18968C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18968C\"></sup>through a land not sown.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Israel was holy<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18969D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18969D\"></sup> to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18969E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18969E\"></sup>the firstfruits<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18969F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18969F\"></sup> of his harvest;all who devoured<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18969G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18969G\"></sup> her were held guilty,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18969H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18969H\"></sup>and disaster overtook them,’”declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Hear the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, you descendants of Jacob,all you clans of Israel.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>This is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says:“What fault did your ancestors find in me,that they strayed so far from me?They followed worthless idols<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18971I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18971I\"></sup>and became worthless<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18971J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18971J\"></sup> themselves.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>They did not ask, ‘Where is the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,who brought us up out of Egypt<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18972K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18972K\"></sup>and led us through the barren wilderness,through a land of deserts<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18972L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18972L\"></sup> and ravines,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18972M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18972M\"></sup>a land of drought and utter darkness,a land where no one travels<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18972N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18972N\"></sup> and no one lives?’",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>I brought you into a fertile landto eat its fruit and rich produce.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18973O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18973O\"></sup>But you came and defiled my landand made my inheritance detestable.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18973P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18973P\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>The priests did not ask,‘Where is the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>?’Those who deal with the law did not know me;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18974Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18974Q\"></sup>the leaders<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18974R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18974R\"></sup> rebelled against me.The prophets prophesied by Baal,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18974S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18974S\"></sup>following worthless idols.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18974T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18974T\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>“Therefore I bring charges<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18975U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18975U\"></sup> against you again,”declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.“And I will bring charges against your children’s children.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Cross over to the coasts of Cyprus<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18976V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18976V\"></sup> and look,send to Kedar<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18976W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18976W\"></sup> and observe closely;see if there has ever been anything like this:",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Has a nation ever changed its gods?(Yet they are not gods<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18977X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18977X\"></sup> at all.)But my people have exchanged their glorious<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18977Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18977Y\"></sup> Godfor worthless idols.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Be appalled at this, you heavens,and shudder with great horror,”declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>“My people have committed two sins:They have forsaken<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18979Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18979Z\"></sup> me,the spring of living water,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18979AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18979AA\"></sup>and have dug their own cisterns,broken cisterns that cannot hold water.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Is Israel a servant, a slave<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18980AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18980AB\"></sup> by birth?Why then has he become plunder?",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Lions<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18981AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18981AC\"></sup> have roared;they have growled at him.They have laid waste<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18981AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18981AD\"></sup> his land;his towns are burned<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18981AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18981AE\"></sup> and deserted.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18981AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18981AF\"></sup>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Also, the men of Memphis<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18982AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18982AG\"></sup> and Tahpanhes<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18982AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18982AH\"></sup>have cracked your skull.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Have you not brought this on yourselves<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18983AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18983AI\"></sup>by forsaking<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18983AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18983AJ\"></sup> the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your Godwhen he led you in the way?",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Now why go to Egypt<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18984AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18984AK\"></sup>to drink water from the Nile?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18984AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18984AL\"></sup>And why go to Assyria<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18984AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18984AM\"></sup>to drink water from the Euphrates?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18984AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18984AN\"></sup>",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>Your wickedness will punish you;your backsliding<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18985AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18985AO\"></sup> will rebuke<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18985AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18985AP\"></sup> you.Consider then and realizehow evil and bitter<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18985AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18985AQ\"></sup> it is for youwhen you forsake<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18985AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18985AR\"></sup> the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your Godand have no awe<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18985AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18985AS\"></sup> of me,”declares the Lord, the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>“Long ago you broke off your yoke<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18986AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18986AT\"></sup>and tore off your bonds;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18986AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18986AU\"></sup>you said, ‘I will not serve you!’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18986AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18986AV\"></sup>Indeed, on every high hill<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18986AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18986AW\"></sup>and under every spreading tree<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18986AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18986AX\"></sup>you lay down as a prostitute.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18986AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18986AY\"></sup>",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>I had planted<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18987AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18987AZ\"></sup> you like a choice vine<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18987BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18987BA\"></sup>of sound and reliable stock.How then did you turn against meinto a corrupt,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18987BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18987BB\"></sup> wild vine?",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Although you wash<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18988BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18988BC\"></sup> yourself with soap<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18988BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18988BD\"></sup>and use an abundance of cleansing powder,the stain of your guilt is still before me,”declares the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18988BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18988BE\"></sup>",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>“How can you say, ‘I am not defiled;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18989BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18989BF\"></sup>I have not run after the Baals’?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18989BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18989BG\"></sup>See how you behaved in the valley;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18989BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18989BH\"></sup>consider what you have done.You are a swift she-camelrunning<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18989BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18989BI\"></sup> here and there,",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>a wild donkey<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18990BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18990BJ\"></sup> accustomed to the desert,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18990BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18990BK\"></sup>sniffing the wind in her craving—in her heat who can restrain her?Any males that pursue her need not tire themselves;at mating time they will find her.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>Do not run until your feet are bareand your throat is dry.But you said, ‘It’s no use!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18991BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18991BL\"></sup>I love foreign gods,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18991BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18991BM\"></sup>and I must go after them.’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18991BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18991BN\"></sup>",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>“As a thief is disgraced<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18992BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18992BO\"></sup> when he is caught,so the people of Israel are disgraced—they, their kings and their officials,their priests<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18992BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18992BP\"></sup> and their prophets.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18992BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18992BQ\"></sup>",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>They say to wood,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18993BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18993BR\"></sup> ‘You are my father,’and to stone,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18993BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18993BS\"></sup> ‘You gave me birth.’They have turned their backs<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18993BT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BT&quot;&gt;BT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18993BT\"></sup> to meand not their faces;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18993BU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BU&quot;&gt;BU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18993BU\"></sup>yet when they are in trouble,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18993BV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BV&quot;&gt;BV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18993BV\"></sup> they say,‘Come and save<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18993BW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BW&quot;&gt;BW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18993BW\"></sup> us!’",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>Where then are the gods<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18994BX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BX&quot;&gt;BX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18994BX\"></sup> you made for yourselves?Let them come if they can save youwhen you are in trouble!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18994BY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BY&quot;&gt;BY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18994BY\"></sup>For you, Judah, have as many godsas you have towns.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18994BZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BZ&quot;&gt;BZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18994BZ\"></sup>",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>“Why do you bring charges against me?You have all<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18995CA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CA&quot;&gt;CA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18995CA\"></sup> rebelled against me,”declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>“In vain I punished your people;they did not respond to correction.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18996CB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CB&quot;&gt;CB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18996CB\"></sup>Your sword has devoured your prophets<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18996CC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CC&quot;&gt;CC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18996CC\"></sup>like a ravenous lion.",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>“You of this generation, consider the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>:“Have I been a desert to Israelor a land of great darkness?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18997CD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CD&quot;&gt;CD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18997CD\"></sup>Why do my people say, ‘We are free to roam;we will come to you no more’?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18997CE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CE&quot;&gt;CE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18997CE\"></sup>",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>Does a young woman forget her jewelry,a bride her wedding ornaments?Yet my people have forgotten<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18998CF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CF&quot;&gt;CF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18998CF\"></sup> me,days without number.",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>How skilled you are at pursuing<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-18999CG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CG&quot;&gt;CG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-18999CG\"></sup> love!Even the worst of women can learn from your ways.",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>On your clothes is foundthe lifeblood<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19000CH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CH&quot;&gt;CH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19000CH\"></sup> of the innocent poor,though you did not catch them breaking in.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19000CI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CI&quot;&gt;CI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19000CI\"></sup>Yet in spite of all this",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup><span class=\"indent-1-breaks\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>you say, ‘I am innocent;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19001CJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CJ&quot;&gt;CJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19001CJ\"></sup>he is not angry with me.’But I will pass judgment<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19001CK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CK&quot;&gt;CK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19001CK\"></sup> on youbecause you say, ‘I have not sinned.’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19001CL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CL&quot;&gt;CL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19001CL\"></sup>",
			"36": "<sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup>Why do you go about so much,changing<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19002CM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CM&quot;&gt;CM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19002CM\"></sup> your ways?You will be disappointed by Egypt<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19002CN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CN&quot;&gt;CN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19002CN\"></sup>as you were by Assyria.",
			"37": "<sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup>You will also leave that placewith your hands on your head,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19003CO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CO&quot;&gt;CO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19003CO\"></sup>for the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has rejected those you trust;you will not be helped<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19003CP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CP&quot;&gt;CP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19003CP\"></sup> by them."
		},
		"3": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">3 </span>“If a man divorces<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19004A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19004A\"></sup> his wifeand she leaves him and marries another man,should he return to her again?Would not the land be completely defiled?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19004B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19004B\"></sup>But you have lived as a prostitute with many lovers<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19004C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19004C\"></sup>—would you now return to me?”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19004D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19004D\"></sup>declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“Look up to the barren heights<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19005E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19005E\"></sup> and see.Is there any place where you have not been ravished?By the roadside<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19005F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19005F\"></sup> you sat waiting for lovers,sat like a nomad in the desert.You have defiled the land<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19005G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19005G\"></sup>with your prostitution<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19005H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19005H\"></sup> and wickedness.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Therefore the showers have been withheld,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19006I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19006I\"></sup>and no spring rains<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19006J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19006J\"></sup> have fallen.Yet you have the brazen<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19006K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19006K\"></sup> look of a prostitute;you refuse to blush with shame.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19006L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19006L\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Have you not just called to me:‘My Father,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19007M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19007M\"></sup> my friend from my youth,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19007N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19007N\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>will you always be angry?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19008O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19008O\"></sup>Will your wrath continue forever?’This is how you talk,but you do all the evil you can.”",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>During the reign of King Josiah,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19009P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19009P\"></sup> the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> said to me, “Have you seen what faithless<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19009Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19009Q\"></sup> Israel has done? She has gone up on every high hill and under every spreading tree<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19009R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19009R\"></sup> and has committed adultery<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19009S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19009S\"></sup> there.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>I thought that after she had done all this she would return to me but she did not, and her unfaithful sister<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19010T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19010T\"></sup> Judah saw it.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19010U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19010U\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>I gave faithless Israel<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19011V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19011V\"></sup> her certificate of divorce<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19011W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19011W\"></sup> and sent her away because of all her adulteries. Yet I saw that her unfaithful sister Judah had no fear;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19011X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19011X\"></sup> she also went out and committed adultery.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Because Israel’s immorality mattered so little to her, she defiled the land<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19012Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19012Y\"></sup> and committed adultery<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19012Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19012Z\"></sup> with stone<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19012AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19012AA\"></sup> and wood.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19012AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19012AB\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>In spite of all this, her unfaithful sister Judah did not return<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19013AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19013AC\"></sup> to me with all her heart, but only in pretense,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19013AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19013AD\"></sup>” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19013AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19013AE\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> said to me, “Faithless Israel is more righteous<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19014AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19014AF\"></sup> than unfaithful<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19014AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19014AG\"></sup> Judah.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19014AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19014AH\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Go, proclaim this message toward the north:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19015AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19015AI\"></sup>“‘Return,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19015AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19015AJ\"></sup> faithless<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19015AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19015AK\"></sup> Israel,’ declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,‘I will frown on you no longer,for I am faithful,’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19015AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19015AL\"></sup> declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,‘I will not be angry<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19015AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19015AM\"></sup> forever.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Only acknowledge<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19016AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19016AN\"></sup> your guilt—you have rebelled against the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God,you have scattered your favors to foreign gods<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19016AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19016AO\"></sup>under every spreading tree,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19016AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19016AP\"></sup>and have not obeyed<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19016AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19016AQ\"></sup> me,’”declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>“Return,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19017AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19017AR\"></sup> faithless people,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, “for I am your husband.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19017AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19017AS\"></sup> I will choose you—one from a town and two from a clan—and bring you to Zion.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Then I will give you shepherds<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19018AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19018AT\"></sup> after my own heart,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19018AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19018AU\"></sup> who will lead you with knowledge and understanding.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>In those days, when your numbers have increased greatly in the land,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, “people will no longer say, ‘The ark<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19019AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19019AV\"></sup> of the covenant of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.’ It will never enter their minds or be remembered;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19019AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19019AW\"></sup> it will not be missed, nor will another one be made.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>At that time they will call Jerusalem The Throne<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19020AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19020AX\"></sup> of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, and all nations<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19020AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19020AY\"></sup> will gather in Jerusalem to honor<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19020AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19020AZ\"></sup> the name of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>. No longer will they follow the stubbornness of their evil hearts.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19020BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19020BA\"></sup>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>In those days the people of Judah will join the people of Israel,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19021BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19021BB\"></sup> and together<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19021BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19021BC\"></sup> they will come from a northern<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19021BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19021BD\"></sup> land to the land<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19021BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19021BE\"></sup> I gave your ancestors as an inheritance.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>“I myself said,“‘How gladly would I treat you like my childrenand give you a pleasant land,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19022BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19022BF\"></sup>the most beautiful inheritance<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19022BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19022BG\"></sup> of any nation.’I thought you would call me ‘Father’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19022BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19022BH\"></sup>and not turn away from following me.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>But like a woman unfaithful to her husband,so you, Israel, have been unfaithful<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19023BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19023BI\"></sup> to me,”declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>A cry is heard on the barren heights,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19024BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19024BJ\"></sup>the weeping<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19024BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19024BK\"></sup> and pleading of the people of Israel,because they have perverted their waysand have forgotten<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19024BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19024BL\"></sup> the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> their God.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>“Return,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19025BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19025BM\"></sup> faithless people;I will cure<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19025BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19025BN\"></sup> you of backsliding.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19025BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19025BO\"></sup>“Yes, we will come to you,for you are the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> our God.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>Surely the idolatrous commotion on the hills<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19026BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19026BP\"></sup>and mountains is a deception;surely in the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> our Godis the salvation<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19026BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19026BQ\"></sup> of Israel.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>From our youth shameful<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19027BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19027BR\"></sup> gods have consumedthe fruits of our ancestors’ labor—their flocks and herds,their sons and daughters.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>Let us lie down in our shame,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19028BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19028BS\"></sup>and let our disgrace cover us.We have sinned<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19028BT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BT&quot;&gt;BT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19028BT\"></sup> against the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> our God,both we and our ancestors;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19028BU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BU&quot;&gt;BU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19028BU\"></sup>from our youth<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19028BV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BV&quot;&gt;BV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19028BV\"></sup> till this daywe have not obeyed<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19028BW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BW&quot;&gt;BW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19028BW\"></sup> the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> our God.”"
		},
		"4": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">4 </span>“If you, Israel, will return,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19029A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19029A\"></sup>then return to me,”declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.“If you put your detestable idols<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19029B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19029B\"></sup> out of my sightand no longer go astray,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>and if in a truthful, just and righteous wayyou swear,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19030C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19030C\"></sup> ‘As surely as the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> lives,’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19030D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19030D\"></sup>then the nations will invoke blessings<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19030E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19030E\"></sup> by himand in him they will boast.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19030F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19030F\"></sup>”",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>This is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says to the people of Judah and to Jerusalem:“Break up your unplowed ground<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19031G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19031G\"></sup>and do not sow among thorns.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19031H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19031H\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Circumcise yourselves to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,circumcise your hearts,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19032I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19032I\"></sup>you people of Judah and inhabitants of Jerusalem,or my wrath<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19032J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19032J\"></sup> will flare up and burn like fire<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19032K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19032K\"></sup>because of the evil<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19032L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19032L\"></sup> you have done—burn with no one to quench<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19032M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19032M\"></sup> it.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>“Announce in Judah and proclaim<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19033N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19033N\"></sup> in Jerusalem and say:‘Sound the trumpet<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19033O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19033O\"></sup> throughout the land!’Cry aloud and say:‘Gather together!Let us flee to the fortified cities!’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19033P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19033P\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Raise the signal<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19034Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19034Q\"></sup> to go to Zion!Flee for safety without delay!For I am bringing disaster<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19034R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19034R\"></sup> from the north,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19034S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19034S\"></sup>even terrible destruction.”",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>A lion<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19035T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19035T\"></sup> has come out of his lair;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19035U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19035U\"></sup>a destroyer<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19035V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19035V\"></sup> of nations has set out.He has left his placeto lay waste<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19035W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19035W\"></sup> your land.Your towns will lie in ruins<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19035X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19035X\"></sup>without inhabitant.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>So put on sackcloth,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19036Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19036Y\"></sup>lament<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19036Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19036Z\"></sup> and wail,for the fierce anger<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19036AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19036AA\"></sup> of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>has not turned away from us.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>“In that day,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,“the king and the officials will lose heart,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19037AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19037AB\"></sup>the priests will be horrified,and the prophets will be appalled.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19037AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19037AC\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Then I said, “Alas, Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>! How completely you have deceived<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19038AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19038AD\"></sup> this people and Jerusalem by saying, ‘You will have peace,’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19038AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19038AE\"></sup> when the sword is at our throats!”",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>At that time this people and Jerusalem will be told, “A scorching wind<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19039AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19039AF\"></sup> from the barren heights in the desert blows toward my people, but not to winnow or cleanse;",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>a wind<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19040AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19040AG\"></sup> too strong for that comes from me. Now I pronounce my judgments<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19040AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19040AH\"></sup> against them.”",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Look! He advances like the clouds,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19041AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19041AI\"></sup>his chariots<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19041AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19041AJ\"></sup> come like a whirlwind,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19041AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19041AK\"></sup>his horses<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19041AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19041AL\"></sup> are swifter than eagles.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19041AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19041AM\"></sup>Woe to us! We are ruined!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19041AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19041AN\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Jerusalem, wash<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19042AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19042AO\"></sup> the evil from your heart and be saved.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19042AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19042AP\"></sup>How long<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19042AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19042AQ\"></sup> will you harbor wicked thoughts?",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>A voice is announcing from Dan,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19043AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19043AR\"></sup>proclaiming disaster from the hills of Ephraim.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19043AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19043AS\"></sup>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>“Tell this to the nations,proclaim concerning Jerusalem:‘A besieging army is coming from a distant land,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19044AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19044AT\"></sup>raising a war cry<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19044AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19044AU\"></sup> against the cities of Judah.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19044AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19044AV\"></sup>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>They surround<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19045AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19045AW\"></sup> her like men guarding a field,because she has rebelled<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19045AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19045AX\"></sup> against me,’”declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>“Your own conduct and actions<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19046AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19046AY\"></sup>have brought this on you.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19046AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19046AZ\"></sup>This is your punishment.How bitter<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19046BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19046BA\"></sup> it is!How it pierces to the heart!”",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>Oh, my anguish, my anguish!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19047BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19047BB\"></sup>I writhe in pain.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19047BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19047BC\"></sup>Oh, the agony of my heart!My heart pounds<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19047BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19047BD\"></sup> within me,I cannot keep silent.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19047BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19047BE\"></sup>For I have heard the sound of the trumpet;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19047BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19047BF\"></sup>I have heard the battle cry.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19047BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19047BG\"></sup>",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Disaster follows disaster;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19048BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19048BH\"></sup>the whole land lies in ruins.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19048BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19048BI\"></sup>In an instant my tents<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19048BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19048BJ\"></sup> are destroyed,my shelter in a moment.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>How long must I see the battle standard<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19049BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19049BK\"></sup>and hear the sound of the trumpet?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19049BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19049BL\"></sup>",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>“My people are fools;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19050BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19050BM\"></sup>they do not know me.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19050BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19050BN\"></sup>They are senseless children;they have no understanding.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19050BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19050BO\"></sup>They are skilled in doing evil;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19050BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19050BP\"></sup>they know not how to do good.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19050BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19050BQ\"></sup>",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>I looked at the earth,and it was formless and empty;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19051BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19051BR\"></sup>and at the heavens,and their light<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19051BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19051BS\"></sup> was gone.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>I looked at the mountains,and they were quaking;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19052BT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BT&quot;&gt;BT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19052BT\"></sup>all the hills were swaying.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>I looked, and there were no people;every bird in the sky had flown away.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19053BU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BU&quot;&gt;BU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19053BU\"></sup>",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>I looked, and the fruitful land was a desert;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19054BV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BV&quot;&gt;BV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19054BV\"></sup>all its towns lay in ruins<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19054BW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BW&quot;&gt;BW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19054BW\"></sup>before the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, before his fierce anger.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19054BX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BX&quot;&gt;BX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19054BX\"></sup>",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>This is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says:“The whole land will be ruined,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19055BY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BY&quot;&gt;BY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19055BY\"></sup>though I will not destroy<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19055BZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BZ&quot;&gt;BZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19055BZ\"></sup> it completely.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>Therefore the earth will mourn<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19056CA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CA&quot;&gt;CA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19056CA\"></sup>and the heavens above grow dark,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19056CB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CB&quot;&gt;CB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19056CB\"></sup>because I have spoken and will not relent,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19056CC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CC&quot;&gt;CC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19056CC\"></sup>I have decided and will not turn back.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19056CD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CD&quot;&gt;CD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19056CD\"></sup>”",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>At the sound of horsemen and archers<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19057CE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CE&quot;&gt;CE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19057CE\"></sup>every town takes to flight.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19057CF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CF&quot;&gt;CF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19057CF\"></sup>Some go into the thickets;some climb up among the rocks.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19057CG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CG&quot;&gt;CG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19057CG\"></sup>All the towns are deserted;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19057CH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CH&quot;&gt;CH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19057CH\"></sup>no one lives in them.",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>What are you doing,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19058CI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CI&quot;&gt;CI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19058CI\"></sup> you devastated one?Why dress yourself in scarletand put on jewels<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19058CJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CJ&quot;&gt;CJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19058CJ\"></sup> of gold?Why highlight your eyes with makeup?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19058CK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CK&quot;&gt;CK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19058CK\"></sup>You adorn yourself in vain.Your lovers<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19058CL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CL&quot;&gt;CL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19058CL\"></sup> despise you;they want to kill you.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19058CM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CM&quot;&gt;CM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19058CM\"></sup>",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>I hear a cry as of a woman in labor,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19059CN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CN&quot;&gt;CN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19059CN\"></sup>a groan as of one bearing her first child—the cry of Daughter Zion<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19059CO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CO&quot;&gt;CO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19059CO\"></sup> gasping for breath,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19059CP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CP&quot;&gt;CP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19059CP\"></sup>stretching out her hands<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19059CQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CQ&quot;&gt;CQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19059CQ\"></sup> and saying,“Alas! I am fainting;my life is given over to murderers.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19059CR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CR&quot;&gt;CR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19059CR\"></sup>"
		},
		"5": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">5 </span>“Go up and down<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19060A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19060A\"></sup> the streets of Jerusalem,look around and consider,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19060B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19060B\"></sup>search through her squares.If you can find but one person<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19060C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19060C\"></sup>who deals honestly<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19060D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19060D\"></sup> and seeks the truth,I will forgive<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19060E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19060E\"></sup> this city.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Although they say, ‘As surely as the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> lives,’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19061F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19061F\"></sup>still they are swearing falsely.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19061G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19061G\"></sup>”",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, do not your eyes<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19062H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19062H\"></sup> look for truth?You struck<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19062I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19062I\"></sup> them, but they felt no pain;you crushed them, but they refused correction.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19062J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19062J\"></sup>They made their faces harder than stone<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19062K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19062K\"></sup>and refused to repent.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19062L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19062L\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>I thought, “These are only the poor;they are foolish,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19063M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19063M\"></sup>for they do not know<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19063N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19063N\"></sup> the way of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,the requirements of their God.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>So I will go to the leaders<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19064O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19064O\"></sup>and speak to them;surely they know the way of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,the requirements of their God.”But with one accord they too had broken off the yokeand torn off the bonds.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19064P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19064P\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Therefore a lion from the forest<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19065Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19065Q\"></sup> will attack them,a wolf from the desert will ravage<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19065R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19065R\"></sup> them,a leopard<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19065S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19065S\"></sup> will lie in wait near their townsto tear to pieces any who venture out,for their rebellion is greatand their backslidings many.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19065T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19065T\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>“Why should I forgive you?Your children have forsaken meand sworn<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19066U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19066U\"></sup> by gods that are not gods.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19066V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19066V\"></sup>I supplied all their needs,yet they committed adultery<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19066W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19066W\"></sup>and thronged to the houses of prostitutes.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19066X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19066X\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>They are well-fed, lusty stallions,each neighing for another man’s wife.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19067Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19067Y\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Should I not punish them for this?”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19068Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19068Z\"></sup>declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.“Should I not avenge<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19068AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19068AA\"></sup> myselfon such a nation as this?",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>“Go through her vineyards and ravage them,but do not destroy them completely.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19069AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19069AB\"></sup>Strip off her branches,for these people do not belong to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>The people of Israel and the people of Judahhave been utterly unfaithful<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19070AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19070AC\"></sup> to me,”declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>They have lied<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19071AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19071AD\"></sup> about the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>;they said, “He will do nothing!No harm will come to us;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19071AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19071AE\"></sup>we will never see sword or famine.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19071AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19071AF\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>The prophets<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19072AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19072AG\"></sup> are but wind<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19072AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19072AH\"></sup>and the word is not in them;so let what they say be done to them.”",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Therefore this is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> God Almighty says:“Because the people have spoken these words,I will make my words in your mouth<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19073AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19073AI\"></sup> a fire<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19073AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19073AJ\"></sup>and these people the wood it consumes.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19073AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19073AK\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>People of Israel,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,“I am bringing a distant nation<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19074AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19074AL\"></sup> against you—an ancient and enduring nation,a people whose language<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19074AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19074AM\"></sup> you do not know,whose speech you do not understand.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Their quivers<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19075AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19075AN\"></sup> are like an open grave;all of them are mighty warriors.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>They will devour<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19076AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19076AO\"></sup> your harvests and food,devour<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19076AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19076AP\"></sup> your sons and daughters;they will devour<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19076AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19076AQ\"></sup> your flocks and herds,devour your vines and fig trees.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19076AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19076AR\"></sup>With the sword<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19076AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19076AS\"></sup> they will destroythe fortified cities<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19076AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19076AT\"></sup> in which you trust.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19076AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19076AU\"></sup>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>“Yet even in those days,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, “I will not destroy<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19077AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19077AV\"></sup> you completely.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>And when the people ask,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19078AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19078AW\"></sup> ‘Why has the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> our God done all this to us?’ you will tell them, ‘As you have forsaken me and served foreign gods<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19078AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19078AX\"></sup> in your own land, so now you will serve foreigners<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19078AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19078AY\"></sup> in a land not your own.’",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>“Announce this to the descendants of Jacoband proclaim<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19079AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19079AZ\"></sup> it in Judah:",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>Hear this, you foolish and senseless people,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19080BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19080BA\"></sup>who have eyes<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19080BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19080BB\"></sup> but do not see,who have ears but do not hear:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19080BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19080BC\"></sup>",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Should you not fear<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19081BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19081BD\"></sup> me?” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.“Should you not tremble<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19081BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19081BE\"></sup> in my presence?I made the sand a boundary for the sea,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19081BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19081BF\"></sup>an everlasting barrier it cannot cross.The waves may roll, but they cannot prevail;they may roar,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19081BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19081BG\"></sup> but they cannot cross it.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>But these people have stubborn and rebellious<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19082BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19082BH\"></sup> hearts;they have turned aside<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19082BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19082BI\"></sup> and gone away.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>They do not say to themselves,‘Let us fear<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19083BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19083BJ\"></sup> the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> our God,who gives autumn and spring rains<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19083BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19083BK\"></sup> in season,who assures us of the regular weeks of harvest.’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19083BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19083BL\"></sup>",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>Your wrongdoings have kept these away;your sins have deprived you of good.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19084BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19084BM\"></sup>",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>“Among my people are the wicked<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19085BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19085BN\"></sup>who lie in wait<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19085BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19085BO\"></sup> like men who snare birdsand like those who set traps<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19085BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19085BP\"></sup> to catch people.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>Like cages full of birds,their houses are full of deceit;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19086BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19086BQ\"></sup>they have become rich<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19086BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19086BR\"></sup> and powerful",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup><span class=\"indent-1-breaks\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>and have grown fat<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19087BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19087BS\"></sup> and sleek.Their evil deeds have no limit;they do not seek justice.They do not promote the case of the fatherless;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19087BT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BT&quot;&gt;BT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19087BT\"></sup>they do not defend the just cause of the poor.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19087BU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BU&quot;&gt;BU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19087BU\"></sup>",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>Should I not punish them for this?”declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.“Should I not avenge<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19088BV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BV&quot;&gt;BV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19088BV\"></sup> myselfon such a nation as this?",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>“A horrible<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19089BW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BW&quot;&gt;BW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19089BW\"></sup> and shocking thinghas happened in the land:",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>The prophets prophesy lies,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19090BX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BX&quot;&gt;BX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19090BX\"></sup>the priests<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19090BY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BY&quot;&gt;BY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19090BY\"></sup> rule by their own authority,and my people love it this way.But what will you do in the end?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19090BZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BZ&quot;&gt;BZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19090BZ\"></sup>"
		},
		"6": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">6 </span>“Flee for safety, people of Benjamin!Flee from Jerusalem!Sound the trumpet<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19091A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19091A\"></sup> in Tekoa!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19091B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19091B\"></sup>Raise the signal over Beth Hakkerem!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19091C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19091C\"></sup>For disaster looms out of the north,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19091D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19091D\"></sup>even terrible destruction.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>I will destroy Daughter Zion,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19092E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19092E\"></sup>so beautiful and delicate.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19092F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19092F\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Shepherds<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19093G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19093G\"></sup> with their flocks will come against her;they will pitch their tents around<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19093H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19093H\"></sup> her,each tending his own portion.”",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>“Prepare for battle against her!Arise, let us attack at noon!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19094I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19094I\"></sup>But, alas, the daylight is fading,and the shadows of evening grow long.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>So arise, let us attack at nightand destroy her fortresses!”",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>This is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty says:“Cut down the trees<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19096J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19096J\"></sup>and build siege ramps<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19096K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19096K\"></sup> against Jerusalem.This city must be punished;it is filled with oppression.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19096L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19096L\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>As a well pours out its water,so she pours out her wickedness.Violence<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19097M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19097M\"></sup> and destruction<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19097N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19097N\"></sup> resound in her;her sickness and wounds are ever before me.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Take warning, Jerusalem,or I will turn away<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19098O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19098O\"></sup> from youand make your land desolateso no one can live in it.”",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>This is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty says:“Let them glean the remnant<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19099P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19099P\"></sup> of Israelas thoroughly as a vine;pass your hand over the branches again,like one gathering grapes.”",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>To whom can I speak and give warning?Who will listen<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19100Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19100Q\"></sup> to me?Their ears are closed<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19100R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19100R\"></sup>so they cannot hear.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19100S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19100S\"></sup>The word<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19100T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19100T\"></sup> of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> is offensive to them;they find no pleasure in it.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>But I am full of the wrath<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19101U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19101U\"></sup> of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,and I cannot hold it in.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19101V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19101V\"></sup>“Pour it out on the children in the streetand on the young men<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19101W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19101W\"></sup> gathered together;both husband and wife will be caught in it,and the old, those weighed down with years.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19101X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19101X\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Their houses will be turned over to others,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19102Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19102Y\"></sup>together with their fields and their wives,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19102Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19102Z\"></sup>when I stretch out my hand<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19102AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19102AA\"></sup>against those who live in the land,”declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>“From the least to the greatest,all<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19103AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19103AB\"></sup> are greedy for gain;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19103AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19103AC\"></sup>prophets and priests alike,all practice deceit.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19103AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19103AD\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>They dress the wound of my peopleas though it were not serious.‘Peace, peace,’ they say,when there is no peace.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19104AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19104AE\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Are they ashamed of their detestable conduct?No, they have no shame at all;they do not even know how to blush.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19105AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19105AF\"></sup>So they will fall among the fallen;they will be brought down when I punish<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19105AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19105AG\"></sup> them,”says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>This is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says:“Stand at the crossroads and look;ask for the ancient paths,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19106AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19106AH\"></sup>ask where the good way<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19106AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19106AI\"></sup> is, and walk in it,and you will find rest<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19106AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19106AJ\"></sup> for your souls.But you said, ‘We will not walk in it.’",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>I appointed watchmen<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19107AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19107AK\"></sup> over you and said,‘Listen to the sound of the trumpet!’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19107AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19107AL\"></sup>But you said, ‘We will not listen.’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19107AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19107AM\"></sup>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Therefore hear, you nations;you who are witnesses,observe what will happen to them.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>Hear, you earth:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19109AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19109AN\"></sup>I am bringing disaster<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19109AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19109AO\"></sup> on this people,the fruit of their schemes,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19109AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19109AP\"></sup>because they have not listened to my words<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19109AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19109AQ\"></sup>and have rejected my law.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19109AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19109AR\"></sup>",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>What do I care about incense from Sheba<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19110AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19110AS\"></sup>or sweet calamus<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19110AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19110AT\"></sup> from a distant land?Your burnt offerings are not acceptable;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19110AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19110AU\"></sup>your sacrifices<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19110AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19110AV\"></sup> do not please me.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19110AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19110AW\"></sup>",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>Therefore this is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says:“I will put obstacles before this people.Parents and children alike will stumble<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19111AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19111AX\"></sup> over them;neighbors and friends will perish.”",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>This is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says:“Look, an army is comingfrom the land of the north;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19112AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19112AY\"></sup>a great nation is being stirred upfrom the ends of the earth.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19112AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19112AZ\"></sup>",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>They are armed with bow and spear;they are cruel and show no mercy.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19113BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19113BA\"></sup>They sound like the roaring sea<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19113BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19113BB\"></sup>as they ride on their horses;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19113BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19113BC\"></sup>they come like men in battle formationto attack you, Daughter Zion.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19113BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19113BD\"></sup>”",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>We have heard reports about them,and our hands hang limp.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19114BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19114BE\"></sup>Anguish<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19114BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19114BF\"></sup> has gripped us,pain like that of a woman in labor.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19114BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19114BG\"></sup>",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>Do not go out to the fieldsor walk on the roads,for the enemy has a sword,and there is terror on every side.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19115BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19115BH\"></sup>",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>Put on sackcloth,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19116BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19116BI\"></sup> my people,and roll in ashes;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19116BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19116BJ\"></sup>mourn with bitter wailing<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19116BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19116BK\"></sup>as for an only son,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19116BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19116BL\"></sup>for suddenly the destroyer<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19116BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19116BM\"></sup>will come upon us.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>“I have made you a tester<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19117BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19117BN\"></sup> of metalsand my people the ore,that you may observeand test their ways.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>They are all hardened rebels,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19118BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19118BO\"></sup>going about to slander.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19118BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19118BP\"></sup>They are bronze and iron;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19118BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19118BQ\"></sup>they all act corruptly.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>The bellows blow fiercelyto burn away the lead with fire,but the refining<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19119BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19119BR\"></sup> goes on in vain;the wicked are not purged out.",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>They are called rejected silver,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19120BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19120BS\"></sup>because the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has rejected them.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19120BT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BT&quot;&gt;BT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19120BT\"></sup>"
		},
		"7": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">7 </span>This is the word that came to Jeremiah from the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>:",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“Stand<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19122A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19122A\"></sup> at the gate of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>’s house and there proclaim this message:“‘Hear the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, all you people of Judah who come through these gates to worship the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>This is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty, the God of Israel, says: Reform your ways<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19123B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19123B\"></sup> and your actions, and I will let you live<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19123C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19123C\"></sup> in this place.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Do not trust<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19124D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19124D\"></sup> in deceptive<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19124E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19124E\"></sup> words and say, “This is the temple of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, the temple of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, the temple of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>!”",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>If you really change<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19125F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19125F\"></sup> your ways and your actions and deal with each other justly,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19125G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19125G\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>if you do not oppress<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19126H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19126H\"></sup> the foreigner, the fatherless or the widow and do not shed innocent blood<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19126I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19126I\"></sup> in this place, and if you do not follow other gods<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19126J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19126J\"></sup> to your own harm,",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>then I will let you live in this place, in the land<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19127K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19127K\"></sup> I gave your ancestors<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19127L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19127L\"></sup> for ever and ever.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>But look, you are trusting<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19128M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19128M\"></sup> in deceptive<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19128N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19128N\"></sup> words that are worthless.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>“‘Will you steal<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19129O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19129O\"></sup> and murder,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19129P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19129P\"></sup> commit adultery<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19129Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19129Q\"></sup> and perjury,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19129R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19129R\"></sup> burn incense to Baal<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19129S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19129S\"></sup> and follow other gods<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19129T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19129T\"></sup> you have not known,",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>and then come and stand<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19130U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19130U\"></sup> before me in this house,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19130V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19130V\"></sup> which bears my Name, and say, “We are safe”—safe to do all these detestable things?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19130W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19130W\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Has this house,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19131X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19131X\"></sup> which bears my Name, become a den of robbers<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19131Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19131Y\"></sup> to you? But I have been watching!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19131Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19131Z\"></sup> declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>“‘Go now to the place in Shiloh<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19132AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19132AA\"></sup> where I first made a dwelling<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19132AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19132AB\"></sup> for my Name,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19132AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19132AC\"></sup> and see what I did<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19132AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19132AD\"></sup> to it because of the wickedness of my people Israel.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>While you were doing all these things, declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, I spoke<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19133AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19133AE\"></sup> to you again and again,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19133AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19133AF\"></sup> but you did not listen;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19133AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19133AG\"></sup> I called<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19133AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19133AH\"></sup> you, but you did not answer.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19133AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19133AI\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Therefore, what I did to Shiloh<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19134AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19134AJ\"></sup> I will now do to the house that bears my Name,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19134AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19134AK\"></sup> the temple<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19134AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19134AL\"></sup> you trust in, the place I gave to you and your ancestors.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>I will thrust you from my presence,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19135AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19135AM\"></sup> just as I did all your fellow Israelites, the people of Ephraim.’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19135AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19135AN\"></sup>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>“So do not pray for this people nor offer any plea<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19136AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19136AO\"></sup> or petition for them; do not plead with me, for I will not listen<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19136AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19136AP\"></sup> to you.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Do you not see what they are doing in the towns of Judah and in the streets of Jerusalem?",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>The children gather wood, the fathers light the fire, and the women knead the dough and make cakes to offer to the Queen of Heaven.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19138AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19138AQ\"></sup> They pour out drink offerings<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19138AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19138AR\"></sup> to other gods to arouse<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19138AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19138AS\"></sup> my anger.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>But am I the one they are provoking?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19139AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19139AT\"></sup> declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>. Are they not rather harming themselves, to their own shame?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19139AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19139AU\"></sup>",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>“‘Therefore this is what the Sovereign<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19140AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19140AV\"></sup> <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says: My anger<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19140AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19140AW\"></sup> and my wrath will be poured<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19140AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19140AX\"></sup> out on this place—on man and beast, on the trees of the field and on the crops of your land—and it will burn and not be quenched.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19140AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19140AY\"></sup>",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>“‘This is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty, the God of Israel, says: Go ahead, add your burnt offerings to your other sacrifices<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19141AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19141AZ\"></sup> and eat<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19141BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19141BA\"></sup> the meat yourselves!",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>For when I brought your ancestors out of Egypt and spoke to them, I did not just give them commands<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19142BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19142BB\"></sup> about burnt offerings and sacrifices,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19142BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19142BC\"></sup>",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>but I gave them this command:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19143BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19143BD\"></sup> Obey<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19143BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19143BE\"></sup> me, and I will be your God and you will be my people.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19143BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19143BF\"></sup> Walk in obedience to all<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19143BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19143BG\"></sup> I command you, that it may go well<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19143BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19143BH\"></sup> with you.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>But they did not listen<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19144BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19144BI\"></sup> or pay attention;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19144BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19144BJ\"></sup> instead, they followed the stubborn inclinations of their evil hearts.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19144BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19144BK\"></sup> They went backward<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19144BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19144BL\"></sup> and not forward.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>From the time your ancestors left Egypt until now, day after day, again and again<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19145BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19145BM\"></sup> I sent you my servants<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19145BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19145BN\"></sup> the prophets.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19145BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19145BO\"></sup>",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>But they did not listen to me or pay attention.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19146BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19146BP\"></sup> They were stiff-necked<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19146BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19146BQ\"></sup> and did more evil than their ancestors.’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19146BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19146BR\"></sup>",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>“When you tell<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19147BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19147BS\"></sup> them all this, they will not listen<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19147BT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BT&quot;&gt;BT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19147BT\"></sup> to you; when you call to them, they will not answer.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19147BU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BU&quot;&gt;BU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19147BU\"></sup>",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>Therefore say to them, ‘This is the nation that has not obeyed the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> its God or responded to correction.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19148BV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BV&quot;&gt;BV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19148BV\"></sup> Truth<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19148BW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BW&quot;&gt;BW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19148BW\"></sup> has perished; it has vanished from their lips.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>“‘Cut off<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19149BX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BX&quot;&gt;BX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19149BX\"></sup> your hair and throw it away; take up a lament<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19149BY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BY&quot;&gt;BY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19149BY\"></sup> on the barren heights, for the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has rejected and abandoned<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19149BZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BZ&quot;&gt;BZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19149BZ\"></sup> this generation that is under his wrath.",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>“‘The people of Judah have done evil<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19150CA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CA&quot;&gt;CA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19150CA\"></sup> in my eyes, declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>. They have set up their detestable idols<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19150CB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CB&quot;&gt;CB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19150CB\"></sup> in the house that bears my Name and have defiled<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19150CC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CC&quot;&gt;CC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19150CC\"></sup> it.",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>They have built the high places of Topheth<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19151CD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CD&quot;&gt;CD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19151CD\"></sup> in the Valley of Ben Hinnom<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19151CE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CE&quot;&gt;CE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19151CE\"></sup> to burn their sons and daughters<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19151CF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CF&quot;&gt;CF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19151CF\"></sup> in the fire—something I did not command, nor did it enter my mind.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19151CG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CG&quot;&gt;CG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19151CG\"></sup>",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>So beware, the days are coming, declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, when people will no longer call it Topheth or the Valley of Ben Hinnom, but the Valley of Slaughter,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19152CH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CH&quot;&gt;CH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19152CH\"></sup> for they will bury<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19152CI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CI&quot;&gt;CI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19152CI\"></sup> the dead in Topheth until there is no more room.",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>Then the carcasses<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19153CJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CJ&quot;&gt;CJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19153CJ\"></sup> of this people will become food<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19153CK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CK&quot;&gt;CK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19153CK\"></sup> for the birds and the wild animals, and there will be no one to frighten them away.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19153CL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CL&quot;&gt;CL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19153CL\"></sup>",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>I will bring an end to the sounds<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19154CM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CM&quot;&gt;CM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19154CM\"></sup> of joy and gladness and to the voices of bride and bridegroom<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19154CN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CN&quot;&gt;CN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19154CN\"></sup> in the towns of Judah and the streets of Jerusalem,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19154CO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CO&quot;&gt;CO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19154CO\"></sup> for the land will become desolate.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19154CP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CP&quot;&gt;CP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19154CP\"></sup>"
		},
		"8": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">8 </span>“‘At that time, declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, the bones of the kings and officials of Judah, the bones of the priests and prophets, and the bones<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19155A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19155A\"></sup> of the people of Jerusalem will be removed<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19155B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19155B\"></sup> from their graves.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>They will be exposed to the sun and the moon and all the stars of the heavens, which they have loved and served<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19156C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19156C\"></sup> and which they have followed and consulted and worshiped.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19156D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19156D\"></sup> They will not be gathered up or buried,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19156E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19156E\"></sup> but will be like dung lying on the ground.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19156F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19156F\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Wherever I banish them,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19157G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19157G\"></sup> all the survivors of this evil nation will prefer death to life,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19157H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19157H\"></sup> declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty.’",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>“Say to them, ‘This is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says:“‘When people fall down, do they not get up?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19158I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19158I\"></sup>When someone turns away,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19158J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19158J\"></sup> do they not return?",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Why then have these people turned away?Why does Jerusalem always turn away?They cling to deceit;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19159K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19159K\"></sup>they refuse to return.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19159L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19159L\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>I have listened<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19160M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19160M\"></sup> attentively,but they do not say what is right.None of them repent<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19160N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19160N\"></sup> of their wickedness,saying, “What have I done?”Each pursues their own course<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19160O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19160O\"></sup>like a horse charging into battle.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Even the stork in the skyknows her appointed seasons,and the dove, the swift and the thrushobserve the time of their migration.But my people do not know<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19161P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19161P\"></sup>the requirements of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>“‘How can you say, “We are wise,for we have the law<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19162Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19162Q\"></sup> of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,”when actually the lying pen of the scribeshas handled it falsely?",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>The wise<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19163R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19163R\"></sup> will be put to shame;they will be dismayed<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19163S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19163S\"></sup> and trapped.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19163T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19163T\"></sup>Since they have rejected the word<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19163U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19163U\"></sup> of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,what kind of wisdom<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19163V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19163V\"></sup> do they have?",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Therefore I will give their wives to other menand their fields to new owners.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19164W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19164W\"></sup>From the least to the greatest,all are greedy for gain;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19164X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19164X\"></sup>prophets<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19164Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19164Y\"></sup> and priests alike,all practice deceit.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19164Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19164Z\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>They dress the wound of my peopleas though it were not serious.“Peace, peace,” they say,when there is no peace.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19165AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19165AA\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Are they ashamed of their detestable conduct?No, they have no shame<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19166AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19166AB\"></sup> at all;they do not even know how to blush.So they will fall among the fallen;they will be brought down when they are punished,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19166AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19166AC\"></sup>says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19166AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19166AD\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>“‘I will take away their harvest,declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.There will be no grapes on the vine.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19167AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19167AE\"></sup>There will be no figs<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19167AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19167AF\"></sup> on the tree,and their leaves will wither.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19167AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19167AG\"></sup>What I have given themwill be taken<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19167AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19167AH\"></sup> from them.’”",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Why are we sitting here?Gather together!Let us flee to the fortified cities<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19168AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19168AI\"></sup>and perish there!For the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> our God has doomed us to perishand given us poisoned water<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19168AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19168AJ\"></sup> to drink,because we have sinned<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19168AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19168AK\"></sup> against him.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>We hoped for peace<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19169AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19169AL\"></sup>but no good has come,for a time of healingbut there is only terror.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19169AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19169AM\"></sup>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>The snorting of the enemy’s horses<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19170AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19170AN\"></sup>is heard from Dan;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19170AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19170AO\"></sup>at the neighing of their stallionsthe whole land trembles.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19170AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19170AP\"></sup>They have come to devour<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19170AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19170AQ\"></sup>the land and everything in it,the city and all who live there.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>“See, I will send venomous snakes<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19171AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19171AR\"></sup> among you,vipers that cannot be charmed,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19171AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19171AS\"></sup>and they will bite you,”declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>You who are my Comforter in sorrow,my heart is faint<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19172AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19172AT\"></sup> within me.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>Listen to the cry of my peoplefrom a land far away:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19173AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19173AU\"></sup>“Is the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> not in Zion?Is her King<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19173AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19173AV\"></sup> no longer there?”“Why have they aroused<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19173AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19173AW\"></sup> my anger with their images,with their worthless<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19173AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19173AX\"></sup> foreign idols?”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19173AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19173AY\"></sup>",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>“The harvest is past,the summer has ended,and we are not saved.”",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>Since my people are crushed,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19175AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19175AZ\"></sup> I am crushed;I mourn,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19175BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19175BA\"></sup> and horror grips me.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Is there no balm in Gilead?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19176BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19176BB\"></sup>Is there no physician<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19176BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19176BC\"></sup> there?Why then is there no healing<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19176BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19176BD\"></sup>for the wound of my people?"
		},
		"9": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">9 </span><sup class=\"versenum mid-line\">1 </sup>Oh, that my head were a spring of waterand my eyes a fountain of tears!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19177A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19177A\"></sup>I would weep<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19177B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19177B\"></sup> day and nightfor the slain of my people.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19177C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19177C\"></sup>",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Oh, that I had in the desert<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19178D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19178D\"></sup>a lodging place for travelers,so that I might leave my peopleand go away from them;for they are all adulterers,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19178E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19178E\"></sup>a crowd of unfaithful<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19178F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19178F\"></sup> people.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>“They make ready their tonguelike a bow, to shoot lies;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19179G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19179G\"></sup>it is not by truththat they triumph in the land.They go from one sin to another;they do not acknowledge<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19179H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19179H\"></sup> me,”declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>“Beware of your friends;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19180I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19180I\"></sup>do not trust anyone in your clan.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19180J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19180J\"></sup>For every one of them is a deceiver,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19180K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19180K\"></sup>and every friend a slanderer.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19180L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19180L\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Friend deceives friend,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19181M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19181M\"></sup>and no one speaks the truth.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19181N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19181N\"></sup>They have taught their tongues to lie;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19181O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19181O\"></sup>they weary themselves with sinning.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>You live in the midst of deception;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19182P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19182P\"></sup>in their deceit they refuse to acknowledge me,”declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Therefore this is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty says:“See, I will refine<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19183Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19183Q\"></sup> and test<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19183R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19183R\"></sup> them,for what else can I dobecause of the sin of my people?",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Their tongue<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19184S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19184S\"></sup> is a deadly arrow;it speaks deceitfully.With their mouths they all speak cordially to their neighbors,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19184T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19184T\"></sup>but in their hearts they set traps<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19184U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19184U\"></sup> for them.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19184V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19184V\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Should I not punish them for this?”declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.“Should I not avenge<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19185W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19185W\"></sup> myselfon such a nation as this?”",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>I will weep and wail for the mountainsand take up a lament concerning the wilderness grasslands.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19186X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19186X\"></sup>They are desolate and untraveled,and the lowing of cattle is not heard.The birds<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19186Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19186Y\"></sup> have all fledand the animals are gone.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>“I will make Jerusalem a heap<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19187Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19187Z\"></sup> of ruins,a haunt of jackals;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19187AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19187AA\"></sup>and I will lay waste the towns of Judah<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19187AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19187AB\"></sup>so no one can live there.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19187AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19187AC\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Who is wise<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19188AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19188AD\"></sup> enough to understand this? Who has been instructed by the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> and can explain it? Why has the land been ruined and laid waste like a desert that no one can cross?",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> said, “It is because they have forsaken my law, which I set before them; they have not obeyed me or followed my law.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19189AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19189AE\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Instead, they have followed<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19190AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19190AF\"></sup> the stubbornness of their hearts;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19190AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19190AG\"></sup> they have followed the Baals, as their ancestors taught them.”",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Therefore this is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty, the God of Israel, says: “See, I will make this people eat bitter food<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19191AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19191AH\"></sup> and drink poisoned water.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19191AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19191AI\"></sup>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>I will scatter them among nations<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19192AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19192AJ\"></sup> that neither they nor their ancestors have known,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19192AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19192AK\"></sup> and I will pursue them with the sword<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19192AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19192AL\"></sup> until I have made an end of them.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19192AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19192AM\"></sup>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>This is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty says:“Consider now! Call for the wailing women<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19193AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19193AN\"></sup> to come;send for the most skillful of them.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Let them come quicklyand wail over ustill our eyes overflow with tearsand water streams from our eyelids.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19194AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19194AO\"></sup>",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>The sound of wailing is heard from Zion:‘How ruined<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19195AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19195AP\"></sup> we are!How great is our shame!We must leave our landbecause our houses are in ruins.’”",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Now, you women, hear the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>;open your ears to the words of his mouth.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19196AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19196AQ\"></sup>Teach your daughters how to wail;teach one another a lament.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19196AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19196AR\"></sup>",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>Death has climbed in through our windows<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19197AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19197AS\"></sup>and has entered our fortresses;it has removed the children from the streetsand the young men<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19197AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19197AT\"></sup> from the public squares.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Say, “This is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> declares:“‘Dead bodies will lielike dung<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19198AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19198AU\"></sup> on the open field,like cut grain behind the reaper,with no one to gather them.’”",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>This is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says:“Let not the wise boast of their wisdom<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19199AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19199AV\"></sup>or the strong boast of their strength<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19199AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19199AW\"></sup>or the rich boast of their riches,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19199AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19199AX\"></sup>",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>but let the one who boasts boast<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19200AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19200AY\"></sup> about this:that they have the understanding to know<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19200AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19200AZ\"></sup> me,that I am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19200BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19200BA\"></sup> who exercises kindness,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19200BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19200BB\"></sup>justice and righteousness<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19200BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19200BC\"></sup> on earth,for in these I delight,”declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>“The days are coming,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, “when I will punish all who are circumcised only in the flesh<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19201BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19201BD\"></sup>—",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>Egypt, Judah, Edom, Ammon, Moab and all who live in the wilderness in distant places.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19202BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19202BE\"></sup> For all these nations are really uncircumcised,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19202BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19202BF\"></sup> and even the whole house of Israel is uncircumcised in heart.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19202BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19202BG\"></sup>”"
		},
		"10": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">10 </span>Hear what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says to you, people of Israel.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>This is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says:“Do not learn the ways of the nations<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19204B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19204B\"></sup>or be terrified by signs<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19204C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19204C\"></sup> in the heavens,though the nations are terrified by them.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>For the practices of the peoples are worthless;they cut a tree out of the forest,and a craftsman<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19205D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19205D\"></sup> shapes it with his chisel.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19205E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19205E\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>They adorn it with silver<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19206F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19206F\"></sup> and gold;they fasten it with hammer and nailsso it will not totter.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19206G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19206G\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Like a scarecrow in a cucumber field,their idols cannot speak;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19207H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19207H\"></sup>they must be carriedbecause they cannot walk.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19207I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19207I\"></sup>Do not fear them;they can do no harm<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19207J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19207J\"></sup>nor can they do any good.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19207K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19207K\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>No one is like you,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19208L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19208L\"></sup> <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>;you are great,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19208M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19208M\"></sup>and your name is mighty in power.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Who should not fear<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19209N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19209N\"></sup> you,King of the nations?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19209O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19209O\"></sup>This is your due.Among all the wise leaders of the nationsand in all their kingdoms,there is no one like you.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>They are all senseless<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19210P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19210P\"></sup> and foolish;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19210Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19210Q\"></sup>they are taught by worthless wooden idols.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19210R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19210R\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Hammered silver is brought from Tarshish<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19211S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19211S\"></sup>and gold from Uphaz.What the craftsman and goldsmith have made<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19211T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19211T\"></sup>is then dressed in blue and purple—all made by skilled workers.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>But the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> is the true God;he is the living God,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19212U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19212U\"></sup> the eternal King.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19212V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19212V\"></sup>When he is angry,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19212W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19212W\"></sup> the earth trembles;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19212X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19212X\"></sup>the nations cannot endure his wrath.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19212Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19212Y\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>“Tell them this: ‘These gods, who did not make the heavens and the earth, will perish<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19213Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19213Z\"></sup> from the earth and from under the heavens.’”",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>But God made<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19214AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19214AA\"></sup> the earth<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19214AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19214AB\"></sup> by his power;he founded the world by his wisdom<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19214AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19214AC\"></sup>and stretched out the heavens<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19214AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19214AD\"></sup> by his understanding.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>When he thunders,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19215AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19215AE\"></sup> the waters in the heavens roar;he makes clouds rise from the ends of the earth.He sends lightning<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19215AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19215AF\"></sup> with the rain<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19215AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19215AG\"></sup>and brings out the wind from his storehouses.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19215AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19215AH\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Everyone is senseless and without knowledge;every goldsmith is shamed<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19216AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19216AI\"></sup> by his idols.The images he makes are a fraud;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19216AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19216AJ\"></sup>they have no breath in them.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>They are worthless,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19217AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19217AK\"></sup> the objects of mockery;when their judgment comes, they will perish.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>He who is the Portion<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19218AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19218AL\"></sup> of Jacob is not like these,for he is the Maker of all things,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19218AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19218AM\"></sup>including Israel, the people of his inheritance<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19218AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19218AN\"></sup>—the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty is his name.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19218AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19218AO\"></sup>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Gather up your belongings<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19219AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19219AP\"></sup> to leave the land,you who live under siege.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>For this is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says:“At this time I will hurl<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19220AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19220AQ\"></sup> outthose who live in this land;I will bring distress<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19220AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19220AR\"></sup> on themso that they may be captured.”",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>Woe to me because of my injury!My wound<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19221AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19221AS\"></sup> is incurable!Yet I said to myself,“This is my sickness, and I must endure<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19221AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19221AT\"></sup> it.”",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>My tent<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19222AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19222AU\"></sup> is destroyed;all its ropes are snapped.My children are gone from me and are no more;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19222AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19222AV\"></sup>no one is left now to pitch my tentor to set up my shelter.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>The shepherds<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19223AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19223AW\"></sup> are senseless<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19223AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19223AX\"></sup>and do not inquire of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19223AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19223AY\"></sup>so they do not prosper<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19223AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19223AZ\"></sup>and all their flock is scattered.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19223BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19223BA\"></sup>",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Listen! The report is coming—a great commotion from the land of the north!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19224BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19224BB\"></sup>It will make the towns of Judah desolate,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19224BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19224BC\"></sup>a haunt of jackals.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19224BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19224BD\"></sup>",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, I know that people’s lives are not their own;it is not for them to direct their steps.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19225BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19225BE\"></sup>",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>Discipline me, <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, but only in due measure—not in your anger,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19226BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19226BF\"></sup>or you will reduce me to nothing.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19226BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19226BG\"></sup>",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>Pour out your wrath on the nations<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19227BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19227BH\"></sup>that do not acknowledge you,on the peoples who do not call on your name.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19227BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19227BI\"></sup>For they have devoured<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19227BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19227BJ\"></sup> Jacob;they have devoured him completelyand destroyed his homeland.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19227BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19227BK\"></sup>"
		},
		"11": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">11 </span>This is the word that came to Jeremiah from the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>:",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“Listen to the terms of this covenant<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19229A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19229A\"></sup> and tell them to the people of Judah and to those who live in Jerusalem.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Tell them that this is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, the God of Israel, says: ‘Cursed<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19230B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19230B\"></sup> is the one who does not obey the terms of this covenant—",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>the terms I commanded your ancestors when I brought them out of Egypt,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19231C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19231C\"></sup> out of the iron-smelting furnace.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19231D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19231D\"></sup>’ I said, ‘Obey<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19231E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19231E\"></sup> me and do everything I command you, and you will be my people,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19231F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19231F\"></sup> and I will be your God.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Then I will fulfill the oath I swore<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19232G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19232G\"></sup> to your ancestors, to give them a land flowing with milk and honey’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19232H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19232H\"></sup>—the land you possess today.”I answered, “Amen,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19232I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19232I\"></sup> <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.”",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> said to me, “Proclaim<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19233J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19233J\"></sup> all these words in the towns of Judah and in the streets of Jerusalem: ‘Listen to the terms of this covenant and follow<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19233K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19233K\"></sup> them.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>From the time I brought your ancestors up from Egypt until today, I warned them again and again,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19234L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19234L\"></sup> saying, “Obey me.”",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>But they did not listen or pay attention;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19235M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19235M\"></sup> instead, they followed the stubbornness of their evil hearts.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19235N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19235N\"></sup> So I brought on them all the curses<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19235O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19235O\"></sup> of the covenant I had commanded them to follow but that they did not keep.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19235P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19235P\"></sup>’”",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Then the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> said to me, “There is a conspiracy<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19236Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19236Q\"></sup> among the people of Judah and those who live in Jerusalem.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>They have returned to the sins of their ancestors,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19237R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19237R\"></sup> who refused to listen to my words.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19237S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19237S\"></sup> They have followed other gods<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19237T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19237T\"></sup> to serve them.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19237U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19237U\"></sup> Both Israel and Judah have broken the covenant<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19237V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19237V\"></sup> I made with their ancestors.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Therefore this is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says: ‘I will bring on them a disaster<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19238W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19238W\"></sup> they cannot escape.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19238X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19238X\"></sup> Although they cry<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19238Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19238Y\"></sup> out to me, I will not listen<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19238Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19238Z\"></sup> to them.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>The towns of Judah and the people of Jerusalem will go and cry out to the gods to whom they burn incense,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19239AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19239AA\"></sup> but they will not help them at all when disaster<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19239AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19239AB\"></sup> strikes.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>You, Judah, have as many gods<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19240AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19240AC\"></sup> as you have towns;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19240AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19240AD\"></sup> and the altars you have set up to burn incense<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19240AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19240AE\"></sup> to that shameful<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19240AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19240AF\"></sup> god Baal are as many as the streets of Jerusalem.’",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>“Do not pray<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19241AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19241AG\"></sup> for this people or offer any plea or petition for them, because I will not listen<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19241AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19241AH\"></sup> when they call to me in the time of their distress.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>“What is my beloved doing in my templeas she, with many others, works out her evil schemes?Can consecrated meat<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19242AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19242AI\"></sup> avert your punishment?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19242AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19242AJ\"></sup>When you engage in your wickedness,then you rejoice.”",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> called you a thriving olive tree<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19243AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19243AK\"></sup>with fruit beautiful in form.But with the roar of a mighty stormhe will set it on fire,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19243AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19243AL\"></sup>and its branches will be broken.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19243AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19243AM\"></sup>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty, who planted<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19244AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19244AN\"></sup> you, has decreed disaster<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19244AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19244AO\"></sup> for you, because the people of both Israel and Judah have done evil and aroused<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19244AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19244AP\"></sup> my anger by burning incense to Baal.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19244AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19244AQ\"></sup>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Because the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> revealed their plot to me, I knew it, for at that time he showed me what they were doing.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>I had been like a gentle lamb led to the slaughter;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19246AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19246AR\"></sup> I did not realize that they had plotted<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19246AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19246AS\"></sup> against me, saying,“Let us destroy the tree and its fruit;let us cut him off from the land of the living,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19246AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19246AT\"></sup>that his name be remembered<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19246AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19246AU\"></sup> no more.”",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>But you, <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty, who judge righteously<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19247AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19247AV\"></sup>and test the heart<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19247AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19247AW\"></sup> and mind,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19247AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19247AX\"></sup>let me see your vengeance<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19247AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19247AY\"></sup> on them,for to you I have committed my cause.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>Therefore this is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says about the people of Anathoth<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19248AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19248AZ\"></sup> who are threatening to kill you,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19248BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19248BA\"></sup> saying, “Do not prophesy<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19248BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19248BB\"></sup> in the name of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> or you will die<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19248BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19248BC\"></sup> by our hands”—",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>therefore this is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty says: “I will punish them. Their young men<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19249BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19249BD\"></sup> will die by the sword, their sons and daughters by famine.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>Not even a remnant<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19250BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19250BE\"></sup> will be left to them, because I will bring disaster on the people of Anathoth in the year of their punishment.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19250BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19250BF\"></sup>”"
		},
		"12": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">12 </span>You are always righteous,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19251A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19251A\"></sup> <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,when I bring a case<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19251B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19251B\"></sup> before you.Yet I would speak with you about your justice:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19251C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19251C\"></sup>Why does the way of the wicked prosper?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19251D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19251D\"></sup>Why do all the faithless live at ease?",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>You have planted<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19252E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19252E\"></sup> them, and they have taken root;they grow and bear fruit.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19252F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19252F\"></sup>You are always on their lipsbut far from their hearts.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19252G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19252G\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Yet you know me, <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>;you see me and test<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19253H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19253H\"></sup> my thoughts about you.Drag them off like sheep<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19253I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19253I\"></sup> to be butchered!Set them apart for the day of slaughter!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19253J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19253J\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>How long will the land lie parched<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19254K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19254K\"></sup>and the grass in every field be withered?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19254L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19254L\"></sup>Because those who live in it are wicked,the animals and birds have perished.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19254M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19254M\"></sup>Moreover, the people are saying,“He will not see what happens to us.”",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>“If you have raced with men on footand they have worn you out,how can you compete with horses?If you stumble in safe country,how will you manage in the thickets<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19255N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19255N\"></sup> by the Jordan?",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Your relatives, members of your own family—even they have betrayed you;they have raised a loud cry against you.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19256O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19256O\"></sup>Do not trust them,though they speak well of you.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19256P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19256P\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>“I will forsake<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19257Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19257Q\"></sup> my house,abandon<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19257R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19257R\"></sup> my inheritance;I will give the one I love<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19257S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19257S\"></sup>into the hands of her enemies.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19257T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19257T\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>My inheritance has become to melike a lion<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19258U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19258U\"></sup> in the forest.She roars at me;therefore I hate her.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19258V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19258V\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Has not my inheritance become to melike a speckled bird of preythat other birds of prey surround and attack?Go and gather all the wild beasts;bring them to devour.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19259W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19259W\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Many shepherds<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19260X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19260X\"></sup> will ruin my vineyardand trample down my field;they will turn my pleasant fieldinto a desolate wasteland.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19260Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19260Y\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>It will be made a wasteland,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19261Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19261Z\"></sup>parched and desolate before me;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19261AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19261AA\"></sup>the whole land will be laid wastebecause there is no one who cares.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Over all the barren heights in the desertdestroyers will swarm,for the sword<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19262AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19262AB\"></sup> of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19262AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19262AC\"></sup> will devour<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19262AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19262AD\"></sup>from one end of the land to the other;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19262AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19262AE\"></sup>no one will be safe.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19262AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19262AF\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>They will sow wheat but reap thorns;they will wear themselves out but gain nothing.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19263AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19263AG\"></sup>They will bear the shame of their harvestbecause of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>’s fierce anger.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19263AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19263AH\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>This is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says: “As for all my wicked neighbors who seize the inheritance<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19264AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19264AI\"></sup> I gave my people Israel, I will uproot<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19264AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19264AJ\"></sup> them from their lands and I will uproot<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19264AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19264AK\"></sup> the people of Judah from among them.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>But after I uproot them, I will again have compassion<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19265AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19265AL\"></sup> and will bring<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19265AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19265AM\"></sup> each of them back to their own inheritance and their own country.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>And if they learn<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19266AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19266AN\"></sup> well the ways of my people and swear by my name, saying, ‘As surely as the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> lives’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19266AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19266AO\"></sup>—even as they once taught my people to swear by Baal<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19266AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19266AP\"></sup>—then they will be established among my people.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19266AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19266AQ\"></sup>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>But if any nation does not listen, I will completely uproot and destroy<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19267AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19267AR\"></sup> it,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>."
		},
		"13": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">13 </span>This is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> said to me: “Go and buy a linen belt and put it around your waist, but do not let it touch water.”",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>So I bought a belt, as the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> directed, and put it around my waist.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Then the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to me a second time:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19270A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19270A\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>“Take the belt you bought and are wearing around your waist, and go now to Perath<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19271B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19271B\"></sup> and hide it there in a crevice in the rocks.”",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>So I went and hid it at Perath, as the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> told me.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19272C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19272C\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Many days later the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> said to me, “Go now to Perath and get the belt I told you to hide there.”",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>So I went to Perath and dug up the belt and took it from the place where I had hidden it, but now it was ruined and completely useless.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Then the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to me:",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>“This is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says: ‘In the same way I will ruin the pride of Judah and the great pride<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19276D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19276D\"></sup> of Jerusalem.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>These wicked people, who refuse to listen<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19277E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19277E\"></sup> to my words, who follow the stubbornness of their hearts<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19277F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19277F\"></sup> and go after other gods<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19277G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19277G\"></sup> to serve and worship them,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19277H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19277H\"></sup> will be like this belt—completely useless!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19277I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19277I\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>For as a belt is bound around the waist, so I bound all the people of Israel and all the people of Judah to me,’ declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, ‘to be my people for my renown<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19278J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19278J\"></sup> and praise and honor.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19278K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19278K\"></sup> But they have not listened.’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19278L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19278L\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>“Say to them: ‘This is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, the God of Israel, says: Every wineskin should be filled with wine.’ And if they say to you, ‘Don’t we know that every wineskin should be filled with wine?’",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>then tell them, ‘This is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says: I am going to fill with drunkenness<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19280M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19280M\"></sup> all who live in this land, including the kings who sit on David’s throne, the priests, the prophets and all those living in Jerusalem.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>I will smash them one against the other, parents and children alike, declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>. I will allow no pity<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19281N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19281N\"></sup> or mercy or compassion<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19281O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19281O\"></sup> to keep me from destroying<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19281P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19281P\"></sup> them.’”",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Hear and pay attention,do not be arrogant,for the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has spoken.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19282Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19282Q\"></sup>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Give glory<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19283R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19283R\"></sup> to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your Godbefore he brings the darkness,before your feet stumble<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19283S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19283S\"></sup>on the darkening hills.You hope for light,but he will turn it to utter darknessand change it to deep gloom.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19283T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19283T\"></sup>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>If you do not listen,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19284U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19284U\"></sup>I will weep in secretbecause of your pride;my eyes will weep bitterly,overflowing with tears,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19284V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19284V\"></sup>because the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>’s flock<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19284W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19284W\"></sup> will be taken captive.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19284X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19284X\"></sup>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Say to the king<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19285Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19285Y\"></sup> and to the queen mother,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19285Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19285Z\"></sup>“Come down from your thrones,for your glorious crowns<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19285AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19285AA\"></sup>will fall from your heads.”",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>The cities in the Negev will be shut up,and there will be no one to open them.All Judah<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19286AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19286AB\"></sup> will be carried into exile,carried completely away.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Look up and seethose who are coming from the north.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19287AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19287AC\"></sup>Where is the flock<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19287AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19287AD\"></sup> that was entrusted to you,the sheep of which you boasted?",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>What will you say when the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> sets over youthose you cultivated as your special allies?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19288AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19288AE\"></sup>Will not pain grip youlike that of a woman in labor?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19288AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19288AF\"></sup>",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>And if you ask yourself,“Why has this happened to me?”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19289AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19289AG\"></sup>—it is because of your many sins<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19289AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19289AH\"></sup>that your skirts have been torn off<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19289AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19289AI\"></sup>and your body mistreated.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19289AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19289AJ\"></sup>",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>Can an Ethiopian change his skinor a leopard its spots?Neither can you do goodwho are accustomed to doing evil.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19290AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19290AK\"></sup>",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>“I will scatter you like chaff<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19291AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19291AL\"></sup>driven by the desert wind.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19291AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19291AM\"></sup>",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>This is your lot,the portion<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19292AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19292AN\"></sup> I have decreed for you,”declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,“because you have forgotten<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19292AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19292AO\"></sup> meand trusted in false gods.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19292AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19292AP\"></sup>",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>I will pull up your skirts over your facethat your shame may be seen<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19293AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19293AQ\"></sup>—",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>your adulteries and lustful neighings,your shameless prostitution!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19294AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19294AR\"></sup>I have seen your detestable actson the hills and in the fields.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19294AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19294AS\"></sup>Woe to you, Jerusalem!How long will you be unclean?”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19294AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19294AT\"></sup>"
		},
		"14": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">14 </span>This is the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> that came to Jeremiah concerning the drought:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19295A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19295A\"></sup>",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“Judah mourns,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19296B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19296B\"></sup>her cities languish;they wail for the land,and a cry goes up from Jerusalem.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>The nobles send their servants for water;they go to the cisternsbut find no water.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19297C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19297C\"></sup>They return with their jars unfilled;dismayed and despairing,they cover their heads.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19297D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19297D\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>The ground is crackedbecause there is no rain in the land;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19298E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19298E\"></sup>the farmers are dismayedand cover their heads.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Even the doe in the fielddeserts her newborn fawnbecause there is no grass.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19299F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19299F\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Wild donkeys stand on the barren heights<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19300G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19300G\"></sup>and pant like jackals;their eyes failfor lack of food.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19300H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19300H\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Although our sins testify<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19301I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19301I\"></sup> against us,do something, <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, for the sake of your name.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19301J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19301J\"></sup>For we have often rebelled;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19301K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19301K\"></sup>we have sinned<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19301L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19301L\"></sup> against you.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>You who are the hope<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19302M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19302M\"></sup> of Israel,its Savior<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19302N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19302N\"></sup> in times of distress,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19302O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19302O\"></sup>why are you like a stranger in the land,like a traveler who stays only a night?",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Why are you like a man taken by surprise,like a warrior powerless to save?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19303P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19303P\"></sup>You are among<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19303Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19303Q\"></sup> us, <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,and we bear your name;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19303R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19303R\"></sup>do not forsake<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19303S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19303S\"></sup> us!",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>This is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says about this people:“They greatly love to wander;they do not restrain their feet.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19304T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19304T\"></sup>So the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> does not accept<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19304U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19304U\"></sup> them;he will now remember<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19304V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19304V\"></sup> their wickednessand punish them for their sins.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19304W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19304W\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Then the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> said to me, “Do not pray<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19305X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19305X\"></sup> for the well-being of this people.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Although they fast, I will not listen to their cry;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19306Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19306Y\"></sup> though they offer burnt offerings<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19306Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19306Z\"></sup> and grain offerings,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19306AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19306AA\"></sup> I will not accept<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19306AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19306AB\"></sup> them. Instead, I will destroy them with the sword,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19306AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19306AC\"></sup> famine<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19306AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19306AD\"></sup> and plague.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19306AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19306AE\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>But I said, “Alas, Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>! The prophets<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19307AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19307AF\"></sup> keep telling them, ‘You will not see the sword or suffer famine.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19307AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19307AG\"></sup> Indeed, I will give you lasting peace<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19307AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19307AH\"></sup> in this place.’”",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Then the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> said to me, “The prophets are prophesying lies<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19308AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19308AI\"></sup> in my name. I have not sent<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19308AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19308AJ\"></sup> them or appointed them or spoken to them. They are prophesying to you false visions,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19308AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19308AK\"></sup> divinations,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19308AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19308AL\"></sup> idolatries and the delusions of their own minds.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Therefore this is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says about the prophets who are prophesying in my name: I did not send them, yet they are saying, ‘No sword or famine will touch this land.’ Those same prophets will perish<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19309AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19309AM\"></sup> by sword and famine.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19309AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19309AN\"></sup>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>And the people they are prophesying to will be thrown out into the streets of Jerusalem because of the famine and sword. There will be no one to bury<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19310AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19310AO\"></sup> them, their wives, their sons and their daughters.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19310AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19310AP\"></sup> I will pour out on them the calamity they deserve.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19310AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19310AQ\"></sup>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>“Speak this word to them:“‘Let my eyes overflow with tears<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19311AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19311AR\"></sup>night and day without ceasing;for the Virgin<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19311AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19311AS\"></sup> Daughter, my people,has suffered a grievous wound,a crushing blow.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19311AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19311AT\"></sup>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>If I go into the country,I see those slain by the sword;if I go into the city,I see the ravages of famine.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19312AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19312AU\"></sup>Both prophet and priesthave gone to a land they know not.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19312AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19312AV\"></sup>’”",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>Have you rejected Judah completely?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19313AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19313AW\"></sup>Do you despise Zion?Why have you afflicted usso that we cannot be healed?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19313AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19313AX\"></sup>We hoped for peacebut no good has come,for a time of healingbut there is only terror.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19313AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19313AY\"></sup>",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>We acknowledge<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19314AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19314AZ\"></sup> our wickedness, <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,and the guilt of our ancestors;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19314BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19314BA\"></sup>we have indeed sinned<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19314BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19314BB\"></sup> against you.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>For the sake of your name<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19315BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19315BC\"></sup> do not despise us;do not dishonor your glorious throne.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19315BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19315BD\"></sup>Remember your covenant<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19315BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19315BE\"></sup> with usand do not break it.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Do any of the worthless idols<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19316BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19316BF\"></sup> of the nations bring rain?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19316BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19316BG\"></sup>Do the skies themselves send down showers?No, it is you, <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> our God.Therefore our hope is in you,for you are the one who does all this.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19316BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19316BH\"></sup>"
		},
		"15": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">15 </span>Then the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> said to me: “Even if Moses<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19317A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19317A\"></sup> and Samuel<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19317B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19317B\"></sup> were to stand before me, my heart would not go out to this people.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19317C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19317C\"></sup> Send them away from my presence!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19317D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19317D\"></sup> Let them go!",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>And if they ask you, ‘Where shall we go?’ tell them, ‘This is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says:“‘Those destined for death, to death;those for the sword, to the sword;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19318E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19318E\"></sup>those for starvation, to starvation;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19318F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19318F\"></sup>those for captivity, to captivity.’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19318G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19318G\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>“I will send four kinds of destroyers<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19319H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19319H\"></sup> against them,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, “the sword<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19319I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19319I\"></sup> to kill and the dogs<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19319J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19319J\"></sup> to drag away and the birds<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19319K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19319K\"></sup> and the wild animals to devour and destroy.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19319L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19319L\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>I will make them abhorrent<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19320M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19320M\"></sup> to all the kingdoms of the earth<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19320N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19320N\"></sup> because of what Manasseh<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19320O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19320O\"></sup> son of Hezekiah king of Judah did in Jerusalem.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>“Who will have pity<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19321P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19321P\"></sup> on you, Jerusalem?Who will mourn for you?Who will stop to ask how you are?",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>You have rejected<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19322Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19322Q\"></sup> me,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.“You keep on backsliding.So I will reach out<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19322R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19322R\"></sup> and destroy you;I am tired of holding back.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19322S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19322S\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>I will winnow<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19323T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19323T\"></sup> them with a winnowing forkat the city gates of the land.I will bring bereavement<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19323U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19323U\"></sup> and destruction on my people,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19323V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19323V\"></sup>for they have not changed their ways.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19323W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19323W\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>I will make their widows<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19324X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19324X\"></sup> more numerousthan the sand of the sea.At midday I will bring a destroyer<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19324Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19324Y\"></sup>against the mothers of their young men;suddenly I will bring down on themanguish and terror.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19324Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19324Z\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>The mother of seven will grow faint<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19325AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19325AA\"></sup>and breathe her last.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19325AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19325AB\"></sup>Her sun will set while it is still day;she will be disgraced<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19325AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19325AC\"></sup> and humiliated.I will put the survivors to the sword<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19325AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19325AD\"></sup>before their enemies,”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19325AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19325AE\"></sup>declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Alas, my mother, that you gave me birth,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19326AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19326AF\"></sup>a man with whom the whole land strives and contends!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19326AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19326AG\"></sup>I have neither lent<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19326AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19326AH\"></sup> nor borrowed,yet everyone curses<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19326AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19326AI\"></sup> me.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> said,“Surely I will deliver you<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19327AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19327AJ\"></sup> for a good purpose;surely I will make your enemies plead<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19327AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19327AK\"></sup> with youin times of disaster and times of distress.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>“Can a man break iron—iron from the north<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19328AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19328AL\"></sup>—or bronze?",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>“Your wealth<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19329AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19329AM\"></sup> and your treasuresI will give as plunder,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19329AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19329AN\"></sup> without charge,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19329AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19329AO\"></sup>because of all your sinsthroughout your country.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19329AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19329AP\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>I will enslave you to your enemiesin a land you do not know,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19330AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19330AQ\"></sup>for my anger will kindle a fire<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19330AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19330AR\"></sup>that will burn against you.”",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, you understand;remember me and care for me.Avenge me on my persecutors.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19331AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19331AS\"></sup>You are long-suffering<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19331AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19331AT\"></sup>—do not take me away;think of how I suffer reproach for your sake.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19331AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19331AU\"></sup>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>When your words came, I ate<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19332AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19332AV\"></sup> them;they were my joy and my heart’s delight,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19332AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19332AW\"></sup>for I bear your name,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19332AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19332AX\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> God Almighty.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>I never sat<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19333AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19333AY\"></sup> in the company of revelers,never made merry with them;I sat alone because your hand<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19333AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19333AZ\"></sup> was on meand you had filled me with indignation.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Why is my pain unendingand my wound grievous and incurable?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19334BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19334BA\"></sup>You are to me like a deceptive brook,like a spring that fails.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19334BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19334BB\"></sup>",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>Therefore this is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says:“If you repent, I will restore youthat you may serve<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19335BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19335BC\"></sup> me;if you utter worthy, not worthless, words,you will be my spokesman.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19335BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19335BD\"></sup>Let this people turn to you,but you must not turn to them.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>I will make you a wall<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19336BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19336BE\"></sup> to this people,a fortified wall of bronze;they will fight against youbut will not overcome<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19336BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19336BF\"></sup> you,for I am with youto rescue and save you,”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19336BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19336BG\"></sup>declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>“I will save<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19337BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19337BH\"></sup> you from the hands of the wicked<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19337BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19337BI\"></sup>and deliver<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19337BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19337BJ\"></sup> you from the grasp of the cruel.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19337BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19337BK\"></sup>"
		},
		"16": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">16 </span>Then the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to me:",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“You must not marry<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19339A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19339A\"></sup> and have sons or daughters in this place.”",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>For this is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says about the sons and daughters born in this land and about the women who are their mothers and the men who are their fathers:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19340B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19340B\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>“They will die of deadly diseases. They will not be mourned or buried<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19341C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19341C\"></sup> but will be like dung lying on the ground.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19341D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19341D\"></sup> They will perish by sword and famine,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19341E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19341E\"></sup> and their dead bodies will become food for the birds and the wild animals.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19341F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19341F\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>For this is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says: “Do not enter a house where there is a funeral meal; do not go to mourn or show sympathy, because I have withdrawn my blessing, my love and my pity<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19342G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19342G\"></sup> from this people,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>“Both high and low will die in this land.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19343H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19343H\"></sup> They will not be buried or mourned,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19343I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19343I\"></sup> and no one will cut<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19343J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19343J\"></sup> themselves or shave<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19343K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19343K\"></sup> their head for the dead.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>No one will offer food<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19344L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19344L\"></sup> to comfort those who mourn<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19344M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19344M\"></sup> for the dead—not even for a father or a mother—nor will anyone give them a drink to console<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19344N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19344N\"></sup> them.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>“And do not enter a house where there is feasting and sit down to eat and drink.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19345O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19345O\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>For this is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty, the God of Israel, says: Before your eyes and in your days I will bring an end to the sounds<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19346P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19346P\"></sup> of joy and gladness and to the voices of bride<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19346Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19346Q\"></sup> and bridegroom in this place.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19346R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19346R\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>“When you tell these people all this and they ask you, ‘Why has the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> decreed such a great disaster against us? What wrong have we done? What sin have we committed against the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> our God?’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19347S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19347S\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>then say to them, ‘It is because your ancestors forsook me,’ declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, ‘and followed other gods and served and worshiped<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19348T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19348T\"></sup> them. They forsook me and did not keep my law.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19348U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19348U\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>But you have behaved more wickedly than your ancestors.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19349V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19349V\"></sup> See how all of you are following the stubbornness of your evil hearts<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19349W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19349W\"></sup> instead of obeying me.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>So I will throw you out of this land<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19350X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19350X\"></sup> into a land neither you nor your ancestors have known,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19350Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19350Y\"></sup> and there you will serve other gods<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19350Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19350Z\"></sup> day and night, for I will show you no favor.’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19350AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19350AA\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>“However, the days are coming,”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19351AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19351AB\"></sup> declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, “when it will no longer be said, ‘As surely as the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> lives, who brought the Israelites up out of Egypt,’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19351AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19351AC\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>but it will be said, ‘As surely as the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> lives, who brought the Israelites up out of the land of the north<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19352AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19352AD\"></sup> and out of all the countries where he had banished them.’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19352AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19352AE\"></sup> For I will restore<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19352AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19352AF\"></sup> them to the land I gave their ancestors.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19352AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19352AG\"></sup>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>“But now I will send for many fishermen,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, “and they will catch them.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19353AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19353AH\"></sup> After that I will send for many hunters, and they will hunt<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19353AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19353AI\"></sup> them down on every mountain and hill and from the crevices of the rocks.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19353AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19353AJ\"></sup>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>My eyes are on all their ways; they are not hidden<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19354AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19354AK\"></sup> from me, nor is their sin concealed from my eyes.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19354AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19354AL\"></sup>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>I will repay<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19355AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19355AM\"></sup> them double<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19355AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19355AN\"></sup> for their wickedness and their sin, because they have defiled my land<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19355AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19355AO\"></sup> with the lifeless forms of their vile images<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19355AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19355AP\"></sup> and have filled my inheritance with their detestable idols.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19355AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19355AQ\"></sup>”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19355AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19355AR\"></sup>",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, my strength and my fortress,my refuge<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19356AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19356AS\"></sup> in time of distress,to you the nations will come<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19356AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19356AT\"></sup>from the ends of the earth and say,“Our ancestors possessed nothing but false gods,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19356AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19356AU\"></sup>worthless idols<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19356AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19356AV\"></sup> that did them no good.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19356AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19356AW\"></sup>",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Do people make their own gods?Yes, but they are not gods!”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19357AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19357AX\"></sup>",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>“Therefore I will teach them—this time I will teach themmy power and might.Then they will knowthat my name<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19358AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19358AY\"></sup> is the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>."
		},
		"17": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">17 </span>“Judah’s sin is engraved with an iron tool,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19359A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19359A\"></sup>inscribed with a flint point,on the tablets of their hearts<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19359B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19359B\"></sup>and on the horns<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19359C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19359C\"></sup> of their altars.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Even their children remembertheir altars and Asherah poles<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19360D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19360D\"></sup>beside the spreading treesand on the high hills.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19360E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19360E\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>My mountain in the landand your wealth and all your treasuresI will give away as plunder,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19361F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19361F\"></sup>together with your high places,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19361G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19361G\"></sup>because of sin throughout your country.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19361H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19361H\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Through your own fault you will losethe inheritance<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19362I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19362I\"></sup> I gave you.I will enslave you to your enemies<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19362J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19362J\"></sup>in a land<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19362K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19362K\"></sup> you do not know,for you have kindled my anger,and it will burn<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19362L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19362L\"></sup> forever.”",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>This is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says:“Cursed is the one who trusts in man,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19363M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19363M\"></sup>who draws strength from mere fleshand whose heart turns away from the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19363N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19363N\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>That person will be like a bush in the wastelands;they will not see prosperity when it comes.They will dwell in the parched places<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19364O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19364O\"></sup> of the desert,in a salt<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19364P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19364P\"></sup> land where no one lives.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>“But blessed<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19365Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19365Q\"></sup> is the one who trusts<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19365R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19365R\"></sup> in the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,whose confidence is in him.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>They will be like a tree planted by the waterthat sends out its roots by the stream.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19366S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19366S\"></sup>It does not fear when heat comes;its leaves are always green.It has no worries in a year of drought<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19366T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19366T\"></sup>and never fails to bear fruit.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19366U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19366U\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>The heart<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19367V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19367V\"></sup> is deceitful above all thingsand beyond cure.Who can understand it?",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>“I the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> search the heart<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19368W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19368W\"></sup>and examine the mind,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19368X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19368X\"></sup>to reward<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19368Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19368Y\"></sup> each person according to their conduct,according to what their deeds deserve.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19368Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19368Z\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Like a partridge that hatches eggs it did not layare those who gain riches by unjust means.When their lives are half gone, their riches will desert them,and in the end they will prove to be fools.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19369AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19369AA\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>A glorious throne,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19370AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19370AB\"></sup> exalted from the beginning,is the place of our sanctuary.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, you are the hope<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19371AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19371AC\"></sup> of Israel;all who forsake<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19371AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19371AD\"></sup> you will be put to shame.Those who turn away from you will be written in the dust<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19371AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19371AE\"></sup>because they have forsaken the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,the spring of living water.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19371AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19371AF\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Heal me, <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, and I will be healed;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19372AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19372AG\"></sup>save<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19372AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19372AH\"></sup> me and I will be saved,for you are the one I praise.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19372AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19372AI\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>They keep saying to me,“Where is the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>?Let it now be fulfilled!”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19373AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19373AJ\"></sup>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>I have not run away from being your shepherd;you know I have not desired the day of despair.What passes my lips<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19374AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19374AK\"></sup> is open before you.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Do not be a terror<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19375AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19375AL\"></sup> to me;you are my refuge<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19375AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19375AM\"></sup> in the day of disaster.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19375AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19375AN\"></sup>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Let my persecutors be put to shame,but keep me from shame;let them be terrified,but keep me from terror.Bring on them the day of disaster;destroy them with double destruction.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19376AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19376AO\"></sup>",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>This is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> said to me: “Go and stand at the Gate of the People, through which the kings of Judah go in and out; stand also at all the other gates of Jerusalem.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19377AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19377AP\"></sup>",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Say to them, ‘Hear the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, you kings of Judah and all people of Judah and everyone living in Jerusalem<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19378AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19378AQ\"></sup> who come through these gates.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19378AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19378AR\"></sup>",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>This is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says: Be careful not to carry a load on the Sabbath<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19379AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19379AS\"></sup> day or bring it through the gates of Jerusalem.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Do not bring a load out of your houses or do any work on the Sabbath, but keep the Sabbath day holy, as I commanded your ancestors.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19380AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19380AT\"></sup>",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>Yet they did not listen or pay attention;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19381AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19381AU\"></sup> they were stiff-necked<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19381AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19381AV\"></sup> and would not listen or respond to discipline.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19381AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19381AW\"></sup>",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>But if you are careful to obey me, declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, and bring no load through the gates of this city on the Sabbath, but keep the Sabbath day holy<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19382AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19382AX\"></sup> by not doing any work on it,",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>then kings who sit on David’s throne<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19383AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19383AY\"></sup> will come through the gates of this city with their officials. They and their officials will come riding in chariots and on horses, accompanied by the men of Judah and those living in Jerusalem, and this city will be inhabited forever.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19383AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19383AZ\"></sup>",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>People will come from the towns of Judah and the villages around Jerusalem, from the territory of Benjamin and the western foothills, from the hill country and the Negev,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19384BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19384BA\"></sup> bringing burnt offerings and sacrifices, grain offerings and incense, and bringing thank offerings to the house of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>But if you do not obey<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19385BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19385BB\"></sup> me to keep the Sabbath<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19385BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19385BC\"></sup> day holy by not carrying any load as you come through the gates of Jerusalem on the Sabbath day, then I will kindle an unquenchable fire<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19385BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19385BD\"></sup> in the gates of Jerusalem that will consume her fortresses.’”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19385BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19385BE\"></sup>"
		},
		"18": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">18 </span>This is the word that came to Jeremiah from the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>:",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“Go down to the potter’s house, and there I will give you my message.”",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>So I went down to the potter’s house, and I saw him working at the wheel.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>But the pot he was shaping from the clay was marred in his hands; so the potter formed it into another pot, shaping it as seemed best to him.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Then the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to me.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>He said, “Can I not do with you, Israel, as this potter does?” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>. “Like clay<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19391A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19391A\"></sup> in the hand of the potter, so are you in my hand,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19391B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19391B\"></sup> Israel.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>If at any time I announce that a nation or kingdom is to be uprooted,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19392C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19392C\"></sup> torn down and destroyed,",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>and if that nation I warned repents of its evil, then I will relent<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19393D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19393D\"></sup> and not inflict on it the disaster<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19393E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19393E\"></sup> I had planned.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>And if at another time I announce that a nation or kingdom is to be built<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19394F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19394F\"></sup> up and planted,",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>and if it does evil<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19395G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19395G\"></sup> in my sight and does not obey me, then I will reconsider<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19395H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19395H\"></sup> the good I had intended to do for it.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19395I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19395I\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>“Now therefore say to the people of Judah and those living in Jerusalem, ‘This is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says: Look! I am preparing a disaster<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19396J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19396J\"></sup> for you and devising a plan<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19396K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19396K\"></sup> against you. So turn<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19396L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19396L\"></sup> from your evil ways,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19396M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19396M\"></sup> each one of you, and reform your ways and your actions.’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19396N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19396N\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>But they will reply, ‘It’s no use.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19397O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19397O\"></sup> We will continue with our own plans; we will all follow the stubbornness of our evil hearts.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19397P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19397P\"></sup>’”",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Therefore this is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says:“Inquire among the nations:Who has ever heard anything like this?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19398Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19398Q\"></sup>A most horrible<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19398R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19398R\"></sup> thing has been doneby Virgin<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19398S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19398S\"></sup> Israel.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Does the snow of Lebanonever vanish from its rocky slopes?Do its cool waters from distant sourcesever stop flowing?",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Yet my people have forgotten<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19400T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19400T\"></sup> me;they burn incense<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19400U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19400U\"></sup> to worthless idols,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19400V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19400V\"></sup>which made them stumble<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19400W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19400W\"></sup> in their ways,in the ancient paths.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19400X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19400X\"></sup>They made them walk in byways,on roads not built up.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19400Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19400Y\"></sup>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Their land will be an object of horror<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19401Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19401Z\"></sup>and of lasting scorn;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19401AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19401AA\"></sup>all who pass by will be appalled<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19401AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19401AB\"></sup>and will shake their heads.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19401AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19401AC\"></sup>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Like a wind<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19402AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19402AD\"></sup> from the east,I will scatter them before their enemies;I will show them my back and not my face<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19402AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19402AE\"></sup>in the day of their disaster.”",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>They said, “Come, let’s make plans<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19403AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19403AF\"></sup> against Jeremiah; for the teaching of the law by the priest<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19403AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19403AG\"></sup> will not cease, nor will counsel from the wise,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19403AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19403AH\"></sup> nor the word from the prophets.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19403AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19403AI\"></sup> So come, let’s attack him with our tongues<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19403AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19403AJ\"></sup> and pay no attention to anything he says.”",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>Listen to me, <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>;hear what my accusers<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19404AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19404AK\"></sup> are saying!",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Should good be repaid with evil?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19405AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19405AL\"></sup>Yet they have dug a pit<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19405AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19405AM\"></sup> for me.Remember that I stood<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19405AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19405AN\"></sup> before youand spoke in their behalf<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19405AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19405AO\"></sup>to turn your wrath away from them.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>So give their children over to famine;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19406AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19406AP\"></sup>hand them over to the power of the sword.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19406AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19406AQ\"></sup>Let their wives be made childless and widows;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19406AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19406AR\"></sup>let their men be put to death,their young men<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19406AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19406AS\"></sup> slain by the sword in battle.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Let a cry<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19407AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19407AT\"></sup> be heard from their houseswhen you suddenly bring invaders against them,for they have dug a pit<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19407AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19407AU\"></sup> to capture meand have hidden snares<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19407AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19407AV\"></sup> for my feet.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>But you, <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, knowall their plots to kill<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19408AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19408AW\"></sup> me.Do not forgive<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19408AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19408AX\"></sup> their crimesor blot out their sins from your sight.Let them be overthrown before you;deal with them in the time of your anger.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19408AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19408AY\"></sup>"
		},
		"19": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">19 </span>This is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says: “Go and buy a clay jar from a potter.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19409A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19409A\"></sup> Take along some of the elders<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19409B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19409B\"></sup> of the people and of the priests",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>and go out to the Valley of Ben Hinnom,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19410C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19410C\"></sup> near the entrance of the Potsherd Gate. There proclaim the words I tell you,",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>and say, ‘Hear the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, you kings<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19411D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19411D\"></sup> of Judah and people of Jerusalem. This is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty, the God of Israel, says: Listen! I am going to bring a disaster<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19411E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19411E\"></sup> on this place that will make the ears of everyone who hears of it tingle.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19411F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19411F\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>For they have forsaken<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19412G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19412G\"></sup> me and made this a place of foreign gods<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19412H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19412H\"></sup>; they have burned incense<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19412I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19412I\"></sup> in it to gods that neither they nor their ancestors nor the kings of Judah ever knew, and they have filled this place with the blood of the innocent.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19412J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19412J\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>They have built the high places of Baal to burn their children<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19413K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19413K\"></sup> in the fire as offerings to Baal—something I did not command or mention, nor did it enter my mind.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19413L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19413L\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>So beware, the days are coming, declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, when people will no longer call this place Topheth<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19414M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19414M\"></sup> or the Valley of Ben Hinnom,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19414N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19414N\"></sup> but the Valley of Slaughter.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19414O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19414O\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>“‘In this place I will ruin the plans<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19415P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19415P\"></sup> of Judah and Jerusalem. I will make them fall by the sword before their enemies,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19415Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19415Q\"></sup> at the hands of those who want to kill them, and I will give their carcasses<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19415R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19415R\"></sup> as food<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19415S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19415S\"></sup> to the birds and the wild animals.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>I will devastate this city and make it an object of horror and scorn;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19416T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19416T\"></sup> all who pass by will be appalled<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19416U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19416U\"></sup> and will scoff because of all its wounds.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19416V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19416V\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>I will make them eat<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19417W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19417W\"></sup> the flesh of their sons and daughters, and they will eat one another’s flesh because their enemies<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19417X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19417X\"></sup> will press the siege so hard against them to destroy them.’",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>“Then break the jar<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19418Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19418Y\"></sup> while those who go with you are watching,",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>and say to them, ‘This is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty says: I will smash<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19419Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19419Z\"></sup> this nation and this city just as this potter’s jar is smashed and cannot be repaired. They will bury<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19419AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19419AA\"></sup> the dead in Topheth until there is no more room.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>This is what I will do to this place and to those who live here, declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>. I will make this city like Topheth.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>The houses<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19421AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19421AB\"></sup> in Jerusalem and those of the kings of Judah will be defiled<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19421AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19421AC\"></sup> like this place, Topheth—all the houses where they burned incense on the roofs<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19421AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19421AD\"></sup> to all the starry hosts<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19421AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19421AE\"></sup> and poured out drink offerings<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19421AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19421AF\"></sup> to other gods.’”",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Jeremiah then returned from Topheth, where the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> had sent him to prophesy, and stood in the court<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19422AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19422AG\"></sup> of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>’s temple and said to all the people,",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>“This is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty, the God of Israel, says: ‘Listen! I am going to bring on this city and all the villages around it every disaster<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19423AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19423AH\"></sup> I pronounced against them, because they were stiff-necked<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19423AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19423AI\"></sup> and would not listen<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19423AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19423AJ\"></sup> to my words.’”"
		},
		"20": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">20 </span>When the priest Pashhur son of Immer,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19424A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19424A\"></sup> the official<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19424B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19424B\"></sup> in charge of the temple of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, heard Jeremiah prophesying these things,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>he had Jeremiah the prophet beaten<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19425C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19425C\"></sup> and put in the stocks<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19425D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19425D\"></sup> at the Upper Gate of Benjamin<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19425E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19425E\"></sup> at the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>’s temple.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>The next day, when Pashhur released him from the stocks, Jeremiah said to him, “The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>’s name<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19426F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19426F\"></sup> for you is not Pashhur, but Terror on Every Side.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19426G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19426G\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>For this is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says: ‘I will make you a terror to yourself and to all your friends; with your own eyes<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19427H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19427H\"></sup> you will see them fall by the sword of their enemies. I will give<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19427I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19427I\"></sup> all Judah into the hands of the king of Babylon, who will carry<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19427J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19427J\"></sup> them away to Babylon or put them to the sword.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>I will deliver all the wealth<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19428K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19428K\"></sup> of this city into the hands of their enemies—all its products, all its valuables and all the treasures of the kings of Judah. They will take it away<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19428L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19428L\"></sup> as plunder and carry it off to Babylon.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>And you, Pashhur, and all who live in your house will go into exile to Babylon. There you will die and be buried, you and all your friends to whom you have prophesied<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19429M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19429M\"></sup> lies.’”",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>You deceived<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19430N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19430N\"></sup> me, <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, and I was deceived;you overpowered<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19430O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19430O\"></sup> me and prevailed.I am ridiculed<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19430P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19430P\"></sup> all day long;everyone mocks<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19430Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19430Q\"></sup> me.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Whenever I speak, I cry outproclaiming violence and destruction.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19431R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19431R\"></sup>So the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has brought meinsult and reproach<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19431S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19431S\"></sup> all day long.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>But if I say, “I will not mention his wordor speak anymore in his name,”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19432T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19432T\"></sup>his word is in my heart like a fire,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19432U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19432U\"></sup>a fire shut up in my bones.I am weary of holding it in;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19432V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19432V\"></sup>indeed, I cannot.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>I hear many whispering,“Terror<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19433W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19433W\"></sup> on every side!Denounce<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19433X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19433X\"></sup> him! Let’s denounce him!”All my friends<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19433Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19433Y\"></sup>are waiting for me to slip,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19433Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19433Z\"></sup> saying,“Perhaps he will be deceived;then we will prevail<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19433AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19433AA\"></sup> over himand take our revenge<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19433AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19433AB\"></sup> on him.”",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>But the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19434AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19434AC\"></sup> is with me like a mighty warrior;so my persecutors<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19434AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19434AD\"></sup> will stumble and not prevail.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19434AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19434AE\"></sup>They will fail and be thoroughly disgraced;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19434AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19434AF\"></sup>their dishonor will never be forgotten.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty, you who examine the righteousand probe the heart and mind,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19435AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19435AG\"></sup>let me see your vengeance<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19435AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19435AH\"></sup> on them,for to you I have committed<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19435AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19435AI\"></sup> my cause.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Sing<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19436AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19436AJ\"></sup> to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>!Give praise to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>!He rescues<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19436AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19436AK\"></sup> the life of the needyfrom the hands of the wicked.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19436AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19436AL\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Cursed be the day I was born!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19437AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19437AM\"></sup>May the day my mother bore me not be blessed!",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Cursed be the man who brought my father the news,who made him very glad, saying,“A child is born to you—a son!”",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>May that man be like the towns<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19439AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19439AN\"></sup>the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> overthrew without pity.May he hear wailing<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19439AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19439AO\"></sup> in the morning,a battle cry at noon.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>For he did not kill me in the womb,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19440AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19440AP\"></sup>with my mother as my grave,her womb enlarged forever.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Why did I ever come out of the womb<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19441AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19441AQ\"></sup>to see trouble<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19441AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19441AR\"></sup> and sorrowand to end my days in shame?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19441AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19441AS\"></sup>"
		},
		"21": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">21 </span>The word came to Jeremiah from the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> when King Zedekiah<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19442A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19442A\"></sup> sent to him Pashhur<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19442B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19442B\"></sup> son of Malkijah and the priest Zephaniah<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19442C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19442C\"></sup> son of Maaseiah. They said:",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“Inquire<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19443D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19443D\"></sup> now of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> for us because Nebuchadnezzar<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19443E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19443E\"></sup> king of Babylon<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19443F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19443F\"></sup> is attacking us. Perhaps the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will perform wonders<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19443G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19443G\"></sup> for us as in times past so that he will withdraw from us.”",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>But Jeremiah answered them, “Tell Zedekiah,",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>‘This is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, the God of Israel, says: I am about to turn<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19445H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19445H\"></sup> against you the weapons of war that are in your hands, which you are using to fight the king of Babylon and the Babylonians who are outside the wall besieging<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19445I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19445I\"></sup> you. And I will gather them inside this city.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>I myself will fight<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19446J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19446J\"></sup> against you with an outstretched hand<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19446K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19446K\"></sup> and a mighty arm<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19446L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19446L\"></sup> in furious anger and in great wrath.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>I will strike<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19447M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19447M\"></sup> down those who live in this city—both man and beast—and they will die of a terrible plague.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19447N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19447N\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>After that, declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, I will give Zedekiah<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19448O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19448O\"></sup> king of Judah, his officials and the people in this city who survive the plague,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19448P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19448P\"></sup> sword and famine, into the hands of Nebuchadnezzar king of Babylon<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19448Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19448Q\"></sup> and to their enemies<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19448R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19448R\"></sup> who want to kill them.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19448S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19448S\"></sup> He will put them to the sword;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19448T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19448T\"></sup> he will show them no mercy or pity or compassion.’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19448U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19448U\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>“Furthermore, tell the people, ‘This is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says: See, I am setting before you the way of life<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19449V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19449V\"></sup> and the way of death.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Whoever stays in this city will die by the sword, famine or plague.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19450W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19450W\"></sup> But whoever goes out and surrenders<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19450X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19450X\"></sup> to the Babylonians who are besieging you will live; they will escape with their lives.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19450Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19450Y\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>I have determined to do this city harm<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19451Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19451Z\"></sup> and not good, declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>. It will be given into the hands<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19451AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19451AA\"></sup> of the king of Babylon, and he will destroy it with fire.’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19451AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19451AB\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>“Moreover, say to the royal house<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19452AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19452AC\"></sup> of Judah, ‘Hear the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>This is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says to you, house of David:“‘Administer justice<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19453AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19453AD\"></sup> every morning;rescue from the hand of the oppressor<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19453AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19453AE\"></sup>the one who has been robbed,or my wrath will break out and burn like fire<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19453AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19453AF\"></sup>because of the evil<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19453AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19453AG\"></sup> you have done—burn with no one to quench<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19453AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19453AH\"></sup> it.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>I am against<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19454AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19454AI\"></sup> you, Jerusalem,you who live above this valley<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19454AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19454AJ\"></sup>on the rocky plateau, declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>—you who say, “Who can come against us?Who can enter our refuge?”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19454AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19454AK\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>I will punish you as your deeds<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19455AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19455AL\"></sup> deserve,declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.I will kindle a fire<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19455AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19455AM\"></sup> in your forests<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19455AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19455AN\"></sup>that will consume everything around you.’”"
		},
		"22": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">22 </span>This is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says: “Go down to the palace of the king<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19456A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19456A\"></sup> of Judah and proclaim this message there:",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>‘Hear<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19457B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19457B\"></sup> the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> to you, king of Judah, you who sit on David’s throne<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19457C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19457C\"></sup>—you, your officials and your people who come through these gates.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19457D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19457D\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>This is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says: Do what is just<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19458E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19458E\"></sup> and right. Rescue from the hand of the oppressor<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19458F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19458F\"></sup> the one who has been robbed. Do no wrong or violence to the foreigner, the fatherless or the widow,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19458G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19458G\"></sup> and do not shed innocent blood<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19458H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19458H\"></sup> in this place.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>For if you are careful to carry out these commands, then kings<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19459I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19459I\"></sup> who sit on David’s throne will come through the gates of this palace, riding in chariots and on horses, accompanied by their officials and their people.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>But if you do not obey<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19460J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19460J\"></sup> these commands, declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, I swear<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19460K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19460K\"></sup> by myself that this palace will become a ruin.’”",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>For this is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says about the palace of the king of Judah:“Though you are like Gilead<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19461L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19461L\"></sup> to me,like the summit of Lebanon,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19461M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19461M\"></sup>I will surely make you like a wasteland,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19461N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19461N\"></sup>like towns not inhabited.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>I will send destroyers<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19462O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19462O\"></sup> against you,each man with his weapons,and they will cut<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19462P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19462P\"></sup> up your fine cedar beamsand throw them into the fire.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19462Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19462Q\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>“People from many nations will pass by this city and will ask one another, ‘Why has the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> done such a thing to this great city?’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19463R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19463R\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>And the answer will be: ‘Because they have forsaken the covenant of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> their God and have worshiped and served other gods.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19464S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19464S\"></sup>’”",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Do not weep for the dead<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19465T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19465T\"></sup> king or mourn<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19465U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19465U\"></sup> his loss;rather, weep bitterly for him who is exiled,because he will never return<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19465V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19465V\"></sup>nor see his native land again.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>For this is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says about Shallum<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19466W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19466W\"></sup> son of Josiah, who succeeded his father as king of Judah but has gone from this place: “He will never return.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>He will die<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19467X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19467X\"></sup> in the place where they have led him captive; he will not see this land again.”",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>“Woe<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19468Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19468Y\"></sup> to him who builds<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19468Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19468Z\"></sup> his palace by unrighteousness,his upper rooms by injustice,making his own people work for nothing,not paying<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19468AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19468AA\"></sup> them for their labor.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>He says, ‘I will build myself a great palace<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19469AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19469AB\"></sup>with spacious upper rooms.’So he makes large windows in it,panels it with cedar<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19469AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19469AC\"></sup>and decorates it in red.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19469AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19469AD\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>“Does it make you a kingto have more and more cedar?Did not your father have food and drink?He did what was right and just,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19470AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19470AE\"></sup>so all went well<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19470AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19470AF\"></sup> with him.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>He defended the cause of the poor and needy,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19471AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19471AG\"></sup>and so all went well.Is that not what it means to know<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19471AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19471AH\"></sup> me?”declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>“But your eyes and your heartare set only on dishonest gain,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19472AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19472AI\"></sup>on shedding innocent blood<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19472AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19472AJ\"></sup>and on oppression and extortion.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19472AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19472AK\"></sup>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Therefore this is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says about Jehoiakim son of Josiah king of Judah:“They will not mourn<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19473AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19473AL\"></sup> for him:‘Alas, my brother! Alas, my sister!’They will not mourn for him:‘Alas, my master! Alas, his splendor!’",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>He will have the burial<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19474AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19474AM\"></sup> of a donkey—dragged away and thrown<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19474AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19474AN\"></sup>outside the gates of Jerusalem.”",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>“Go up to Lebanon and cry out,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19475AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19475AO\"></sup>let your voice be heard in Bashan,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19475AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19475AP\"></sup>cry out from Abarim,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19475AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19475AQ\"></sup>for all your allies<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19475AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19475AR\"></sup> are crushed.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>I warned you when you felt secure,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19476AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19476AS\"></sup>but you said, ‘I will not listen!’This has been your way from your youth;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19476AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19476AT\"></sup>you have not obeyed<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19476AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19476AU\"></sup> me.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>The wind<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19477AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19477AV\"></sup> will drive all your shepherds<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19477AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19477AW\"></sup> away,and your allies<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19477AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19477AX\"></sup> will go into exile.Then you will be ashamed and disgraced<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19477AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19477AY\"></sup>because of all your wickedness.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>You who live in ‘Lebanon,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19478AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19478AZ\"></sup>’who are nestled in cedar buildings,how you will groan when pangs come upon you,pain<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19478BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19478BA\"></sup> like that of a woman in labor!",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>“As surely as I live,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, “even if you, Jehoiachin<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19479BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19479BB\"></sup> son of Jehoiakim king of Judah, were a signet ring<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19479BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19479BC\"></sup> on my right hand, I would still pull you off.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>I will deliver<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19480BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19480BD\"></sup> you into the hands of those who want to kill you, those you fear—Nebuchadnezzar king of Babylon and the Babylonians.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>I will hurl<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19481BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19481BE\"></sup> you and the mother<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19481BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19481BF\"></sup> who gave you birth into another country, where neither of you was born, and there you both will die.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>You will never come back to the land you long to return<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19482BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19482BG\"></sup> to.”",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>Is this man Jehoiachin<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19483BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19483BH\"></sup> a despised, broken pot,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19483BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19483BI\"></sup>an object no one wants?Why will he and his children be hurled<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19483BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19483BJ\"></sup> out,cast into a land<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19483BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19483BK\"></sup> they do not know?",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>O land,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19484BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19484BL\"></sup> land, land,hear the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>!",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>This is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says:“Record this man as if childless,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19485BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19485BM\"></sup>a man who will not prosper<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19485BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19485BN\"></sup> in his lifetime,for none of his offspring<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19485BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19485BO\"></sup> will prosper,none will sit on the throne<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19485BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19485BP\"></sup> of Davidor rule anymore in Judah.”"
		},
		"23": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">23 </span>“Woe to the shepherds<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19486A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19486A\"></sup> who are destroying and scattering<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19486B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19486B\"></sup> the sheep of my pasture!”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19486C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19486C\"></sup> declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Therefore this is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, the God of Israel, says to the shepherds<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19487D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19487D\"></sup> who tend my people: “Because you have scattered my flock<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19487E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19487E\"></sup> and driven them away and have not bestowed care on them, I will bestow punishment on you for the evil<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19487F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19487F\"></sup> you have done,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>“I myself will gather the remnant<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19488G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19488G\"></sup> of my flock out of all the countries where I have driven them and will bring them back to their pasture,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19488H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19488H\"></sup> where they will be fruitful and increase in number.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>I will place shepherds<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19489I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19489I\"></sup> over them who will tend them, and they will no longer be afraid<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19489J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19489J\"></sup> or terrified, nor will any be missing,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19489K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19489K\"></sup>” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>“The days are coming,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,“when I will raise up for David a righteous Branch,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19490L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19490L\"></sup>a King<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19490M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19490M\"></sup> who will reign<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19490N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19490N\"></sup> wiselyand do what is just and right<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19490O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19490O\"></sup> in the land.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>In his days Judah will be savedand Israel will live in safety.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19491P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19491P\"></sup>This is the name<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19491Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19491Q\"></sup> by which he will be called:The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Our Righteous Savior.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19491R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19491R\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>“So then, the days are coming,”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19492S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19492S\"></sup> declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, “when people will no longer say, ‘As surely as the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> lives, who brought the Israelites up out of Egypt,’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19492T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19492T\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>but they will say, ‘As surely as the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> lives, who brought the descendants of Israel up out of the land of the north and out of all the countries where he had banished them.’ Then they will live in their own land.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19493U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19493U\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Concerning the prophets:My heart<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19494V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19494V\"></sup> is broken within me;all my bones tremble.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19494W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19494W\"></sup>I am like a drunken man,like a strong man overcome by wine,because of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>and his holy words.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19494X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19494X\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>The land is full of adulterers;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19495Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19495Y\"></sup>because of the curse<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19495Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19495Z\"></sup> the land lies parchedand the pastures<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19495AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19495AA\"></sup> in the wilderness are withered.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19495AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19495AB\"></sup>The prophets follow an evil courseand use their power unjustly.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>“Both prophet and priest are godless;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19496AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19496AC\"></sup>even in my temple<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19496AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19496AD\"></sup> I find their wickedness,”declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>“Therefore their path will become slippery;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19497AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19497AE\"></sup>they will be banished to darknessand there they will fall.I will bring disaster on themin the year they are punished,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19497AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19497AF\"></sup>”declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>“Among the prophets of SamariaI saw this repulsive thing:They prophesied by Baal<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19498AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19498AG\"></sup>and led my people Israel astray.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19498AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19498AH\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>And among the prophets of JerusalemI have seen something horrible:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19499AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19499AI\"></sup>They commit adultery and live a lie.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19499AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19499AJ\"></sup>They strengthen the hands of evildoers,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19499AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19499AK\"></sup>so that not one of them turns from their wickedness.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19499AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19499AL\"></sup>They are all like Sodom<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19499AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19499AM\"></sup> to me;the people of Jerusalem are like Gomorrah.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19499AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19499AN\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Therefore this is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty says concerning the prophets:“I will make them eat bitter foodand drink poisoned water,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19500AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19500AO\"></sup>because from the prophets of Jerusalemungodliness<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19500AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19500AP\"></sup> has spread throughout the land.”",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>This is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty says:“Do not listen<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19501AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19501AQ\"></sup> to what the prophets are prophesying to you;they fill you with false hopes.They speak visions<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19501AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19501AR\"></sup> from their own minds,not from the mouth<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19501AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19501AS\"></sup> of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>They keep saying<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19502AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19502AT\"></sup> to those who despise me,‘The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says: You will have peace.’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19502AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19502AU\"></sup>And to all who follow the stubbornness<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19502AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19502AV\"></sup> of their heartsthey say, ‘No harm<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19502AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19502AW\"></sup> will come to you.’",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>But which of them has stood in the council<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19503AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19503AX\"></sup> of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>to see or to hear his word?Who has listened and heard his word?",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>See, the storm<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19504AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19504AY\"></sup> of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>will burst out in wrath,a whirlwind<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19504AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19504AZ\"></sup> swirling downon the heads of the wicked.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>The anger<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19505BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19505BA\"></sup> of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will not turn back<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19505BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19505BB\"></sup>until he fully accomplishesthe purposes of his heart.In days to comeyou will understand it clearly.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>I did not send<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19506BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19506BC\"></sup> these prophets,yet they have run with their message;I did not speak to them,yet they have prophesied.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>But if they had stood in my council,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19507BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19507BD\"></sup>they would have proclaimed<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19507BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19507BE\"></sup> my words to my peopleand would have turned<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19507BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19507BF\"></sup> them from their evil waysand from their evil deeds.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19507BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19507BG\"></sup>",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>“Am I only a God nearby,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19508BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19508BH\"></sup>”declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,“and not a God far away?",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>Who can hide<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19509BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19509BI\"></sup> in secret placesso that I cannot see them?”declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.“Do not I fill heaven and earth?”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19509BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19509BJ\"></sup>declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>“I have heard what the prophets say who prophesy lies<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19510BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19510BK\"></sup> in my name. They say, ‘I had a dream!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19510BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19510BL\"></sup> I had a dream!’",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>How long will this continue in the hearts of these lying prophets, who prophesy the delusions<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19511BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19511BM\"></sup> of their own minds?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19511BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19511BN\"></sup>",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>They think the dreams they tell one another will make my people forget<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19512BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19512BO\"></sup> my name, just as their ancestors forgot<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19512BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19512BP\"></sup> my name through Baal worship.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19512BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19512BQ\"></sup>",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>Let the prophet who has a dream<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19513BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19513BR\"></sup> recount the dream, but let the one who has my word<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19513BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19513BS\"></sup> speak it faithfully. For what has straw to do with grain?” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>“Is not my word like fire,”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19514BT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BT&quot;&gt;BT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19514BT\"></sup> declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, “and like a hammer<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19514BU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BU&quot;&gt;BU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19514BU\"></sup> that breaks a rock in pieces?",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>“Therefore,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, “I am against<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19515BV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BV&quot;&gt;BV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19515BV\"></sup> the prophets<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19515BW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BW&quot;&gt;BW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19515BW\"></sup> who steal from one another words supposedly from me.",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>Yes,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, “I am against the prophets who wag their own tongues and yet declare, ‘The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> declares.’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19516BX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BX&quot;&gt;BX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19516BX\"></sup>",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>Indeed, I am against those who prophesy false dreams,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19517BY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BY&quot;&gt;BY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19517BY\"></sup>” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>. “They tell them and lead my people astray<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19517BZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BZ&quot;&gt;BZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19517BZ\"></sup> with their reckless lies,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19517CA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CA&quot;&gt;CA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19517CA\"></sup> yet I did not send<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19517CB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CB&quot;&gt;CB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19517CB\"></sup> or appoint them. They do not benefit<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19517CC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CC&quot;&gt;CC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19517CC\"></sup> these people in the least,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>“When these people, or a prophet or a priest, ask you, ‘What is the message<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19518CD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CD&quot;&gt;CD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19518CD\"></sup> from the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>?’ say to them, ‘What message? I will forsake<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19518CE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CE&quot;&gt;CE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19518CE\"></sup> you, declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.’",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>If a prophet or a priest or anyone else claims, ‘This is a message<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19519CF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CF&quot;&gt;CF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19519CF\"></sup> from the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,’ I will punish<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19519CG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CG&quot;&gt;CG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19519CG\"></sup> them and their household.",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup>This is what each of you keeps saying to your friends and other Israelites: ‘What is the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>’s answer?’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19520CH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CH&quot;&gt;CH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19520CH\"></sup> or ‘What has the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> spoken?’",
			"36": "<sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup>But you must not mention ‘a message from the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>’ again, because each one’s word becomes their own message. So you distort<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19521CI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CI&quot;&gt;CI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19521CI\"></sup> the words of the living God,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19521CJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CJ&quot;&gt;CJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19521CJ\"></sup> the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty, our God.",
			"37": "<sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup>This is what you keep saying to a prophet: ‘What is the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>’s answer to you?’ or ‘What has the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> spoken?’",
			"38": "<sup class=\"versenum\">38 </sup>Although you claim, ‘This is a message from the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,’ this is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says: You used the words, ‘This is a message from the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,’ even though I told you that you must not claim, ‘This is a message from the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.’",
			"39": "<sup class=\"versenum\">39 </sup>Therefore, I will surely forget you and cast<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19524CK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CK&quot;&gt;CK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19524CK\"></sup> you out of my presence along with the city I gave to you and your ancestors.",
			"40": "<sup class=\"versenum\">40 </sup>I will bring on you everlasting disgrace<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19525CL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CL&quot;&gt;CL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19525CL\"></sup>—everlasting shame that will not be forgotten.”"
		},
		"24": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">24 </span>After Jehoiachin<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19526A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19526A\"></sup> son of Jehoiakim king of Judah and the officials, the skilled workers and the artisans of Judah were carried into exile from Jerusalem to Babylon by Nebuchadnezzar king of Babylon, the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> showed me two baskets of figs<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19526B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19526B\"></sup> placed in front of the temple of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>One basket had very good figs, like those that ripen early;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19527C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19527C\"></sup> the other basket had very bad<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19527D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19527D\"></sup> figs, so bad they could not be eaten.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Then the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> asked me, “What do you see,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19528E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19528E\"></sup> Jeremiah?”“Figs,” I answered. “The good ones are very good, but the bad ones are so bad they cannot be eaten.”",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Then the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to me:",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>“This is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, the God of Israel, says: ‘Like these good figs, I regard as good the exiles from Judah, whom I sent<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19530F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19530F\"></sup> away from this place to the land of the Babylonians.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>My eyes will watch over them for their good, and I will bring them back<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19531G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19531G\"></sup> to this land. I will build<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19531H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19531H\"></sup> them up and not tear them down; I will plant<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19531I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19531I\"></sup> them and not uproot them.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>I will give them a heart to know<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19532J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19532J\"></sup> me, that I am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>. They will be my people,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19532K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19532K\"></sup> and I will be their God, for they will return<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19532L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19532L\"></sup> to me with all their heart.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19532M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19532M\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>“‘But like the bad<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19533N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19533N\"></sup> figs, which are so bad they cannot be eaten,’ says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, ‘so will I deal with Zedekiah<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19533O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19533O\"></sup> king of Judah, his officials<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19533P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19533P\"></sup> and the survivors<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19533Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19533Q\"></sup> from Jerusalem, whether they remain in this land or live in Egypt.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19533R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19533R\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>I will make them abhorrent<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19534S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19534S\"></sup> and an offense to all the kingdoms of the earth, a reproach and a byword,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19534T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19534T\"></sup> a curse<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19534U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19534U\"></sup> and an object of ridicule, wherever I banish<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19534V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19534V\"></sup> them.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>I will send the sword,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19535W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19535W\"></sup> famine<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19535X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19535X\"></sup> and plague<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19535Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19535Y\"></sup> against them until they are destroyed from the land I gave to them and their ancestors.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19535Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19535Z\"></sup>’”"
		},
		"25": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">25 </span>The word came to Jeremiah concerning all the people of Judah in the fourth year of Jehoiakim<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19536A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19536A\"></sup> son of Josiah king of Judah, which was the first year of Nebuchadnezzar<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19536B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19536B\"></sup> king of Babylon.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>So Jeremiah the prophet said to all the people of Judah<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19537C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19537C\"></sup> and to all those living in Jerusalem:",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>For twenty-three years—from the thirteenth year of Josiah<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19538D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19538D\"></sup> son of Amon king of Judah until this very day—the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has come to me and I have spoken to you again and again,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19538E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19538E\"></sup> but you have not listened.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19538F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19538F\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>And though the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has sent all his servants the prophets<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19539G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19539G\"></sup> to you again and again, you have not listened or paid any attention.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19539H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19539H\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>They said, “Turn<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19540I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19540I\"></sup> now, each of you, from your evil ways and your evil practices, and you can stay in the land<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19540J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19540J\"></sup> the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> gave to you and your ancestors for ever and ever.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Do not follow other gods<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19541K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19541K\"></sup> to serve and worship them; do not arouse my anger with what your hands have made. Then I will not harm you.”",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>“But you did not listen to me,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, “and you have aroused<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19542L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19542L\"></sup> my anger with what your hands have made,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19542M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19542M\"></sup> and you have brought harm<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19542N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19542N\"></sup> to yourselves.”",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Therefore the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty says this: “Because you have not listened to my words,",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>I will summon<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19544O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19544O\"></sup> all the peoples of the north<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19544P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19544P\"></sup> and my servant<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19544Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19544Q\"></sup> Nebuchadnezzar<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19544R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19544R\"></sup> king of Babylon,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, “and I will bring them against this land and its inhabitants and against all the surrounding nations. I will completely destroy<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19544S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19544S\"></sup> them and make them an object of horror and scorn,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19544T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19544T\"></sup> and an everlasting ruin.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19544U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19544U\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>I will banish from them the sounds<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19545V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19545V\"></sup> of joy and gladness, the voices of bride and bridegroom,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19545W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19545W\"></sup> the sound of millstones<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19545X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19545X\"></sup> and the light of the lamp.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19545Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19545Y\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>This whole country will become a desolate wasteland,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19546Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19546Z\"></sup> and these nations will serve<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19546AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19546AA\"></sup> the king of Babylon seventy years.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19546AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19546AB\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>“But when the seventy years<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19547AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19547AC\"></sup> are fulfilled, I will punish the king of Babylon<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19547AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19547AD\"></sup> and his nation, the land of the Babylonians, for their guilt,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, “and will make it desolate<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19547AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19547AE\"></sup> forever.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>I will bring on that land all the things I have spoken against it, all that are written<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19548AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19548AF\"></sup> in this book and prophesied by Jeremiah against all the nations.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>They themselves will be enslaved<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19549AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19549AG\"></sup> by many nations<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19549AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19549AH\"></sup> and great kings; I will repay<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19549AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19549AI\"></sup> them according to their deeds and the work of their hands.”",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>This is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, the God of Israel, said to me: “Take from my hand this cup<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19550AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19550AJ\"></sup> filled with the wine of my wrath and make all the nations to whom I send<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19550AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19550AK\"></sup> you drink it.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>When they drink<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19551AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19551AL\"></sup> it, they will stagger<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19551AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19551AM\"></sup> and go mad<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19551AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19551AN\"></sup> because of the sword<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19551AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19551AO\"></sup> I will send among them.”",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>So I took the cup from the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>’s hand and made all the nations to whom he sent<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19552AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19552AP\"></sup> me drink it:",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Jerusalem<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19553AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19553AQ\"></sup> and the towns of Judah, its kings and officials, to make them a ruin<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19553AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19553AR\"></sup> and an object of horror and scorn,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19553AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19553AS\"></sup> a curse<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19553AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19553AT\"></sup>—as they are today;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19553AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19553AU\"></sup>",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>Pharaoh king<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19554AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19554AV\"></sup> of Egypt,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19554AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19554AW\"></sup> his attendants, his officials and all his people,",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>and all the foreign people there; all the kings of Uz;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19555AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19555AX\"></sup> all the kings of the Philistines<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19555AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19555AY\"></sup> (those of Ashkelon,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19555AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19555AZ\"></sup> Gaza,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19555BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19555BA\"></sup> Ekron, and the people left at Ashdod);",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>Edom,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19556BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19556BB\"></sup> Moab<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19556BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19556BC\"></sup> and Ammon;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19556BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19556BD\"></sup>",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>all the kings of Tyre<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19557BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19557BE\"></sup> and Sidon;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19557BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19557BF\"></sup> the kings of the coastlands<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19557BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19557BG\"></sup> across the sea;",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>Dedan,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19558BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19558BH\"></sup> Tema,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19558BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19558BI\"></sup> Buz<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19558BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19558BJ\"></sup> and all who are in distant places;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19558BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19558BK\"></sup>",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>all the kings of Arabia<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19559BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19559BL\"></sup> and all the kings of the foreign people<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19559BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19559BM\"></sup> who live in the wilderness;",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>all the kings of Zimri,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19560BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19560BN\"></sup> Elam<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19560BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19560BO\"></sup> and Media;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19560BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19560BP\"></sup>",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>and all the kings of the north,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19561BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19561BQ\"></sup> near and far, one after the other—all the kingdoms<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19561BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19561BR\"></sup> on the face of the earth. And after all of them, the king of Sheshak<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19561BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19561BS\"></sup> will drink it too.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>“Then tell them, ‘This is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty, the God of Israel, says: Drink, get drunk<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19562BT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BT&quot;&gt;BT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19562BT\"></sup> and vomit, and fall to rise no more because of the sword<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19562BU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BU&quot;&gt;BU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19562BU\"></sup> I will send among you.’",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>But if they refuse to take the cup from your hand and drink<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19563BV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BV&quot;&gt;BV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19563BV\"></sup>, tell them, ‘This is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty says: You must drink it!",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>See, I am beginning to bring disaster<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19564BW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BW&quot;&gt;BW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19564BW\"></sup> on the city that bears my Name,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19564BX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BX&quot;&gt;BX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19564BX\"></sup> and will you indeed go unpunished?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19564BY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BY&quot;&gt;BY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19564BY\"></sup> You will not go unpunished, for I am calling down a sword<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19564BZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BZ&quot;&gt;BZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19564BZ\"></sup> on all<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19564CA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CA&quot;&gt;CA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19564CA\"></sup> who live on the earth,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19564CB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CB&quot;&gt;CB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19564CB\"></sup> declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty.’",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>“Now prophesy all these words against them and say to them:“‘The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will roar<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19565CC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CC&quot;&gt;CC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19565CC\"></sup> from on high;he will thunder<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19565CD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CD&quot;&gt;CD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19565CD\"></sup> from his holy dwelling<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19565CE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CE&quot;&gt;CE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19565CE\"></sup>and roar mightily against his land.He will shout like those who tread<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19565CF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CF&quot;&gt;CF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19565CF\"></sup> the grapes,shout against all who live on the earth.",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>The tumult<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19566CG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CG&quot;&gt;CG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19566CG\"></sup> will resound to the ends of the earth,for the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will bring charges<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19566CH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CH&quot;&gt;CH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19566CH\"></sup> against the nations;he will bring judgment<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19566CI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CI&quot;&gt;CI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19566CI\"></sup> on all<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19566CJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CJ&quot;&gt;CJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19566CJ\"></sup> mankindand put the wicked to the sword,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19566CK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CK&quot;&gt;CK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19566CK\"></sup>’”declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>This is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty says:“Look! Disaster<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19567CL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CL&quot;&gt;CL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19567CL\"></sup> is spreadingfrom nation to nation;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19567CM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CM&quot;&gt;CM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19567CM\"></sup>a mighty storm<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19567CN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CN&quot;&gt;CN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19567CN\"></sup> is risingfrom the ends of the earth.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19567CO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CO&quot;&gt;CO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19567CO\"></sup>",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>At that time those slain<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19568CP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CP&quot;&gt;CP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19568CP\"></sup> by the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will be everywhere—from one end of the earth to the other. They will not be mourned or gathered<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19568CQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CQ&quot;&gt;CQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19568CQ\"></sup> up or buried,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19568CR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CR&quot;&gt;CR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19568CR\"></sup> but will be like dung lying on the ground.",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>Weep and wail, you shepherds;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19569CS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CS&quot;&gt;CS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19569CS\"></sup>roll<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19569CT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CT&quot;&gt;CT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19569CT\"></sup> in the dust, you leaders of the flock.For your time to be slaughtered<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19569CU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CU&quot;&gt;CU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19569CU\"></sup> has come;you will fall like the best of the rams.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19569CV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CV&quot;&gt;CV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19569CV\"></sup>",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup>The shepherds will have nowhere to flee,the leaders of the flock no place to escape.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19570CW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CW&quot;&gt;CW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19570CW\"></sup>",
			"36": "<sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup>Hear the cry<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19571CX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CX&quot;&gt;CX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19571CX\"></sup> of the shepherds,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19571CY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CY&quot;&gt;CY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19571CY\"></sup>the wailing of the leaders of the flock,for the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> is destroying their pasture.",
			"37": "<sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup>The peaceful meadows will be laid wastebecause of the fierce anger of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"38": "<sup class=\"versenum\">38 </sup>Like a lion<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19573CZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CZ&quot;&gt;CZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19573CZ\"></sup> he will leave his lair,and their land will become desolate<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19573DA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DA&quot;&gt;DA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19573DA\"></sup>because of the sword of the oppressor<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19573DB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DB&quot;&gt;DB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19573DB\"></sup>and because of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>’s fierce anger.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19573DC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DC&quot;&gt;DC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19573DC\"></sup>"
		},
		"26": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">26 </span>Early in the reign of Jehoiakim<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19574A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19574A\"></sup> son of Josiah king of Judah, this word came from the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>:",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“This is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says: Stand in the courtyard<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19575B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19575B\"></sup> of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>’s house and speak to all the people of the towns of Judah who come to worship in the house of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19575C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19575C\"></sup> Tell<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19575D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19575D\"></sup> them everything I command you; do not omit<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19575E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19575E\"></sup> a word.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Perhaps they will listen and each will turn<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19576F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19576F\"></sup> from their evil ways. Then I will relent<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19576G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19576G\"></sup> and not inflict on them the disaster I was planning because of the evil they have done.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Say to them, ‘This is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says: If you do not listen<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19577H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19577H\"></sup> to me and follow my law,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19577I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19577I\"></sup> which I have set before you,",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>and if you do not listen to the words of my servants the prophets, whom I have sent to you again and again (though you have not listened<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19578J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19578J\"></sup>),",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>then I will make this house like Shiloh<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19579K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19579K\"></sup> and this city a curse<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19579L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19579L\"></sup> among all the nations of the earth.’”",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>The priests, the prophets and all the people heard Jeremiah speak these words in the house of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>But as soon as Jeremiah finished telling all the people everything the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> had commanded<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19581M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19581M\"></sup> him to say, the priests, the prophets and all the people seized<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19581N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19581N\"></sup> him and said, “You must die!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19581O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19581O\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Why do you prophesy in the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>’s name that this house will be like Shiloh and this city will be desolate and deserted?”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19582P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19582P\"></sup> And all the people crowded<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19582Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19582Q\"></sup> around Jeremiah in the house of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>When the officials<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19583R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19583R\"></sup> of Judah heard about these things, they went up from the royal palace to the house of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> and took their places at the entrance of the New Gate<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19583S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19583S\"></sup> of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>’s house.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Then the priests and the prophets said to the officials and all the people, “This man should be sentenced to death<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19584T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19584T\"></sup> because he has prophesied against this city. You have heard it with your own ears!”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19584U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19584U\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Then Jeremiah said to all the officials<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19585V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19585V\"></sup> and all the people: “The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> sent me to prophesy<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19585W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19585W\"></sup> against this house and this city all the things you have heard.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19585X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19585X\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Now reform<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19586Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19586Y\"></sup> your ways and your actions and obey<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19586Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19586Z\"></sup> the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God. Then the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will relent<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19586AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19586AA\"></sup> and not bring the disaster he has pronounced against you.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>As for me, I am in your hands;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19587AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19587AB\"></sup> do with me whatever you think is good and right.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Be assured, however, that if you put me to death, you will bring the guilt of innocent blood<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19588AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19588AC\"></sup> on yourselves and on this city and on those who live in it, for in truth the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has sent me to you to speak all these words<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19588AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19588AD\"></sup> in your hearing.”",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Then the officials<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19589AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19589AE\"></sup> and all the people said to the priests and the prophets, “This man should not be sentenced to death!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19589AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19589AF\"></sup> He has spoken to us in the name of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> our God.”",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Some of the elders of the land stepped forward and said to the entire assembly of people,",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>“Micah<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19591AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19591AG\"></sup> of Moresheth prophesied in the days of Hezekiah king of Judah. He told all the people of Judah, ‘This is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty says:“‘Zion<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19591AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19591AH\"></sup> will be plowed like a field,Jerusalem will become a heap of rubble,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19591AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19591AI\"></sup>the temple hill<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19591AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19591AJ\"></sup> a mound overgrown with thickets.’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19591AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19591AK\"></sup>",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>“Did Hezekiah king of Judah or anyone else in Judah put him to death? Did not Hezekiah<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19592AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19592AL\"></sup> fear the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> and seek<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19592AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19592AM\"></sup> his favor? And did not the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> relent,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19592AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19592AN\"></sup> so that he did not bring the disaster<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19592AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19592AO\"></sup> he pronounced against them? We are about to bring a terrible disaster<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19592AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19592AP\"></sup> on ourselves!”",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>(Now Uriah son of Shemaiah from Kiriath Jearim<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19593AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19593AQ\"></sup> was another man who prophesied in the name of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>; he prophesied the same things against this city and this land as Jeremiah did.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>When King Jehoiakim<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19594AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19594AR\"></sup> and all his officers and officials<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19594AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19594AS\"></sup> heard his words, the king was determined to put him to death.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19594AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19594AT\"></sup> But Uriah heard of it and fled<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19594AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19594AU\"></sup> in fear to Egypt.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>King Jehoiakim, however, sent Elnathan<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19595AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19595AV\"></sup> son of Akbor to Egypt, along with some other men.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>They brought Uriah out of Egypt and took him to King Jehoiakim, who had him struck down with a sword<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19596AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19596AW\"></sup> and his body thrown into the burial place of the common people.)<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19596AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19596AX\"></sup>",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>Furthermore, Ahikam<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19597AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19597AY\"></sup> son of Shaphan supported Jeremiah, and so he was not handed over to the people to be put to death."
		},
		"27": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">27 </span>Early in the reign of Zedekiah<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19598A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19598A\"></sup> son of Josiah king of Judah, this word came to Jeremiah from the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>:",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>This is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> said to me: “Make a yoke<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19599B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19599B\"></sup> out of straps and crossbars and put it on your neck.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Then send<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19600C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19600C\"></sup> word to the kings of Edom, Moab, Ammon,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19600D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19600D\"></sup> Tyre and Sidon<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19600E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19600E\"></sup> through the envoys who have come to Jerusalem to Zedekiah king of Judah.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Give them a message for their masters and say, ‘This is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty, the God of Israel, says: “Tell this to your masters:",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>With my great power and outstretched arm<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19602F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19602F\"></sup> I made<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19602G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19602G\"></sup> the earth and its people and the animals<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19602H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19602H\"></sup> that are on it, and I give<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19602I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19602I\"></sup> it to anyone I please.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Now I will give all your countries into the hands of my servant<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19603J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19603J\"></sup> Nebuchadnezzar<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19603K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19603K\"></sup> king of Babylon; I will make even the wild animals subject to him.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19603L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19603L\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>All nations will serve<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19604M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19604M\"></sup> him and his son and his grandson until the time<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19604N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19604N\"></sup> for his land comes; then many nations and great kings will subjugate<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19604O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19604O\"></sup> him.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>“‘“If, however, any nation or kingdom will not serve Nebuchadnezzar king of Babylon or bow its neck under his yoke, I will punish<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19605P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19605P\"></sup> that nation with the sword,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19605Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19605Q\"></sup> famine<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19605R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19605R\"></sup> and plague,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19605S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19605S\"></sup> declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, until I destroy it by his hand.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>So do not listen to your prophets,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19606T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19606T\"></sup> your diviners,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19606U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19606U\"></sup> your interpreters of dreams,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19606V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19606V\"></sup> your mediums<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19606W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19606W\"></sup> or your sorcerers<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19606X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19606X\"></sup> who tell you, ‘You will not serve<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19606Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19606Y\"></sup> the king of Babylon.’",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>They prophesy lies<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19607Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19607Z\"></sup> to you that will only serve to remove<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19607AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19607AA\"></sup> you far from your lands; I will banish you and you will perish.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>But if any nation will bow its neck under the yoke<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19608AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19608AB\"></sup> of the king of Babylon and serve him, I will let that nation remain in its own land to till it and to live<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19608AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19608AC\"></sup> there, declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.”’”",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>I gave the same message to Zedekiah king of Judah. I said, “Bow your neck under the yoke<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19609AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19609AD\"></sup> of the king of Babylon; serve him and his people, and you will live.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19609AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19609AE\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Why will you and your people die<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19610AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19610AF\"></sup> by the sword, famine and plague<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19610AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19610AG\"></sup> with which the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has threatened any nation that will not serve the king of Babylon?",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Do not listen<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19611AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19611AH\"></sup> to the words of the prophets<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19611AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19611AI\"></sup> who say to you, ‘You will not serve the king of Babylon,’ for they are prophesying lies<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19611AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19611AJ\"></sup> to you.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>‘I have not sent<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19612AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19612AK\"></sup> them,’ declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>. ‘They are prophesying lies in my name.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19612AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19612AL\"></sup> Therefore, I will banish you and you will perish,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19612AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19612AM\"></sup> both you and the prophets who prophesy to you.’”",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Then I said to the priests and all these people, “This is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says: Do not listen to the prophets who say, ‘Very soon now the articles<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19613AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19613AN\"></sup> from the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>’s house will be brought back from Babylon.’ They are prophesying lies to you.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Do not listen<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19614AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19614AO\"></sup> to them. Serve the king of Babylon, and you will live.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19614AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19614AP\"></sup> Why should this city become a ruin?",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>If they are prophets and have the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, let them plead<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19615AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19615AQ\"></sup> with the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty that the articles remaining in the house of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> and in the palace of the king of Judah and in Jerusalem not be taken to Babylon.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>For this is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty says about the pillars, the bronze Sea,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19616AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19616AR\"></sup> the movable stands and the other articles<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19616AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19616AS\"></sup> that are left in this city,",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>which Nebuchadnezzar king of Babylon did not take away when he carried<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19617AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19617AT\"></sup> Jehoiachin<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19617AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19617AU\"></sup> son of Jehoiakim king of Judah into exile from Jerusalem to Babylon, along with all the nobles of Judah and Jerusalem—",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>yes, this is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty, the God of Israel, says about the things that are left in the house of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> and in the palace of the king of Judah and in Jerusalem:",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>‘They will be taken<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19619AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19619AV\"></sup> to Babylon and there they will remain until the day<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19619AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19619AW\"></sup> I come for them,’ declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>. ‘Then I will bring<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19619AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19619AX\"></sup> them back and restore them to this place.’”"
		},
		"28": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">28 </span>In the fifth month of that same year, the fourth year, early in the reign of Zedekiah<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19620A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19620A\"></sup> king of Judah, the prophet Hananiah son of Azzur, who was from Gibeon,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19620B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19620B\"></sup> said to me in the house of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> in the presence of the priests and all the people:",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“This is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty, the God of Israel, says: ‘I will break the yoke<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19621C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19621C\"></sup> of the king of Babylon.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Within two years I will bring back to this place all the articles<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19622D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19622D\"></sup> of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>’s house that Nebuchadnezzar king of Babylon removed from here and took to Babylon.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>I will also bring back to this place Jehoiachin<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19623E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19623E\"></sup> son of Jehoiakim king of Judah and all the other exiles from Judah who went to Babylon,’ declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, ‘for I will break the yoke of the king of Babylon.’”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19623F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19623F\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Then the prophet Jeremiah replied to the prophet Hananiah before the priests and all the people who were standing in the house of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>He said, “Amen! May the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> do so! May the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> fulfill the words you have prophesied by bringing the articles of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>’s house and all the exiles back to this place from Babylon.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19625G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19625G\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Nevertheless, listen to what I have to say in your hearing and in the hearing of all the people:",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>From early times the prophets who preceded you and me have prophesied war, disaster and plague<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19627H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19627H\"></sup> against many countries and great kingdoms.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>But the prophet who prophesies peace will be recognized as one truly sent by the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> only if his prediction comes true.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19628I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19628I\"></sup>”",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Then the prophet Hananiah took the yoke<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19629J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19629J\"></sup> off the neck of the prophet Jeremiah and broke it,",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>and he said<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19630K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19630K\"></sup> before all the people, “This is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says: ‘In the same way I will break the yoke of Nebuchadnezzar king of Babylon off the neck of all the nations within two years.’” At this, the prophet Jeremiah went on his way.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>After the prophet Hananiah had broken the yoke off the neck of the prophet Jeremiah, the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to Jeremiah:",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>“Go and tell Hananiah, ‘This is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says: You have broken a wooden yoke, but in its place you will get a yoke of iron.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>This is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty, the God of Israel, says: I will put an iron yoke<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19633L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19633L\"></sup> on the necks of all these nations to make them serve<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19633M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19633M\"></sup> Nebuchadnezzar<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19633N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19633N\"></sup> king of Babylon, and they will serve him. I will even give him control over the wild animals.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19633O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19633O\"></sup>’”",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Then the prophet Jeremiah said to Hananiah the prophet, “Listen, Hananiah! The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has not sent<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19634P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19634P\"></sup> you, yet you have persuaded this nation to trust in lies.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19634Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19634Q\"></sup>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Therefore this is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says: ‘I am about to remove you from the face of the earth.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19635R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19635R\"></sup> This very year you are going to die,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19635S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19635S\"></sup> because you have preached rebellion<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19635T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19635T\"></sup> against the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.’”",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>In the seventh month of that same year, Hananiah the prophet died.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19636U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19636U\"></sup>"
		},
		"29": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">29 </span>This is the text of the letter<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19637A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19637A\"></sup> that the prophet Jeremiah sent from Jerusalem to the surviving elders among the exiles and to the priests, the prophets and all the other people Nebuchadnezzar had carried into exile from Jerusalem to Babylon.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19637B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19637B\"></sup>",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>(This was after King Jehoiachin<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19638C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19638C\"></sup> and the queen mother,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19638D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19638D\"></sup> the court officials and the leaders of Judah and Jerusalem, the skilled workers and the artisans had gone into exile from Jerusalem.)",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>He entrusted the letter to Elasah son of Shaphan and to Gemariah son of Hilkiah, whom Zedekiah king of Judah sent to King Nebuchadnezzar in Babylon. It said:",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>This is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty, the God of Israel, says to all those I carried<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19640E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19640E\"></sup> into exile from Jerusalem to Babylon:",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>“Build<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19641F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19641F\"></sup> houses and settle down; plant gardens and eat what they produce.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Marry and have sons and daughters; find wives for your sons and give your daughters in marriage, so that they too may have sons and daughters. Increase in number there; do not decrease.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19642G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19642G\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Also, seek<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19643H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19643H\"></sup> the peace and prosperity of the city to which I have carried you into exile. Pray<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19643I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19643I\"></sup> to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> for it, because if it prospers, you too will prosper.”",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Yes, this is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty, the God of Israel, says: “Do not let the prophets<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19644J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19644J\"></sup> and diviners among you deceive<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19644K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19644K\"></sup> you. Do not listen to the dreams<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19644L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19644L\"></sup> you encourage them to have.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19644M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19644M\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>They are prophesying lies<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19645N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19645N\"></sup> to you in my name. I have not sent<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19645O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19645O\"></sup> them,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>This is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says: “When seventy years<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19646P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19646P\"></sup> are completed for Babylon, I will come to you<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19646Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19646Q\"></sup> and fulfill my good promise<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19646R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19646R\"></sup> to bring you back<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19646S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19646S\"></sup> to this place.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>For I know the plans<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19647T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19647T\"></sup> I have for you,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, “plans to prosper<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19647U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19647U\"></sup> you and not to harm you, plans to give you hope and a future.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19647V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19647V\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Then you will call<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19648W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19648W\"></sup> on me and come and pray<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19648X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19648X\"></sup> to me, and I will listen<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19648Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19648Y\"></sup> to you.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>You will seek<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19649Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19649Z\"></sup> me and find me when you seek me with all your heart.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19649AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19649AA\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>I will be found by you,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, “and will bring you back<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19650AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19650AB\"></sup> from captivity. I will gather you from all the nations and places where I have banished you,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, “and will bring you back to the place from which I carried you into exile.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19650AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19650AC\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>You may say, “The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has raised up prophets for us in Babylon,”",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>but this is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says about the king who sits on David’s throne and all the people who remain in this city, your fellow citizens who did not go with you into exile—",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>yes, this is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty says: “I will send the sword, famine and plague<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19653AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19653AD\"></sup> against them and I will make them like figs<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19653AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19653AE\"></sup> that are so bad they cannot be eaten.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>I will pursue them with the sword, famine and plague and will make them abhorrent<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19654AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19654AF\"></sup> to all the kingdoms of the earth, a curse<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19654AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19654AG\"></sup> and an object of horror,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19654AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19654AH\"></sup> of scorn<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19654AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19654AI\"></sup> and reproach, among all the nations where I drive them.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>For they have not listened to my words,”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19655AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19655AJ\"></sup> declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, “words that I sent to them again and again<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19655AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19655AK\"></sup> by my servants the prophets.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19655AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19655AL\"></sup> And you exiles have not listened either,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Therefore, hear the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, all you exiles whom I have sent<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19656AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19656AM\"></sup> away from Jerusalem to Babylon.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>This is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty, the God of Israel, says about Ahab son of Kolaiah and Zedekiah son of Maaseiah, who are prophesying lies<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19657AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19657AN\"></sup> to you in my name: “I will deliver them into the hands of Nebuchadnezzar king of Babylon, and he will put them to death before your very eyes.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Because of them, all the exiles from Judah who are in Babylon will use this curse: ‘May the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> treat you like Zedekiah and Ahab, whom the king of Babylon burned<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19658AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19658AO\"></sup> in the fire.’",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>For they have done outrageous things in Israel; they have committed adultery<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19659AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19659AP\"></sup> with their neighbors’ wives, and in my name they have uttered lies—which I did not authorize. I know<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19659AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19659AQ\"></sup> it and am a witness<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19659AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19659AR\"></sup> to it,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>Tell Shemaiah the Nehelamite,",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>“This is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty, the God of Israel, says: You sent letters in your own name to all the people in Jerusalem, to the priest Zephaniah<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19661AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19661AS\"></sup> son of Maaseiah, and to all the other priests. You said to Zephaniah,",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>‘The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has appointed you priest in place of Jehoiada to be in charge of the house of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>; you should put any maniac<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19662AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19662AT\"></sup> who acts like a prophet into the stocks<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19662AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19662AU\"></sup> and neck-irons.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>So why have you not reprimanded Jeremiah from Anathoth, who poses as a prophet among you?",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>He has sent this message<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19664AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19664AV\"></sup> to us in Babylon: It will be a long time.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19664AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19664AW\"></sup> Therefore build<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19664AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19664AX\"></sup> houses and settle down; plant gardens and eat what they produce.’”",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>Zephaniah<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19665AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19665AY\"></sup> the priest, however, read the letter to Jeremiah the prophet.",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>Then the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to Jeremiah:",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>“Send this message to all the exiles: ‘This is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says about Shemaiah<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19667AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19667AZ\"></sup> the Nehelamite: Because Shemaiah has prophesied to you, even though I did not send<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19667BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19667BA\"></sup> him, and has persuaded you to trust in lies,",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>this is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says: I will surely punish Shemaiah the Nehelamite and his descendants.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19668BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19668BB\"></sup> He will have no one left among this people, nor will he see the good<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19668BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19668BC\"></sup> things I will do for my people, declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, because he has preached rebellion<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19668BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19668BD\"></sup> against me.’”"
		},
		"30": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">30 </span>This is the word that came to Jeremiah from the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>:",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“This is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, the God of Israel, says: ‘Write<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19670A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19670A\"></sup> in a book all the words I have spoken to you.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>The days<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19671B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19671B\"></sup> are coming,’ declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, ‘when I will bring<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19671C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19671C\"></sup> my people Israel and Judah back from captivity and restore<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19671D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19671D\"></sup> them to the land I gave their ancestors to possess,’ says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.”",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>These are the words the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> spoke concerning Israel and Judah:",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>“This is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says:“‘Cries of fear<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19673E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19673E\"></sup> are heard—terror, not peace.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Ask and see:Can a man bear children?Then why do I see every strong manwith his hands on his stomach like a woman in labor,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19674F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19674F\"></sup>every face turned deathly pale?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19674G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19674G\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>How awful that day<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19675H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19675H\"></sup> will be!No other will be like it.It will be a time of trouble<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19675I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19675I\"></sup> for Jacob,but he will be saved<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19675J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19675J\"></sup> out of it.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>“‘In that day,’ declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty,‘I will break the yoke<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19676K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19676K\"></sup> off their necksand will tear off their bonds;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19676L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19676L\"></sup>no longer will foreigners enslave them.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19676M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19676M\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Instead, they will serve the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> their Godand David<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19677N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19677N\"></sup> their king,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19677O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19677O\"></sup>whom I will raise up for them.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>“‘So do not be afraid,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19678P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19678P\"></sup> Jacob my servant;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19678Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19678Q\"></sup>do not be dismayed, Israel,’declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.‘I will surely save<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19678R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19678R\"></sup> you out of a distant place,your descendants from the land of their exile.Jacob will again have peace and security,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19678S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19678S\"></sup>and no one will make him afraid.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19678T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19678T\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>I am with you<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19679U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19679U\"></sup> and will save you,’declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.‘Though I completely destroy all the nationsamong which I scatter you,I will not completely destroy<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19679V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19679V\"></sup> you.I will discipline<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19679W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19679W\"></sup> you but only in due measure;I will not let you go entirely unpunished.’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19679X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19679X\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>“This is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says:“‘Your wound<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19680Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19680Y\"></sup> is incurable,your injury beyond healing.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19680Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19680Z\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>There is no one to plead your cause,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19681AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19681AA\"></sup>no remedy for your sore,no healing<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19681AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19681AB\"></sup> for you.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>All your allies<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19682AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19682AC\"></sup> have forgotten you;they care nothing for you.I have struck you as an enemy<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19682AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19682AD\"></sup> wouldand punished you as would the cruel,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19682AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19682AE\"></sup>because your guilt is so greatand your sins<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19682AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19682AF\"></sup> so many.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Why do you cry out over your wound,your pain that has no cure?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19683AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19683AG\"></sup>Because of your great guilt and many sinsI have done these things to you.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19683AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19683AH\"></sup>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>“‘But all who devour<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19684AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19684AI\"></sup> you will be devoured;all your enemies will go into exile.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19684AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19684AJ\"></sup>Those who plunder<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19684AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19684AK\"></sup> you will be plundered;all who make spoil of you I will despoil.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>But I will restore you to healthand heal<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19685AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19685AL\"></sup> your wounds,’declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,‘because you are called an outcast,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19685AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19685AM\"></sup>Zion for whom no one cares.’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19685AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19685AN\"></sup>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>“This is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says:“‘I will restore the fortunes<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19686AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19686AO\"></sup> of Jacob’s tents<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19686AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19686AP\"></sup>and have compassion<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19686AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19686AQ\"></sup> on his dwellings;the city will be rebuilt<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19686AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19686AR\"></sup> on her ruins,and the palace will stand in its proper place.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>From them will come songs<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19687AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19687AS\"></sup> of thanksgiving<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19687AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19687AT\"></sup>and the sound of rejoicing.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19687AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19687AU\"></sup>I will add to their numbers,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19687AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19687AV\"></sup>and they will not be decreased;I will bring them honor,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19687AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19687AW\"></sup>and they will not be disdained.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Their children<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19688AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19688AX\"></sup> will be as in days of old,and their community will be established<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19688AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19688AY\"></sup> before me;I will punish<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19688AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19688AZ\"></sup> all who oppress them.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>Their leader<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19689BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19689BA\"></sup> will be one of their own;their ruler will arise from among them.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19689BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19689BB\"></sup>I will bring him near<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19689BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19689BC\"></sup> and he will come close to me—for who is he who will devote himselfto be close to me?’declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>“‘So you will be my people,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19690BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19690BD\"></sup>and I will be your God.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19690BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19690BE\"></sup>’”",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>See, the storm<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19691BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19691BF\"></sup> of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>will burst out in wrath,a driving wind swirling downon the heads of the wicked.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>The fierce anger<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19692BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19692BG\"></sup> of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will not turn back<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19692BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19692BH\"></sup>until he fully accomplishesthe purposes of his heart.In days to comeyou will understand<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19692BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19692BI\"></sup> this."
		},
		"31": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">31 </span>“At that time,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, “I will be the God<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19693A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19693A\"></sup> of all the families of Israel, and they will be my people.”",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>This is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says:“The people who survive the swordwill find favor<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19694B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19694B\"></sup> in the wilderness;I will come to give rest<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19694C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19694C\"></sup> to Israel.”",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> appeared to us in the past, saying:“I have loved<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19695D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19695D\"></sup> you with an everlasting love;I have drawn<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19695E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19695E\"></sup> you with unfailing kindness.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>I will build you up again,and you, Virgin<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19696F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19696F\"></sup> Israel, will be rebuilt.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19696G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19696G\"></sup>Again you will take up your timbrels<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19696H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19696H\"></sup>and go out to dance<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19696I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19696I\"></sup> with the joyful.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19696J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19696J\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Again you will plant<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19697K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19697K\"></sup> vineyardson the hills of Samaria;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19697L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19697L\"></sup>the farmers will plant themand enjoy their fruit.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19697M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19697M\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>There will be a day when watchmen<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19698N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19698N\"></sup> cry outon the hills of Ephraim,‘Come, let us go up to Zion,to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> our God.’”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19698O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19698O\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>This is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says:“Sing<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19699P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19699P\"></sup> with joy for Jacob;shout for the foremost<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19699Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19699Q\"></sup> of the nations.Make your praises heard, and say,‘<span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, save<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19699R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19699R\"></sup> your people,the remnant<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19699S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19699S\"></sup> of Israel.’",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>See, I will bring them from the land of the north<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19700T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19700T\"></sup>and gather<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19700U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19700U\"></sup> them from the ends of the earth.Among them will be the blind<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19700V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19700V\"></sup> and the lame,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19700W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19700W\"></sup>expectant mothers and women in labor;a great throng will return.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>They will come with weeping;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19701X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19701X\"></sup>they will pray as I bring them back.I will lead<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19701Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19701Y\"></sup> them beside streams of water<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19701Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19701Z\"></sup>on a level<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19701AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19701AA\"></sup> path where they will not stumble,because I am Israel’s father,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19701AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19701AB\"></sup>and Ephraim is my firstborn son.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>“Hear the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, you nations;proclaim it in distant coastlands:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19702AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19702AC\"></sup>‘He who scattered<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19702AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19702AD\"></sup> Israel will gather<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19702AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19702AE\"></sup> themand will watch over his flock like a shepherd.’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19702AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19702AF\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>For the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will deliver Jacoband redeem<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19703AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19703AG\"></sup> them from the hand of those stronger<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19703AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19703AH\"></sup> than they.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>They will come and shout for joy<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19704AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19704AI\"></sup> on the heights<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19704AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19704AJ\"></sup> of Zion;they will rejoice in the bounty<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19704AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19704AK\"></sup> of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>—the grain, the new wine and the olive oil,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19704AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19704AL\"></sup>the young of the flocks<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19704AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19704AM\"></sup> and herds.They will be like a well-watered garden,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19704AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19704AN\"></sup>and they will sorrow<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19704AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19704AO\"></sup> no more.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Then young women will dance and be glad,young men and old as well.I will turn their mourning<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19705AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19705AP\"></sup> into gladness;I will give them comfort<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19705AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19705AQ\"></sup> and joy<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19705AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19705AR\"></sup> instead of sorrow.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>I will satisfy<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19706AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19706AS\"></sup> the priests<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19706AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19706AT\"></sup> with abundance,and my people will be filled with my bounty,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19706AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19706AU\"></sup>”declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>This is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says:“A voice is heard in Ramah,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19707AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19707AV\"></sup>mourning and great weeping,Rachel weeping for her childrenand refusing to be comforted,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19707AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19707AW\"></sup>because they are no more.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19707AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19707AX\"></sup>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>This is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says:“Restrain your voice from weepingand your eyes from tears,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19708AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19708AY\"></sup>for your work will be rewarded,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19708AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19708AZ\"></sup>”declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.“They will return<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19708BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19708BA\"></sup> from the land of the enemy.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>So there is hope<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19709BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19709BB\"></sup> for your descendants,”declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.“Your children<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19709BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19709BC\"></sup> will return to their own land.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>“I have surely heard Ephraim’s moaning:‘You disciplined<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19710BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19710BD\"></sup> me like an unruly calf,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19710BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19710BE\"></sup>and I have been disciplined.Restore<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19710BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19710BF\"></sup> me, and I will return,because you are the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> my God.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>After I strayed,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19711BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19711BG\"></sup>I repented;after I came to understand,I beat<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19711BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19711BH\"></sup> my breast.I was ashamed<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19711BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19711BI\"></sup> and humiliatedbecause I bore the disgrace of my youth.’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19711BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19711BJ\"></sup>",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Is not Ephraim my dear son,the child<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19712BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19712BK\"></sup> in whom I delight?Though I often speak against him,I still remember<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19712BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19712BL\"></sup> him.Therefore my heart yearns for him;I have great compassion<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19712BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19712BM\"></sup> for him,”declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>“Set up road signs;put up guideposts.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19713BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19713BN\"></sup>Take note of the highway,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19713BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19713BO\"></sup>the road that you take.Return,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19713BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19713BP\"></sup> Virgin<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19713BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19713BQ\"></sup> Israel,return to your towns.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>How long will you wander,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19714BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19714BR\"></sup>unfaithful<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19714BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19714BS\"></sup> Daughter Israel?The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will create a new thing<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19714BT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BT&quot;&gt;BT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19714BT\"></sup> on earth—the woman will return to<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19714BU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BU&quot;&gt;BU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19714BU\"></sup> the man.”",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>This is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty, the God of Israel, says: “When I bring them back from captivity,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19715BV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BV&quot;&gt;BV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19715BV\"></sup> the people in the land of Judah and in its towns will once again use these words: ‘The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> bless<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19715BW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BW&quot;&gt;BW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19715BW\"></sup> you, you prosperous city,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19715BX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BX&quot;&gt;BX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19715BX\"></sup> you sacred mountain.’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19715BY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BY&quot;&gt;BY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19715BY\"></sup>",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>People will live<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19716BZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BZ&quot;&gt;BZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19716BZ\"></sup> together in Judah and all its towns—farmers and those who move about with their flocks.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19716CA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CA&quot;&gt;CA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19716CA\"></sup>",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>I will refresh the weary<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19717CB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CB&quot;&gt;CB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19717CB\"></sup> and satisfy the faint.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19717CC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CC&quot;&gt;CC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19717CC\"></sup>",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>At this I awoke<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19718CD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CD&quot;&gt;CD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19718CD\"></sup> and looked around. My sleep had been pleasant to me.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>“The days are coming,”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19719CE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CE&quot;&gt;CE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19719CE\"></sup> declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, “when I will plant<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19719CF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CF&quot;&gt;CF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19719CF\"></sup> the kingdoms of Israel and Judah with the offspring of people and of animals.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>Just as I watched<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19720CG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CG&quot;&gt;CG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19720CG\"></sup> over them to uproot<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19720CH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CH&quot;&gt;CH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19720CH\"></sup> and tear down, and to overthrow, destroy and bring disaster,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19720CI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CI&quot;&gt;CI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19720CI\"></sup> so I will watch over them to build and to plant,”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19720CJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CJ&quot;&gt;CJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19720CJ\"></sup> declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>“In those days people will no longer say,‘The parents<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19721CK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CK&quot;&gt;CK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19721CK\"></sup> have eaten sour grapes,and the children’s teeth are set on edge.’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19721CL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CL&quot;&gt;CL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19721CL\"></sup>",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>Instead, everyone will die for their own sin;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19722CM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CM&quot;&gt;CM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19722CM\"></sup> whoever eats sour grapes—their own teeth will be set on edge.",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>“The days are coming,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,“when I will make a new covenant<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19723CN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CN&quot;&gt;CN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19723CN\"></sup>with the people of Israeland with the people of Judah.",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>It will not be like the covenant<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19724CO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CO&quot;&gt;CO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19724CO\"></sup>I made with their ancestors<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19724CP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CP&quot;&gt;CP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19724CP\"></sup>when I took them by the handto lead them out of Egypt,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19724CQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CQ&quot;&gt;CQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19724CQ\"></sup>because they broke my covenant,though I was a husband<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19724CR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CR&quot;&gt;CR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19724CR\"></sup> to them,”declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>“This is the covenant I will make with the people of Israelafter that time,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.“I will put my law in their minds<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19725CS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CS&quot;&gt;CS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19725CS\"></sup>and write it on their hearts.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19725CT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CT&quot;&gt;CT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19725CT\"></sup>I will be their God,and they will be my people.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19725CU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CU&quot;&gt;CU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19725CU\"></sup>",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>No longer will they teach<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19726CV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CV&quot;&gt;CV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19726CV\"></sup> their neighbor,or say to one another, ‘Know the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,’because they will all know<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19726CW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CW&quot;&gt;CW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19726CW\"></sup> me,from the least of them to the greatest,”declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.“For I will forgive<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19726CX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CX&quot;&gt;CX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19726CX\"></sup> their wickednessand will remember their sins<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19726CY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CY&quot;&gt;CY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19726CY\"></sup> no more.”",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup>This is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says,he who appoints<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19727CZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CZ&quot;&gt;CZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19727CZ\"></sup> the sunto shine by day,who decrees the moon and starsto shine by night,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19727DA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DA&quot;&gt;DA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19727DA\"></sup>who stirs up the sea<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19727DB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DB&quot;&gt;DB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19727DB\"></sup>so that its waves roar<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19727DC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DC&quot;&gt;DC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19727DC\"></sup>—the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty is his name:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19727DD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DD&quot;&gt;DD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19727DD\"></sup>",
			"36": "<sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup>“Only if these decrees<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19728DE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DE&quot;&gt;DE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19728DE\"></sup> vanish from my sight,”declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,“will Israel<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19728DF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DF&quot;&gt;DF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19728DF\"></sup> ever ceasebeing a nation before me.”",
			"37": "<sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup>This is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says:“Only if the heavens above can be measured<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19729DG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DG&quot;&gt;DG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19729DG\"></sup>and the foundations of the earth below be searched outwill I reject<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19729DH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DH&quot;&gt;DH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19729DH\"></sup> all the descendants of Israelbecause of all they have done,”declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"38": "<sup class=\"versenum\">38 </sup>“The days are coming,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, “when this city will be rebuilt<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19730DI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DI&quot;&gt;DI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19730DI\"></sup> for me from the Tower of Hananel<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19730DJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DJ&quot;&gt;DJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19730DJ\"></sup> to the Corner Gate.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19730DK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DK&quot;&gt;DK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19730DK\"></sup>",
			"39": "<sup class=\"versenum\">39 </sup>The measuring line<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19731DL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DL&quot;&gt;DL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19731DL\"></sup> will stretch from there straight to the hill of Gareb and then turn to Goah.",
			"40": "<sup class=\"versenum\">40 </sup>The whole valley<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19732DM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DM&quot;&gt;DM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19732DM\"></sup> where dead bodies<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19732DN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DN&quot;&gt;DN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19732DN\"></sup> and ashes are thrown, and all the terraces out to the Kidron Valley<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19732DO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DO&quot;&gt;DO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19732DO\"></sup> on the east as far as the corner of the Horse Gate,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19732DP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DP&quot;&gt;DP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19732DP\"></sup> will be holy<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19732DQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DQ&quot;&gt;DQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19732DQ\"></sup> to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>. The city will never again be uprooted or demolished.”"
		},
		"32": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">32 </span>This is the word that came to Jeremiah from the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> in the tenth<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19733A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19733A\"></sup> year of Zedekiah king of Judah, which was the eighteenth<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19733B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19733B\"></sup> year of Nebuchadnezzar.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>The army of the king of Babylon was then besieging<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19734C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19734C\"></sup> Jerusalem, and Jeremiah the prophet was confined<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19734D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19734D\"></sup> in the courtyard of the guard<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19734E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19734E\"></sup> in the royal palace of Judah.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Now Zedekiah king of Judah had imprisoned him there, saying, “Why do you prophesy<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19735F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19735F\"></sup> as you do? You say, ‘This is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says: I am about to give this city into the hands of the king of Babylon, and he will capture<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19735G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19735G\"></sup> it.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Zedekiah<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19736H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19736H\"></sup> king of Judah will not escape<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19736I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19736I\"></sup> the Babylonians<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19736J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19736J\"></sup> but will certainly be given into the hands of the king of Babylon, and will speak with him face to face and see him with his own eyes.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>He will take<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19737K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19737K\"></sup> Zedekiah to Babylon, where he will remain until I deal with him,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19737L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19737L\"></sup> declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>. If you fight against the Babylonians, you will not succeed.’”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19737M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19737M\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Jeremiah said, “The word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to me:",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Hanamel son of Shallum your uncle is going to come to you and say, ‘Buy my field at Anathoth,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19739N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19739N\"></sup> because as nearest relative it is your right and duty<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19739O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19739O\"></sup> to buy it.’",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>“Then, just as the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> had said, my cousin Hanamel came to me in the courtyard of the guard and said, ‘Buy my field<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19740P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19740P\"></sup> at Anathoth in the territory of Benjamin. Since it is your right to redeem it and possess it, buy it for yourself.’“I knew that this was the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>;",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>so I bought the field<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19741Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19741Q\"></sup> at Anathoth from my cousin Hanamel and weighed out for him seventeen shekels of silver.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19741R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19741R\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>I signed and sealed the deed,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19742S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19742S\"></sup> had it witnessed,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19742T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19742T\"></sup> and weighed out the silver on the scales.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>I took the deed of purchase—the sealed copy containing the terms and conditions, as well as the unsealed copy—",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>and I gave this deed to Baruch<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19744U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19744U\"></sup> son of Neriah,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19744V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19744V\"></sup> the son of Mahseiah, in the presence of my cousin Hanamel and of the witnesses who had signed the deed and of all the Jews sitting in the courtyard of the guard.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>“In their presence I gave Baruch these instructions:",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>‘This is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty, the God of Israel, says: Take these documents, both the sealed<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19746W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19746W\"></sup> and unsealed copies of the deed of purchase, and put them in a clay jar so they will last a long time.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>For this is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty, the God of Israel, says: Houses, fields and vineyards will again be bought in this land.’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19747X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19747X\"></sup>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>“After I had given the deed of purchase to Baruch<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19748Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19748Y\"></sup> son of Neriah, I prayed to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>:",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>“Ah, Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19749Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19749Z\"></sup> you have made the heavens and the earth<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19749AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19749AA\"></sup> by your great power and outstretched arm.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19749AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19749AB\"></sup> Nothing is too hard<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19749AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19749AC\"></sup> for you.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>You show love<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19750AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19750AD\"></sup> to thousands but bring the punishment for the parents’ sins into the laps<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19750AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19750AE\"></sup> of their children<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19750AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19750AF\"></sup> after them. Great and mighty God,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19750AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19750AG\"></sup> whose name is the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19750AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19750AH\"></sup>",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>great are your purposes and mighty are your deeds.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19751AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19751AI\"></sup> Your eyes are open to the ways of all mankind;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19751AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19751AJ\"></sup> you reward each person according to their conduct and as their deeds deserve.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19751AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19751AK\"></sup>",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>You performed signs and wonders<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19752AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19752AL\"></sup> in Egypt<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19752AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19752AM\"></sup> and have continued them to this day, in Israel and among all mankind, and have gained the renown<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19752AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19752AN\"></sup> that is still yours.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>You brought your people Israel out of Egypt with signs and wonders, by a mighty hand<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19753AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19753AO\"></sup> and an outstretched arm<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19753AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19753AP\"></sup> and with great terror.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19753AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19753AQ\"></sup>",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>You gave them this land you had sworn to give their ancestors, a land flowing with milk and honey.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19754AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19754AR\"></sup>",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>They came in and took possession<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19755AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19755AS\"></sup> of it, but they did not obey you or follow your law;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19755AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19755AT\"></sup> they did not do what you commanded them to do. So you brought all this disaster<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19755AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19755AU\"></sup> on them.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>“See how the siege ramps<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19756AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19756AV\"></sup> are built up to take the city. Because of the sword, famine and plague,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19756AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19756AW\"></sup> the city will be given into the hands of the Babylonians who are attacking it. What you said<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19756AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19756AX\"></sup> has happened,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19756AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19756AY\"></sup> as you now see.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>And though the city will be given into the hands of the Babylonians, you, Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, say to me, ‘Buy the field<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19757AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19757AZ\"></sup> with silver and have the transaction witnessed.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19757BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19757BA\"></sup>’”",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>Then the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to Jeremiah:",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>“I am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, the God of all mankind.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19759BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19759BB\"></sup> Is anything too hard for me?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19759BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19759BC\"></sup>",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>Therefore this is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says: I am about to give this city into the hands of the Babylonians and to Nebuchadnezzar<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19760BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19760BD\"></sup> king of Babylon, who will capture it.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19760BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19760BE\"></sup>",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>The Babylonians who are attacking this city will come in and set it on fire; they will burn it down,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19761BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19761BF\"></sup> along with the houses<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19761BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19761BG\"></sup> where the people aroused my anger by burning incense on the roofs to Baal and by pouring out drink offerings<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19761BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19761BH\"></sup> to other gods.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19761BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19761BI\"></sup>",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>“The people of Israel and Judah have done nothing but evil in my sight from their youth;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19762BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19762BJ\"></sup> indeed, the people of Israel have done nothing but arouse my anger<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19762BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19762BK\"></sup> with what their hands have made,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19762BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19762BL\"></sup> declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>From the day it was built until now, this city<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19763BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19763BM\"></sup> has so aroused my anger and wrath that I must remove<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19763BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19763BN\"></sup> it from my sight.",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>The people of Israel and Judah have provoked<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19764BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19764BO\"></sup> me by all the evil<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19764BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19764BP\"></sup> they have done—they, their kings and officials,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19764BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19764BQ\"></sup> their priests and prophets, the people of Judah and those living in Jerusalem.",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>They turned their backs<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19765BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19765BR\"></sup> to me and not their faces; though I taught<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19765BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19765BS\"></sup> them again and again, they would not listen or respond to discipline.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19765BT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BT&quot;&gt;BT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19765BT\"></sup>",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>They set up their vile images<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19766BU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BU&quot;&gt;BU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19766BU\"></sup> in the house that bears my Name<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19766BV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BV&quot;&gt;BV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19766BV\"></sup> and defiled<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19766BW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BW&quot;&gt;BW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19766BW\"></sup> it.",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup>They built high places for Baal in the Valley of Ben Hinnom<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19767BX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BX&quot;&gt;BX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19767BX\"></sup> to sacrifice their sons and daughters to Molek,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19767BY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BY&quot;&gt;BY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19767BY\"></sup> though I never commanded—nor did it enter my mind<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19767BZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BZ&quot;&gt;BZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19767BZ\"></sup>—that they should do such a detestable<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19767CA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CA&quot;&gt;CA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19767CA\"></sup> thing and so make Judah sin.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19767CB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CB&quot;&gt;CB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19767CB\"></sup>",
			"36": "<sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup>“You are saying about this city, ‘By the sword, famine and plague<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19768CC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CC&quot;&gt;CC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19768CC\"></sup> it will be given into the hands of the king of Babylon’; but this is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, the God of Israel, says:",
			"37": "<sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup>I will surely gather<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19769CD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CD&quot;&gt;CD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19769CD\"></sup> them from all the lands where I banish them in my furious anger<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19769CE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CE&quot;&gt;CE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19769CE\"></sup> and great wrath; I will bring them back to this place and let them live in safety.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19769CF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CF&quot;&gt;CF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19769CF\"></sup>",
			"38": "<sup class=\"versenum\">38 </sup>They will be my people,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19770CG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CG&quot;&gt;CG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19770CG\"></sup> and I will be their God.",
			"39": "<sup class=\"versenum\">39 </sup>I will give them singleness<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19771CH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CH&quot;&gt;CH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19771CH\"></sup> of heart and action, so that they will always fear<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19771CI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CI&quot;&gt;CI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19771CI\"></sup> me and that all will then go well for them and for their children after them.",
			"40": "<sup class=\"versenum\">40 </sup>I will make an everlasting covenant<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19772CJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CJ&quot;&gt;CJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19772CJ\"></sup> with them: I will never stop doing good to them, and I will inspire<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19772CK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CK&quot;&gt;CK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19772CK\"></sup> them to fear me, so that they will never turn away from me.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19772CL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CL&quot;&gt;CL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19772CL\"></sup>",
			"41": "<sup class=\"versenum\">41 </sup>I will rejoice<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19773CM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CM&quot;&gt;CM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19773CM\"></sup> in doing them good<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19773CN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CN&quot;&gt;CN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19773CN\"></sup> and will assuredly plant<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19773CO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CO&quot;&gt;CO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19773CO\"></sup> them in this land with all my heart and soul.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19773CP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CP&quot;&gt;CP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19773CP\"></sup>",
			"42": "<sup class=\"versenum\">42 </sup>“This is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says: As I have brought all this great calamity<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19774CQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CQ&quot;&gt;CQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19774CQ\"></sup> on this people, so I will give them all the prosperity I have promised<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19774CR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CR&quot;&gt;CR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19774CR\"></sup> them.",
			"43": "<sup class=\"versenum\">43 </sup>Once more fields will be bought<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19775CS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CS&quot;&gt;CS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19775CS\"></sup> in this land of which you say, ‘It is a desolate<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19775CT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CT&quot;&gt;CT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19775CT\"></sup> waste, without people or animals, for it has been given into the hands of the Babylonians.’",
			"44": "<sup class=\"versenum\">44 </sup>Fields will be bought for silver, and deeds<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19776CU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CU&quot;&gt;CU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19776CU\"></sup> will be signed, sealed and witnessed<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19776CV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CV&quot;&gt;CV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19776CV\"></sup> in the territory of Benjamin, in the villages around Jerusalem, in the towns of Judah and in the towns of the hill country, of the western foothills and of the Negev,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19776CW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CW&quot;&gt;CW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19776CW\"></sup> because I will restore<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19776CX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CX&quot;&gt;CX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19776CX\"></sup> their fortunes, declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.”"
		},
		"33": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">33 </span>While Jeremiah was still confined<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19777A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19777A\"></sup> in the courtyard<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19777B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19777B\"></sup> of the guard, the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to him a second time:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19777C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19777C\"></sup>",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“This is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says, he who made the earth,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19778D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19778D\"></sup> the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> who formed it and established it—the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> is his name:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19778E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19778E\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>‘Call<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19779F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19779F\"></sup> to me and I will answer you and tell you great and unsearchable<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19779G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19779G\"></sup> things you do not know.’",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>For this is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, the God of Israel, says about the houses in this city and the royal palaces of Judah that have been torn down to be used against the siege<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19780H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19780H\"></sup> ramps<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19780I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19780I\"></sup> and the sword",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>in the fight with the Babylonians: ‘They will be filled with the dead bodies of the people I will slay in my anger and wrath.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19781J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19781J\"></sup> I will hide my face<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19781K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19781K\"></sup> from this city because of all its wickedness.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>“‘Nevertheless, I will bring health and healing to it; I will heal<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19782L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19782L\"></sup> my people and will let them enjoy abundant peace<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19782M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19782M\"></sup> and security.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>I will bring Judah<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19783N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19783N\"></sup> and Israel back from captivity<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19783O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19783O\"></sup> and will rebuild<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19783P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19783P\"></sup> them as they were before.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19783Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19783Q\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>I will cleanse<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19784R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19784R\"></sup> them from all the sin they have committed against me and will forgive<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19784S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19784S\"></sup> all their sins of rebellion against me.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Then this city will bring me renown,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19785T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19785T\"></sup> joy, praise<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19785U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19785U\"></sup> and honor<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19785V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19785V\"></sup> before all nations on earth that hear of all the good things I do for it; and they will be in awe and will tremble<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19785W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19785W\"></sup> at the abundant prosperity and peace I provide for it.’",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>“This is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says: ‘You say about this place, “It is a desolate waste, without people or animals.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19786X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19786X\"></sup> Yet in the towns of Judah and the streets of Jerusalem that are deserted,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19786Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19786Y\"></sup> inhabited by neither people nor animals, there will be heard once more",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>the sounds of joy and gladness,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19787Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19787Z\"></sup> the voices of bride and bridegroom, and the voices of those who bring thank offerings<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19787AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19787AA\"></sup> to the house of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, saying,“Give thanks to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty,for the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> is good;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19787AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19787AB\"></sup>his love endures forever.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19787AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19787AC\"></sup>For I will restore the fortunes<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19787AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19787AD\"></sup> of the land as they were before,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19787AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19787AE\"></sup>’ says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>“This is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty says: ‘In this place, desolate<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19788AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19788AF\"></sup> and without people or animals<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19788AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19788AG\"></sup>—in all its towns there will again be pastures for shepherds to rest their flocks.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19788AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19788AH\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>In the towns of the hill<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19789AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19789AI\"></sup> country, of the western foothills and of the Negev,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19789AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19789AJ\"></sup> in the territory of Benjamin, in the villages around Jerusalem and in the towns of Judah, flocks will again pass under the hand<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19789AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19789AK\"></sup> of the one who counts them,’ says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>“‘The days are coming,’ declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, ‘when I will fulfill the good promise<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19790AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19790AL\"></sup> I made to the people of Israel and Judah.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>“‘In those days and at that timeI will make a righteous<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19791AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19791AM\"></sup> Branch<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19791AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19791AN\"></sup> sprout from David’s line;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19791AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19791AO\"></sup>he will do what is just and right in the land.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>In those days Judah will be saved<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19792AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19792AP\"></sup>and Jerusalem will live in safety.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19792AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19792AQ\"></sup>This is the name by which it will be called:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19792AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19792AR\"></sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Our Righteous Savior.’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19792AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19792AS\"></sup>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>For this is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says: ‘David will never fail<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19793AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19793AT\"></sup> to have a man to sit on the throne of Israel,",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>nor will the Levitical<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19794AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19794AU\"></sup> priests<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19794AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19794AV\"></sup> ever fail to have a man to stand before me continually to offer burnt offerings, to burn grain offerings and to present sacrifices.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19794AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19794AW\"></sup>’”",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>The word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to Jeremiah:",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>“This is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says: ‘If you can break my covenant with the day<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19796AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19796AX\"></sup> and my covenant with the night, so that day and night no longer come at their appointed time,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19796AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19796AY\"></sup>",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>then my covenant<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19797AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19797AZ\"></sup> with David my servant—and my covenant with the Levites<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19797BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19797BA\"></sup> who are priests ministering before me—can be broken and David will no longer have a descendant to reign on his throne.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19797BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19797BB\"></sup>",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>I will make the descendants of David my servant and the Levites who minister before me as countless<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19798BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19798BC\"></sup> as the stars in the sky and as measureless as the sand on the seashore.’”",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>The word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to Jeremiah:",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>“Have you not noticed that these people are saying, ‘The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has rejected the two kingdoms<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19800BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19800BD\"></sup> he chose’? So they despise<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19800BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19800BE\"></sup> my people and no longer regard them as a nation.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19800BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19800BF\"></sup>",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>This is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says: ‘If I have not made my covenant with day and night<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19801BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19801BG\"></sup> and established the laws<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19801BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19801BH\"></sup> of heaven and earth,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19801BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19801BI\"></sup>",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>then I will reject<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19802BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19802BJ\"></sup> the descendants of Jacob<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19802BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19802BK\"></sup> and David my servant and will not choose one of his sons to rule over the descendants of Abraham, Isaac and Jacob. For I will restore their fortunes<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19802BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19802BL\"></sup> and have compassion<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19802BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19802BM\"></sup> on them.’”"
		},
		"34": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">34 </span>While Nebuchadnezzar king of Babylon and all his army and all the kingdoms and peoples<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19803A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19803A\"></sup> in the empire he ruled were fighting against Jerusalem<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19803B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19803B\"></sup> and all its surrounding towns, this word came to Jeremiah from the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>:",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“This is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, the God of Israel, says: Go to Zedekiah<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19804C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19804C\"></sup> king of Judah and tell him, ‘This is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says: I am about to give this city into the hands of the king of Babylon, and he will burn it down.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19804D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19804D\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>You will not escape from his grasp but will surely be captured and given into his hands.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19805E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19805E\"></sup> You will see the king of Babylon with your own eyes, and he will speak with you face to face. And you will go to Babylon.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>“‘Yet hear the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>’s promise to you, Zedekiah king of Judah. This is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says concerning you: You will not die by the sword;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19806F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19806F\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>you will die peacefully. As people made a funeral fire<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19807G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19807G\"></sup> in honor of your predecessors, the kings who ruled before you, so they will make a fire in your honor and lament, “Alas,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19807H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19807H\"></sup> master!” I myself make this promise, declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.’”",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Then Jeremiah the prophet told all this to Zedekiah king of Judah, in Jerusalem,",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>while the army of the king of Babylon was fighting against Jerusalem and the other cities of Judah that were still holding out—Lachish<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19809I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19809I\"></sup> and Azekah.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19809J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19809J\"></sup> These were the only fortified cities left in Judah.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>The word came to Jeremiah from the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> after King Zedekiah had made a covenant with all the people<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19810K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19810K\"></sup> in Jerusalem to proclaim freedom<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19810L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19810L\"></sup> for the slaves.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Everyone was to free their Hebrew slaves, both male and female; no one was to hold a fellow Hebrew in bondage.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19811M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19811M\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>So all the officials and people who entered into this covenant agreed that they would free their male and female slaves and no longer hold them in bondage. They agreed, and set them free.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>But afterward they changed their minds<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19813N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19813N\"></sup> and took back the slaves they had freed and enslaved them again.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Then the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to Jeremiah:",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>“This is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, the God of Israel, says: I made a covenant with your ancestors<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19815O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19815O\"></sup> when I brought them out of Egypt, out of the land of slavery.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19815P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19815P\"></sup> I said,",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>‘Every seventh year each of you must free any fellow Hebrews who have sold themselves to you. After they have served you six years, you must let them go free.’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19816Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19816Q\"></sup> Your ancestors, however, did not listen to me or pay attention<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19816R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19816R\"></sup> to me.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Recently you repented and did what is right in my sight: Each of you proclaimed freedom to your own people.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19817S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19817S\"></sup> You even made a covenant before me in the house that bears my Name.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19817T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19817T\"></sup>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>But now you have turned around<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19818U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19818U\"></sup> and profaned<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19818V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19818V\"></sup> my name; each of you has taken back the male and female slaves you had set free to go where they wished. You have forced them to become your slaves again.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>“Therefore this is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says: You have not obeyed me; you have not proclaimed freedom to your own people. So I now proclaim ‘freedom’ for you,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19819W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19819W\"></sup> declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>—‘freedom’ to fall by the sword, plague<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19819X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19819X\"></sup> and famine.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19819Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19819Y\"></sup> I will make you abhorrent to all the kingdoms of the earth.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19819Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19819Z\"></sup>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Those who have violated my covenant<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19820AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19820AA\"></sup> and have not fulfilled the terms of the covenant they made before me, I will treat like the calf they cut in two and then walked between its pieces.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19820AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19820AB\"></sup>",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>The leaders of Judah and Jerusalem, the court officials,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19821AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19821AC\"></sup> the priests and all the people of the land who walked between the pieces of the calf,",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>I will deliver<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19822AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19822AD\"></sup> into the hands of their enemies who want to kill them.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19822AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19822AE\"></sup> Their dead bodies will become food for the birds and the wild animals.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19822AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19822AF\"></sup>",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>“I will deliver Zedekiah<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19823AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19823AG\"></sup> king of Judah and his officials<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19823AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19823AH\"></sup> into the hands of their enemies<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19823AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19823AI\"></sup> who want to kill them, to the army of the king of Babylon,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19823AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19823AJ\"></sup> which has withdrawn<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19823AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19823AK\"></sup> from you.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>I am going to give the order, declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, and I will bring them back to this city. They will fight against it, take<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19824AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19824AL\"></sup> it and burn<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19824AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19824AM\"></sup> it down. And I will lay waste<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19824AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19824AN\"></sup> the towns of Judah so no one can live there.”"
		},
		"35": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">35 </span>This is the word that came to Jeremiah from the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> during the reign of Jehoiakim<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19825A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19825A\"></sup> son of Josiah king of Judah:",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“Go to the Rekabite<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19826B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19826B\"></sup> family and invite them to come to one of the side rooms<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19826C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19826C\"></sup> of the house of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> and give them wine to drink.”",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>So I went to get Jaazaniah son of Jeremiah, the son of Habazziniah, and his brothers and all his sons—the whole family of the Rekabites.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>I brought them into the house of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, into the room of the sons of Hanan son of Igdaliah the man of God.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19828D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19828D\"></sup> It was next to the room of the officials, which was over that of Maaseiah son of Shallum<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19828E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19828E\"></sup> the doorkeeper.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19828F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19828F\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Then I set bowls full of wine and some cups before the Rekabites and said to them, “Drink some wine.”",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>But they replied, “We do not drink wine, because our forefather Jehonadab<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19830G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19830G\"></sup> son of Rekab gave us this command: ‘Neither you nor your descendants must ever drink wine.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19830H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19830H\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Also you must never build houses, sow seed or plant vineyards; you must never have any of these things, but must always live in tents.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19831I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19831I\"></sup> Then you will live a long time in the land<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19831J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19831J\"></sup> where you are nomads.’",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>We have obeyed everything our forefather<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19832K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19832K\"></sup> Jehonadab son of Rekab commanded us. Neither we nor our wives nor our sons and daughters have ever drunk wine",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>or built houses to live in or had vineyards, fields or crops.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19833L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19833L\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>We have lived in tents and have fully obeyed everything our forefather Jehonadab commanded us.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>But when Nebuchadnezzar king of Babylon invaded<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19835M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19835M\"></sup> this land, we said, ‘Come, we must go to Jerusalem<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19835N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19835N\"></sup> to escape the Babylonian and Aramean armies.’ So we have remained in Jerusalem.”",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Then the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to Jeremiah, saying:",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>“This is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty, the God of Israel, says: Go and tell<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19837O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19837O\"></sup> the people of Judah and those living in Jerusalem, ‘Will you not learn a lesson<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19837P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19837P\"></sup> and obey my words?’ declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>‘Jehonadab son of Rekab ordered his descendants not to drink wine and this command has been kept. To this day they do not drink wine, because they obey their forefather’s command.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19838Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19838Q\"></sup> But I have spoken to you again and again,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19838R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19838R\"></sup> yet you have not obeyed<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19838S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19838S\"></sup> me.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Again and again I sent all my servants the prophets<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19839T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19839T\"></sup> to you. They said, “Each of you must turn<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19839U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19839U\"></sup> from your wicked ways and reform<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19839V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19839V\"></sup> your actions; do not follow other gods<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19839W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19839W\"></sup> to serve them. Then you will live in the land<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19839X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19839X\"></sup> I have given to you and your ancestors.” But you have not paid attention or listened<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19839Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19839Y\"></sup> to me.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>The descendants of Jehonadab son of Rekab have carried out the command their forefather<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19840Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19840Z\"></sup> gave them, but these people have not obeyed me.’",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>“Therefore this is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> God Almighty, the God of Israel, says: ‘Listen! I am going to bring on Judah and on everyone living in Jerusalem every disaster<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19841AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19841AA\"></sup> I pronounced against them. I spoke to them, but they did not listen;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19841AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19841AB\"></sup> I called to them, but they did not answer.’”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19841AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19841AC\"></sup>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Then Jeremiah said to the family of the Rekabites, “This is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty, the God of Israel, says: ‘You have obeyed the command of your forefather<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19842AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19842AD\"></sup> Jehonadab and have followed all his instructions and have done everything he ordered.’",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>Therefore this is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty, the God of Israel, says: ‘Jehonadab son of Rekab will never fail<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19843AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19843AE\"></sup> to have a descendant to serve<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19843AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19843AF\"></sup> me.’”"
		},
		"36": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">36 </span>In the fourth year of Jehoiakim<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19844A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19844A\"></sup> son of Josiah king of Judah, this word came to Jeremiah from the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>:",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“Take a scroll<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19845B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19845B\"></sup> and write on it all the words<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19845C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19845C\"></sup> I have spoken to you concerning Israel, Judah and all the other nations from the time I began speaking to you in the reign of Josiah<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19845D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19845D\"></sup> till now.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Perhaps<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19846E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19846E\"></sup> when the people of Judah hear<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19846F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19846F\"></sup> about every disaster I plan to inflict on them, they will each turn<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19846G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19846G\"></sup> from their wicked ways; then I will forgive<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19846H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19846H\"></sup> their wickedness and their sin.”",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>So Jeremiah called Baruch<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19847I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19847I\"></sup> son of Neriah,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19847J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19847J\"></sup> and while Jeremiah dictated<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19847K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19847K\"></sup> all the words the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> had spoken to him, Baruch wrote them on the scroll.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19847L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19847L\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Then Jeremiah told Baruch, “I am restricted; I am not allowed to go to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>’s temple.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>So you go to the house of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> on a day of fasting<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19849M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19849M\"></sup> and read to the people from the scroll the words of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> that you wrote as I dictated.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19849N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19849N\"></sup> Read them to all the people of Judah<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19849O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19849O\"></sup> who come in from their towns.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Perhaps they will bring their petition<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19850P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19850P\"></sup> before the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> and will each turn<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19850Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19850Q\"></sup> from their wicked ways, for the anger<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19850R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19850R\"></sup> and wrath pronounced against this people by the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> are great.”",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Baruch son of Neriah did everything Jeremiah the prophet told him to do; at the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>’s temple he read the words of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> from the scroll.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>In the ninth month<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19852S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19852S\"></sup> of the fifth year of Jehoiakim son of Josiah king of Judah, a time of fasting<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19852T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19852T\"></sup> before the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> was proclaimed for all the people in Jerusalem and those who had come from the towns of Judah.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>From the room of Gemariah<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19853U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19853U\"></sup> son of Shaphan<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19853V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19853V\"></sup> the secretary,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19853W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19853W\"></sup> which was in the upper courtyard at the entrance of the New Gate<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19853X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19853X\"></sup> of the temple, Baruch read to all the people at the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>’s temple the words of Jeremiah from the scroll.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>When Micaiah son of Gemariah, the son of Shaphan, heard all the words of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> from the scroll,",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>he went down to the secretary’s<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19855Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19855Y\"></sup> room in the royal palace, where all the officials were sitting: Elishama the secretary, Delaiah son of Shemaiah, Elnathan<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19855Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19855Z\"></sup> son of Akbor, Gemariah son of Shaphan, Zedekiah son of Hananiah, and all the other officials.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19855AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19855AA\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>After Micaiah told them everything he had heard Baruch read to the people from the scroll,",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>all the officials sent Jehudi<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19857AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19857AB\"></sup> son of Nethaniah, the son of Shelemiah, the son of Cushi, to say to Baruch, “Bring the scroll<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19857AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19857AC\"></sup> from which you have read to the people and come.” So Baruch son of Neriah went to them with the scroll in his hand.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>They said to him, “Sit down, please, and read it to us.”So Baruch read it to them.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>When they heard all these words, they looked at each other in fear<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19859AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19859AD\"></sup> and said to Baruch, “We must report all these words to the king.”",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Then they asked Baruch, “Tell us, how did you come to write<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19860AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19860AE\"></sup> all this? Did Jeremiah dictate it?”",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>“Yes,” Baruch replied, “he dictated<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19861AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19861AF\"></sup> all these words to me, and I wrote them in ink on the scroll.”",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>Then the officials<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19862AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19862AG\"></sup> said to Baruch, “You and Jeremiah, go and hide.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19862AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19862AH\"></sup> Don’t let anyone know where you are.”",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>After they put the scroll in the room of Elishama the secretary, they went to the king in the courtyard and reported everything to him.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>The king sent Jehudi<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19864AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19864AI\"></sup> to get the scroll, and Jehudi brought it from the room of Elishama the secretary and read it to the king<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19864AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19864AJ\"></sup> and all the officials standing beside him.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>It was the ninth month and the king was sitting in the winter apartment,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19865AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19865AK\"></sup> with a fire burning in the firepot in front of him.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>Whenever Jehudi had read three or four columns of the scroll,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19866AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19866AL\"></sup> the king cut them off with a scribe’s knife and threw them into the firepot, until the entire scroll was burned in the fire.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19866AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19866AM\"></sup>",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>The king and all his attendants who heard all these words showed no fear,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19867AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19867AN\"></sup> nor did they tear their clothes.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19867AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19867AO\"></sup>",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>Even though Elnathan, Delaiah<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19868AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19868AP\"></sup> and Gemariah<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19868AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19868AQ\"></sup> urged the king not to burn the scroll, he would not listen to them.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>Instead, the king commanded Jerahmeel, a son of the king, Seraiah son of Azriel and Shelemiah son of Abdeel to arrest<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19869AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19869AR\"></sup> Baruch the scribe and Jeremiah the prophet. But the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> had hidden<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19869AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19869AS\"></sup> them.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>After the king burned the scroll containing the words that Baruch had written at Jeremiah’s dictation,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19870AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19870AT\"></sup> the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to Jeremiah:",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>“Take another scroll<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19871AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19871AU\"></sup> and write on it all the words that were on the first scroll, which Jehoiakim king of Judah burned up.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>Also tell Jehoiakim king of Judah, ‘This is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says: You burned that scroll and said, “Why did you write on it that the king of Babylon would certainly come and destroy this land and wipe from it<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19872AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19872AV\"></sup> both man and beast?”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19872AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19872AW\"></sup>",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>Therefore this is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says about Jehoiakim<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19873AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19873AX\"></sup> king of Judah: He will have no one to sit on the throne of David; his body will be thrown out<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19873AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19873AY\"></sup> and exposed<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19873AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19873AZ\"></sup> to the heat by day and the frost by night.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19873BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19873BA\"></sup>",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>I will punish him and his children<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19874BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19874BB\"></sup> and his attendants for their wickedness; I will bring on them and those living in Jerusalem and the people of Judah every disaster<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19874BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19874BC\"></sup> I pronounced against them, because they have not listened.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19874BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19874BD\"></sup>’”",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>So Jeremiah took another scroll and gave it to the scribe Baruch son of Neriah, and as Jeremiah dictated,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19875BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19875BE\"></sup> Baruch wrote<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19875BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19875BF\"></sup> on it all the words of the scroll that Jehoiakim king of Judah had burned<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19875BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19875BG\"></sup> in the fire. And many similar words were added to them."
		},
		"37": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">37 </span>Zedekiah<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19876A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19876A\"></sup> son of Josiah was made king<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19876B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19876B\"></sup> of Judah by Nebuchadnezzar king of Babylon; he reigned in place of Jehoiachin<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19876C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19876C\"></sup> son of Jehoiakim.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Neither he nor his attendants nor the people of the land paid any attention<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19877D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19877D\"></sup> to the words the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> had spoken through Jeremiah the prophet.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>King Zedekiah, however, sent<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19878E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19878E\"></sup> Jehukal<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19878F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19878F\"></sup> son of Shelemiah with the priest Zephaniah<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19878G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19878G\"></sup> son of Maaseiah to Jeremiah the prophet with this message: “Please pray<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19878H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19878H\"></sup> to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> our God for us.”",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Now Jeremiah was free to come and go among the people, for he had not yet been put in prison.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19879I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19879I\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Pharaoh’s army had marched out of Egypt,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19880J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19880J\"></sup> and when the Babylonians who were besieging Jerusalem heard the report about them, they withdrew<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19880K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19880K\"></sup> from Jerusalem.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19880L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19880L\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Then the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to Jeremiah the prophet:",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>“This is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, the God of Israel, says: Tell the king of Judah, who sent you to inquire<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19882M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19882M\"></sup> of me, ‘Pharaoh’s army, which has marched<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19882N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19882N\"></sup> out to support you, will go back to its own land, to Egypt.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19882O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19882O\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Then the Babylonians will return and attack this city; they will capture<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19883P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19883P\"></sup> it and burn<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19883Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19883Q\"></sup> it down.’",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>“This is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says: Do not deceive<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19884R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19884R\"></sup> yourselves, thinking, ‘The Babylonians will surely leave us.’ They will not!",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Even if you were to defeat the entire Babylonian army that is attacking you and only wounded men were left in their tents, they would come out and burn<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19885S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19885S\"></sup> this city down.”",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>After the Babylonian army had withdrawn<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19886T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19886T\"></sup> from Jerusalem because of Pharaoh’s army,",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Jeremiah started to leave the city to go to the territory of Benjamin to get his share of the property<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19887U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19887U\"></sup> among the people there.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>But when he reached the Benjamin Gate,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19888V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19888V\"></sup> the captain of the guard, whose name was Irijah son of Shelemiah, the son of Hananiah, arrested him and said, “You are deserting to the Babylonians!”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19888W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19888W\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>“That’s not true!” Jeremiah said. “I am not deserting to the Babylonians.” But Irijah would not listen to him; instead, he arrested<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19889X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19889X\"></sup> Jeremiah and brought him to the officials.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>They were angry with Jeremiah and had him beaten<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19890Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19890Y\"></sup> and imprisoned<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19890Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19890Z\"></sup> in the house<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19890AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19890AA\"></sup> of Jonathan the secretary, which they had made into a prison.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Jeremiah was put into a vaulted cell in a dungeon, where he remained a long time.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Then King Zedekiah sent<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19892AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19892AB\"></sup> for him and had him brought to the palace, where he asked<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19892AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19892AC\"></sup> him privately,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19892AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19892AD\"></sup> “Is there any word from the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>?”“Yes,” Jeremiah replied, “you will be delivered<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19892AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19892AE\"></sup> into the hands of the king of Babylon.”",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Then Jeremiah said to King Zedekiah, “What crime<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19893AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19893AF\"></sup> have I committed against you or your attendants or this people, that you have put me in prison?",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>Where are your prophets<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19894AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19894AG\"></sup> who prophesied to you, ‘The king of Babylon will not attack you or this land’?",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>But now, my lord the king, please listen. Let me bring my petition before you: Do not send me back to the house of Jonathan the secretary, or I will die there.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19895AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19895AH\"></sup>",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>King Zedekiah then gave orders for Jeremiah to be placed in the courtyard of the guard and given a loaf of bread from the street of the bakers each day until all the bread<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19896AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19896AI\"></sup> in the city was gone.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19896AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19896AJ\"></sup> So Jeremiah remained in the courtyard of the guard.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19896AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19896AK\"></sup>"
		},
		"38": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">38 </span>Shephatiah son of Mattan, Gedaliah son of Pashhur<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19897A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19897A\"></sup>, Jehukal<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19897B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19897B\"></sup> son of Shelemiah, and Pashhur son of Malkijah heard what Jeremiah was telling all the people when he said,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“This is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says: ‘Whoever stays in this city will die by the sword, famine or plague,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19898C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19898C\"></sup> but whoever goes over to the Babylonians will live. They will escape with their lives; they will live.’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19898D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19898D\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>And this is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says: ‘This city will certainly be given into the hands of the army of the king of Babylon, who will capture it.’”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19899E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19899E\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Then the officials<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19900F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19900F\"></sup> said to the king, “This man should be put to death.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19900G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19900G\"></sup> He is discouraging<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19900H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19900H\"></sup> the soldiers who are left in this city, as well as all the people, by the things he is saying to them. This man is not seeking the good of these people but their ruin.”",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>“He is in your hands,”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19901I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19901I\"></sup> King Zedekiah answered. “The king can do nothing<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19901J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19901J\"></sup> to oppose you.”",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>So they took Jeremiah and put him into the cistern of Malkijah, the king’s son, which was in the courtyard of the guard.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19902K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19902K\"></sup> They lowered Jeremiah by ropes<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19902L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19902L\"></sup> into the cistern; it had no water in it,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19902M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19902M\"></sup> only mud, and Jeremiah sank down into the mud.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19902N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19902N\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>But Ebed-Melek,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19903O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19903O\"></sup> a Cushite, an official<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19903P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19903P\"></sup> in the royal palace, heard that they had put Jeremiah into the cistern. While the king was sitting in the Benjamin Gate,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19903Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19903Q\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Ebed-Melek went out of the palace and said to him,",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>“My lord the king, these men have acted wickedly in all they have done to Jeremiah the prophet. They have thrown him into a cistern,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19905R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19905R\"></sup> where he will starve to death when there is no longer any bread<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19905S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19905S\"></sup> in the city.”",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Then the king commanded Ebed-Melek the Cushite, “Take thirty men from here with you and lift Jeremiah the prophet out of the cistern before he dies.”",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>So Ebed-Melek took the men with him and went to a room under the treasury in the palace. He took some old rags and worn-out clothes from there and let them down with ropes<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19907T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19907T\"></sup> to Jeremiah in the cistern.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Ebed-Melek the Cushite said to Jeremiah, “Put these old rags and worn-out clothes under your arms to pad the ropes.” Jeremiah did so,",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>and they pulled him up with the ropes and lifted him out of the cistern. And Jeremiah remained in the courtyard of the guard.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19909U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19909U\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Then King Zedekiah sent<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19910V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19910V\"></sup> for Jeremiah the prophet and had him brought to the third entrance to the temple of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>. “I am going to ask you something,” the king said to Jeremiah. “Do not hide<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19910W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19910W\"></sup> anything from me.”",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Jeremiah said to Zedekiah, “If I give you an answer, will you not kill me? Even if I did give you counsel, you would not listen to me.”",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>But King Zedekiah swore this oath secretly<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19912X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19912X\"></sup> to Jeremiah: “As surely as the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> lives, who has given us breath,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19912Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19912Y\"></sup> I will neither kill you nor hand you over to those who want to kill you.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19912Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19912Z\"></sup>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Then Jeremiah said to Zedekiah, “This is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> God Almighty, the God of Israel, says: ‘If you surrender<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19913AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19913AA\"></sup> to the officers of the king of Babylon, your life will be spared and this city will not be burned down; you and your family will live.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19913AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19913AB\"></sup>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>But if you will not surrender to the officers of the king of Babylon, this city will be given into the hands<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19914AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19914AC\"></sup> of the Babylonians and they will burn<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19914AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19914AD\"></sup> it down; you yourself will not escape<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19914AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19914AE\"></sup> from them.’”",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>King Zedekiah said to Jeremiah, “I am afraid<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19915AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19915AF\"></sup> of the Jews who have gone over<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19915AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19915AG\"></sup> to the Babylonians, for the Babylonians may hand me over to them and they will mistreat me.”",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>“They will not hand you over,” Jeremiah replied. “Obey<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19916AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19916AH\"></sup> the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> by doing what I tell you. Then it will go well<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19916AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19916AI\"></sup> with you, and your life<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19916AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19916AJ\"></sup> will be spared.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>But if you refuse to surrender, this is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has revealed to me:",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>All the women<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19918AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19918AK\"></sup> left in the palace of the king of Judah will be brought out to the officials of the king of Babylon. Those women will say to you:“‘They misled you and overcame you—those trusted friends<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19918AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19918AL\"></sup> of yours.Your feet are sunk in the mud;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19918AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19918AM\"></sup>your friends have deserted you.’",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>“All your wives and children<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19919AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19919AN\"></sup> will be brought out to the Babylonians. You yourself will not escape<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19919AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19919AO\"></sup> from their hands but will be captured<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19919AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19919AP\"></sup> by the king of Babylon; and this city will be burned down.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19919AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19919AQ\"></sup>",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>Then Zedekiah said to Jeremiah, “Do not let anyone know<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19920AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19920AR\"></sup> about this conversation, or you may die.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>If the officials hear that I talked with you, and they come to you and say, ‘Tell us what you said to the king and what the king said to you; do not hide it from us or we will kill you,’",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>then tell<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19922AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19922AS\"></sup> them, ‘I was pleading with the king not to send me back to Jonathan’s house<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19922AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19922AT\"></sup> to die there.’”",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>All the officials did come to Jeremiah and question him, and he told them everything the king had ordered him to say. So they said no more to him, for no one had heard his conversation with the king.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>And Jeremiah remained in the courtyard of the guard<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19924AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19924AU\"></sup> until the day Jerusalem was captured.This is how Jerusalem<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19924AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19924AW\"></sup> was taken:"
		},
		"39": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum mid-paragraph\">39 </span><sup class=\"versenum mid-paragraph\">1 </sup>In the ninth year of Zedekiah<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19925A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19925A\"></sup> king of Judah, in the tenth month, Nebuchadnezzar<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19925B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19925B\"></sup> king of Babylon marched against Jerusalem with his whole army and laid siege<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19925C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19925C\"></sup> to it.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>And on the ninth day of the fourth<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19926D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19926D\"></sup> month of Zedekiah’s eleventh year, the city wall<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19926E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19926E\"></sup> was broken through.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19926F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19926F\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Then all the officials<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19927G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19927G\"></sup> of the king of Babylon came and took seats in the Middle Gate: Nergal-Sharezer of Samgar, Nebo-Sarsekim a chief officer, Nergal-Sharezer a high official and all the other officials of the king of Babylon.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>When Zedekiah king of Judah and all the soldiers saw them, they fled; they left the city at night by way of the king’s garden, through the gate between the two walls,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19928H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19928H\"></sup> and headed toward the Arabah.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19928I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19928I\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>But the Babylonian army pursued them and overtook Zedekiah<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19929J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19929J\"></sup> in the plains of Jericho. They captured<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19929K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19929K\"></sup> him and took him to Nebuchadnezzar king of Babylon at Riblah<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19929L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19929L\"></sup> in the land of Hamath, where he pronounced sentence on him.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>There at Riblah the king of Babylon slaughtered the sons of Zedekiah before his eyes and also killed all the nobles<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19930M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19930M\"></sup> of Judah.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Then he put out Zedekiah’s eyes<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19931N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19931N\"></sup> and bound him with bronze shackles to take him to Babylon.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19931O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19931O\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>The Babylonians set fire<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19932P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19932P\"></sup> to the royal palace and the houses of the people and broke down the walls<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19932Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19932Q\"></sup> of Jerusalem.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Nebuzaradan commander of the imperial guard carried into exile to Babylon the people who remained in the city, along with those who had gone over to him,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19933R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19933R\"></sup> and the rest of the people.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19933S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19933S\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>But Nebuzaradan the commander of the guard left behind in the land of Judah some of the poor people, who owned nothing; and at that time he gave them vineyards and fields.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Now Nebuchadnezzar king of Babylon had given these orders about Jeremiah through Nebuzaradan commander of the imperial guard:",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>“Take him and look after him; don’t harm<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19936T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19936T\"></sup> him but do for him whatever he asks.”",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>So Nebuzaradan the commander of the guard, Nebushazban a chief officer, Nergal-Sharezer a high official and all the other officers<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19937U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19937U\"></sup> of the king of Babylon",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>sent and had Jeremiah taken out of the courtyard of the guard.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19938V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19938V\"></sup> They turned him over to Gedaliah<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19938W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19938W\"></sup> son of Ahikam,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19938X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19938X\"></sup> the son of Shaphan,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19938Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19938Y\"></sup> to take him back to his home. So he remained among his own people.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19938Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19938Z\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>While Jeremiah had been confined in the courtyard of the guard, the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to him:",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>“Go and tell Ebed-Melek<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19940AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19940AA\"></sup> the Cushite, ‘This is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty, the God of Israel, says: I am about to fulfill my words<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19940AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19940AB\"></sup> against this city—words concerning disaster,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19940AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19940AC\"></sup> not prosperity. At that time they will be fulfilled before your eyes.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>But I will rescue<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19941AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19941AD\"></sup> you on that day, declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>; you will not be given into the hands of those you fear.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>I will save<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19942AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19942AE\"></sup> you; you will not fall by the sword<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19942AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19942AF\"></sup> but will escape with your life,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19942AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19942AG\"></sup> because you trust<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19942AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19942AH\"></sup> in me, declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.’”"
		},
		"40": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">40 </span>The word came to Jeremiah from the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> after Nebuzaradan commander of the imperial guard had released him at Ramah.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19943A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19943A\"></sup> He had found Jeremiah bound in chains among all the captives<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19943B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19943B\"></sup> from Jerusalem and Judah who were being carried into exile to Babylon.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>When the commander<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19944C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19944C\"></sup> of the guard found Jeremiah, he said to him, “The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God decreed<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19944D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19944D\"></sup> this disaster<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19944E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19944E\"></sup> for this place.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19944F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19944F\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>And now the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has brought it about; he has done just as he said he would. All this happened because you people sinned<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19945G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19945G\"></sup> against the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> and did not obey<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19945H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19945H\"></sup> him.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>But today I am freeing<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19946I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19946I\"></sup> you from the chains<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19946J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19946J\"></sup> on your wrists. Come with me to Babylon, if you like, and I will look after you; but if you do not want to, then don’t come. Look, the whole country lies before you; go wherever you please.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19946K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19946K\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>However, before Jeremiah turned to go, Nebuzaradan added, “Go back to Gedaliah<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19947L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19947L\"></sup> son of Ahikam,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19947M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19947M\"></sup> the son of Shaphan, whom the king of Babylon has appointed<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19947N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19947N\"></sup> over the towns<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19947O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19947O\"></sup> of Judah, and live with him among the people, or go anywhere else you please.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19947P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19947P\"></sup>Then the commander gave him provisions and a present<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19947Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19947Q\"></sup> and let him go.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>So Jeremiah went to Gedaliah son of Ahikam at Mizpah<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19948R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19948R\"></sup> and stayed with him among the people who were left behind in the land.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>When all the army officers and their men who were still in the open country heard that the king of Babylon had appointed Gedaliah son of Ahikam as governor<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19949T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19949T\"></sup> over the land and had put him in charge of the men, women and children who were the poorest<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19949U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19949U\"></sup> in the land and who had not been carried into exile to Babylon,",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>they came to Gedaliah at Mizpah<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19950V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19950V\"></sup>—Ishmael<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19950W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19950W\"></sup> son of Nethaniah, Johanan<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19950X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19950X\"></sup> and Jonathan the sons of Kareah, Seraiah son of Tanhumeth, the sons of Ephai the Netophathite,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19950Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19950Y\"></sup> and Jaazaniah the son of the Maakathite,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19950Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19950Z\"></sup> and their men.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Gedaliah son of Ahikam, the son of Shaphan, took an oath to reassure them and their men. “Do not be afraid to serve<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19951AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19951AA\"></sup> the Babylonians,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19951AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19951AB\"></sup>” he said. “Settle down in the land and serve the king of Babylon, and it will go well with you.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19951AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19951AC\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>I myself will stay at Mizpah<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19952AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19952AD\"></sup> to represent you before the Babylonians who come to us, but you are to harvest the wine,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19952AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19952AE\"></sup> summer fruit and olive oil, and put them in your storage jars,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19952AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19952AF\"></sup> and live in the towns you have taken over.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19952AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19952AG\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>When all the Jews in Moab,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19953AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19953AH\"></sup> Ammon, Edom<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19953AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19953AI\"></sup> and all the other countries<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19953AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19953AJ\"></sup> heard that the king of Babylon had left a remnant in Judah and had appointed Gedaliah son of Ahikam, the son of Shaphan, as governor over them,",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>they all came back to the land of Judah, to Gedaliah at Mizpah, from all the countries where they had been scattered.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19954AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19954AK\"></sup> And they harvested an abundance of wine and summer fruit.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Johanan<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19955AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19955AL\"></sup> son of Kareah and all the army officers still in the open country came to Gedaliah at Mizpah<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19955AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19955AM\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>and said to him, “Don’t you know that Baalis king of the Ammonites<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19956AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19956AN\"></sup> has sent Ishmael<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19956AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19956AO\"></sup> son of Nethaniah to take your life?” But Gedaliah son of Ahikam did not believe them.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Then Johanan<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19957AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19957AP\"></sup> son of Kareah said privately to Gedaliah in Mizpah, “Let me go and kill<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19957AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19957AQ\"></sup> Ishmael son of Nethaniah, and no one will know it. Why should he take your life and cause all the Jews who are gathered around you to be scattered<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19957AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19957AR\"></sup> and the remnant<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19957AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19957AS\"></sup> of Judah to perish?”",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>But Gedaliah son of Ahikam said to Johanan<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19958AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19958AT\"></sup> son of Kareah, “Don’t do such a thing! What you are saying about Ishmael is not true.”"
		},
		"41": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">41 </span>In the seventh month Ishmael<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19959A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19959A\"></sup> son of Nethaniah, the son of Elishama, who was of royal blood and had been one of the king’s officers, came with ten men to Gedaliah son of Ahikam at Mizpah. While they were eating together there,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Ishmael<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19960B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19960B\"></sup> son of Nethaniah and the ten men who were with him got up and struck down Gedaliah son of Ahikam, the son of Shaphan, with the sword,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19960C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19960C\"></sup> killing the one whom the king of Babylon had appointed<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19960D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19960D\"></sup> as governor over the land.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19960E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19960E\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Ishmael also killed all the men of Judah who were with Gedaliah at Mizpah, as well as the Babylonian soldiers who were there.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>The day after Gedaliah’s assassination, before anyone knew about it,",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>eighty men who had shaved off their beards,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19963F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19963F\"></sup> torn their clothes<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19963G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19963G\"></sup> and cut<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19963H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19963H\"></sup> themselves came from Shechem,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19963I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19963I\"></sup> Shiloh<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19963J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19963J\"></sup> and Samaria,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19963K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19963K\"></sup> bringing grain offerings and incense<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19963L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19963L\"></sup> with them to the house of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19963M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19963M\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Ishmael son of Nethaniah went out from Mizpah to meet them, weeping<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19964N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19964N\"></sup> as he went. When he met them, he said, “Come to Gedaliah son of Ahikam.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19964O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19964O\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>When they went into the city, Ishmael son of Nethaniah and the men who were with him slaughtered them and threw them into a cistern.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19965P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19965P\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>But ten of them said to Ishmael, “Don’t kill us! We have wheat and barley, olive oil and honey, hidden in a field.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19966Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19966Q\"></sup> So he let them alone and did not kill them with the others.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Now the cistern where he threw all the bodies of the men he had killed along with Gedaliah was the one King Asa<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19967R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19967R\"></sup> had made as part of his defense<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19967S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19967S\"></sup> against Baasha<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19967T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19967T\"></sup> king of Israel. Ishmael son of Nethaniah filled it with the dead.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Ishmael made captives of all the rest of the people<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19968U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19968U\"></sup> who were in Mizpah—the king’s daughters<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19968V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19968V\"></sup> along with all the others who were left there, over whom Nebuzaradan commander of the imperial guard had appointed Gedaliah son of Ahikam. Ishmael son of Nethaniah took them captive and set out to cross over to the Ammonites.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19968W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19968W\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>When Johanan<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19969X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19969X\"></sup> son of Kareah and all the army officers who were with him heard about all the crimes Ishmael son of Nethaniah had committed,",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>they took all their men and went to fight<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19970Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19970Y\"></sup> Ishmael son of Nethaniah. They caught up with him near the great pool<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19970Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19970Z\"></sup> in Gibeon.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>When all the people<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19971AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19971AA\"></sup> Ishmael had with him saw Johanan son of Kareah and the army officers who were with him, they were glad.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>All the people Ishmael had taken captive at Mizpah<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19972AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19972AB\"></sup> turned and went over to Johanan son of Kareah.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>But Ishmael son of Nethaniah and eight of his men escaped<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19973AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19973AC\"></sup> from Johanan and fled to the Ammonites.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Then Johanan son of Kareah and all the army officers<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19974AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19974AD\"></sup> who were with him led away all the people of Mizpah who had survived,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19974AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19974AE\"></sup> whom Johanan had recovered from Ishmael son of Nethaniah after Ishmael had assassinated Gedaliah son of Ahikam—the soldiers, women, children and court officials he had recovered from Gibeon.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>And they went on, stopping at Geruth Kimham<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19975AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19975AF\"></sup> near Bethlehem<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19975AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19975AG\"></sup> on their way to Egypt<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19975AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19975AH\"></sup>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>to escape the Babylonians. They were afraid<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19976AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19976AI\"></sup> of them because Ishmael son of Nethaniah had killed Gedaliah<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19976AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19976AJ\"></sup> son of Ahikam, whom the king of Babylon had appointed as governor over the land."
		},
		"42": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">42 </span>Then all the army officers, including Johanan<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19977A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19977A\"></sup> son of Kareah and Jezaniah son of Hoshaiah,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19977B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19977B\"></sup> and all the people from the least to the greatest<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19977C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19977C\"></sup> approached",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Jeremiah the prophet and said to him, “Please hear our petition and pray<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19978D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19978D\"></sup> to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God for this entire remnant.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19978E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19978E\"></sup> For as you now see, though we were once many, now only a few<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19978F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19978F\"></sup> are left.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Pray that the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God will tell us where we should go and what we should do.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19979G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19979G\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>“I have heard you,” replied Jeremiah the prophet. “I will certainly pray<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19980H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19980H\"></sup> to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God as you have requested; I will tell<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19980I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19980I\"></sup> you everything the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says and will keep nothing back from you.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19980J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19980J\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Then they said to Jeremiah, “May the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> be a true<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19981K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19981K\"></sup> and faithful<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19981L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19981L\"></sup> witness<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19981M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19981M\"></sup> against us if we do not act in accordance with everything the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God sends you to tell us.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Whether it is favorable or unfavorable, we will obey the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> our God, to whom we are sending you, so that it will go well<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19982N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19982N\"></sup> with us, for we will obey<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19982O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19982O\"></sup> the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> our God.”",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Ten days later the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to Jeremiah.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>So he called together Johanan son of Kareah and all the army officers<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19984P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19984P\"></sup> who were with him and all the people from the least to the greatest.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19984Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19984Q\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>He said to them, “This is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, the God of Israel, to whom you sent me to present your petition,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19985R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19985R\"></sup> says:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19985S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19985S\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>‘If you stay in this land,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19986T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19986T\"></sup> I will build<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19986U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19986U\"></sup> you up and not tear you down; I will plant<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19986V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19986V\"></sup> you and not uproot you,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19986W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19986W\"></sup> for I have relented concerning the disaster I have inflicted on you.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19986X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19986X\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Do not be afraid of the king of Babylon,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19987Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19987Y\"></sup> whom you now fear.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19987Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19987Z\"></sup> Do not be afraid of him, declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, for I am with you and will save<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19987AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19987AA\"></sup> you and deliver you from his hands.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19987AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19987AB\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>I will show you compassion<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19988AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19988AC\"></sup> so that he will have compassion on you and restore you to your land.’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19988AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19988AD\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>“However, if you say, ‘We will not stay in this land,’ and so disobey<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19989AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19989AE\"></sup> the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God,",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>and if you say, ‘No, we will go and live in Egypt,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19990AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19990AF\"></sup> where we will not see war or hear the trumpet<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19990AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19990AG\"></sup> or be hungry for bread,’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19990AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19990AH\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>then hear the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19991AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19991AI\"></sup> you remnant of Judah. This is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty, the God of Israel, says: ‘If you are determined to go to Egypt and you do go to settle there,",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>then the sword<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19992AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19992AJ\"></sup> you fear<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19992AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19992AK\"></sup> will overtake you there, and the famine<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19992AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19992AL\"></sup> you dread will follow you into Egypt, and there you will die.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19992AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19992AM\"></sup>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Indeed, all who are determined to go to Egypt to settle there will die by the sword, famine and plague;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19993AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19993AN\"></sup> not one of them will survive or escape the disaster I will bring on them.’",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>This is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty, the God of Israel, says: ‘As my anger and wrath<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19994AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19994AO\"></sup> have been poured out on those who lived in Jerusalem,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19994AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19994AP\"></sup> so will my wrath be poured out on you when you go to Egypt. You will be a curse<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19994AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19994AQ\"></sup> and an object of horror,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19994AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19994AR\"></sup> a curse and an object of reproach;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19994AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19994AS\"></sup> you will never see this place again.’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19994AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19994AT\"></sup>",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>“Remnant<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19995AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19995AU\"></sup> of Judah, the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has told you, ‘Do not go to Egypt.’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19995AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19995AV\"></sup> Be sure of this: I warn you today",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>that you made a fatal mistake when you sent me to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God and said, ‘Pray to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> our God for us; tell us everything he says and we will do it.’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19996AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19996AW\"></sup>",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>I have told you today, but you still have not obeyed the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God in all he sent me to tell you.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19997AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19997AX\"></sup>",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>So now, be sure of this: You will die by the sword, famine<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19998AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19998AY\"></sup> and plague<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19998AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19998AZ\"></sup> in the place where you want to go to settle.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19998BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19998BA\"></sup>"
		},
		"43": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">43 </span>When Jeremiah had finished telling the people all the words of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> their God—everything the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> had sent him to tell them<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-19999A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-19999A\"></sup>—",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Azariah son of Hoshaiah<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20000B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20000B\"></sup> and Johanan<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20000C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20000C\"></sup> son of Kareah and all the arrogant<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20000D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20000D\"></sup> men said to Jeremiah, “You are lying!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20000E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20000E\"></sup> The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> our God has not sent you to say, ‘You must not go to Egypt to settle there.’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20000F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20000F\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>But Baruch<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20001G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20001G\"></sup> son of Neriah is inciting you against us to hand us over to the Babylonians, so they may kill us or carry us into exile to Babylon.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20001H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20001H\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>So Johanan son of Kareah and all the army officers and all the people<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20002I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20002I\"></sup> disobeyed the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>’s command<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20002J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20002J\"></sup> to stay in the land of Judah.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20002K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20002K\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Instead, Johanan son of Kareah and all the army officers led away all the remnant of Judah who had come back to live in the land of Judah from all the nations where they had been scattered.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20003L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20003L\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>They also led away all those whom Nebuzaradan commander of the imperial guard had left with Gedaliah son of Ahikam, the son of Shaphan—the men, the women,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20004M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20004M\"></sup> the children and the king’s daughters. And they took Jeremiah the prophet and Baruch<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20004N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20004N\"></sup> son of Neriah along with them.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>So they entered Egypt<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20005O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20005O\"></sup> in disobedience to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> and went as far as Tahpanhes.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20005P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20005P\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>In Tahpanhes<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20006Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20006Q\"></sup> the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to Jeremiah:",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>“While the Jews are watching, take some large stones<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20007R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20007R\"></sup> with you and bury them in clay in the brick<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20007S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20007S\"></sup> pavement at the entrance to Pharaoh’s palace<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20007T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20007T\"></sup> in Tahpanhes.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Then say to them, ‘This is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty, the God of Israel, says: I will send for my servant<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20008U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20008U\"></sup> Nebuchadnezzar<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20008V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20008V\"></sup> king of Babylon, and I will set his throne<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20008W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20008W\"></sup> over these stones I have buried here; he will spread his royal canopy<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20008X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20008X\"></sup> above them.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>He will come and attack Egypt,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20009Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20009Y\"></sup> bringing death<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20009Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20009Z\"></sup> to those destined<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20009AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20009AA\"></sup> for death, captivity to those destined for captivity,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20009AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20009AB\"></sup> and the sword to those destined for the sword.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20009AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20009AC\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>He will set fire<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20010AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20010AD\"></sup> to the temples<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20010AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20010AE\"></sup> of the gods<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20010AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20010AF\"></sup> of Egypt; he will burn their temples and take their gods captive.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20010AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20010AG\"></sup> As a shepherd picks<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20010AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20010AH\"></sup> his garment clean of lice, so he will pick Egypt clean and depart.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>There in the temple of the sun<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20011AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20011AI\"></sup> in Egypt he will demolish the sacred pillars<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20011AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20011AJ\"></sup> and will burn down the temples of the gods of Egypt.’”"
		},
		"44": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">44 </span>This word came to Jeremiah concerning all the Jews living in Lower Egypt<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20012A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20012A\"></sup>—in Migdol,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20012B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20012B\"></sup> Tahpanhes<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20012C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20012C\"></sup> and Memphis<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20012D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20012D\"></sup>—and in Upper Egypt:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20012E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20012E\"></sup>",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“This is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty, the God of Israel, says: You saw the great disaster<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20013F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20013F\"></sup> I brought on Jerusalem and on all the towns of Judah.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20013G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20013G\"></sup> Today they lie deserted and in ruins<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20013H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20013H\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>because of the evil<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20014I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20014I\"></sup> they have done. They aroused my anger<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20014J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20014J\"></sup> by burning incense<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20014K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20014K\"></sup> to and worshiping other gods<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20014L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20014L\"></sup> that neither they nor you nor your ancestors<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20014M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20014M\"></sup> ever knew.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Again and again<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20015N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20015N\"></sup> I sent my servants the prophets,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20015O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20015O\"></sup> who said, ‘Do not do this detestable<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20015P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20015P\"></sup> thing that I hate!’",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>But they did not listen or pay attention;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20016Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20016Q\"></sup> they did not turn from their wickedness<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20016R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20016R\"></sup> or stop burning incense<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20016S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20016S\"></sup> to other gods.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20016T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20016T\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Therefore, my fierce anger was poured out;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20017U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20017U\"></sup> it raged against the towns of Judah and the streets of Jerusalem and made them the desolate ruins<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20017V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20017V\"></sup> they are today.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>“Now this is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> God Almighty, the God of Israel, says: Why bring such great disaster<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20018W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20018W\"></sup> on yourselves by cutting off from Judah the men and women,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20018X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20018X\"></sup> the children and infants, and so leave yourselves without a remnant?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20018Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20018Y\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Why arouse my anger with what your hands have made,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20019Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20019Z\"></sup> burning incense<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20019AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20019AA\"></sup> to other gods in Egypt,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20019AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20019AB\"></sup> where you have come to live?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20019AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20019AC\"></sup> You will destroy yourselves and make yourselves a curse and an object of reproach<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20019AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20019AD\"></sup> among all the nations on earth.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Have you forgotten the wickedness committed by your ancestors<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20020AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20020AE\"></sup> and by the kings<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20020AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20020AF\"></sup> and queens<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20020AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20020AG\"></sup> of Judah and the wickedness committed by you and your wives<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20020AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20020AH\"></sup> in the land of Judah and the streets of Jerusalem?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20020AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20020AI\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>To this day they have not humbled<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20021AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20021AJ\"></sup> themselves or shown reverence,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20021AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20021AK\"></sup> nor have they followed my law<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20021AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20021AL\"></sup> and the decrees<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20021AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20021AM\"></sup> I set before you and your ancestors.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20021AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20021AN\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>“Therefore this is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20022AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20022AO\"></sup> the God of Israel, says: I am determined to bring disaster<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20022AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20022AP\"></sup> on you and to destroy all Judah.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>I will take away the remnant<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20023AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20023AQ\"></sup> of Judah who were determined to go to Egypt to settle there. They will all perish in Egypt; they will fall by the sword or die from famine. From the least to the greatest,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20023AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20023AR\"></sup> they will die by sword or famine.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20023AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20023AS\"></sup> They will become a curse and an object of horror, a curse and an object of reproach.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20023AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20023AT\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>I will punish<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20024AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20024AU\"></sup> those who live in Egypt with the sword,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20024AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20024AV\"></sup> famine and plague,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20024AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20024AW\"></sup> as I punished Jerusalem.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>None of the remnant of Judah who have gone to live in Egypt will escape or survive to return to the land of Judah, to which they long to return and live; none will return except a few fugitives.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20025AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20025AX\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Then all the men who knew that their wives<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20026AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20026AY\"></sup> were burning incense<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20026AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20026AZ\"></sup> to other gods, along with all the women<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20026BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20026BA\"></sup> who were present—a large assembly—and all the people living in Lower and Upper Egypt,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20026BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20026BB\"></sup> said to Jeremiah,",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>“We will not listen<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20027BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20027BC\"></sup> to the message you have spoken to us in the name of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20027BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20027BD\"></sup>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>We will certainly do everything we said we would:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20028BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20028BE\"></sup> We will burn incense<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20028BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20028BF\"></sup> to the Queen of Heaven<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20028BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20028BG\"></sup> and will pour out drink offerings to her just as we and our ancestors, our kings and our officials<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20028BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20028BH\"></sup> did in the towns of Judah and in the streets of Jerusalem.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20028BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20028BI\"></sup> At that time we had plenty of food<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20028BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20028BJ\"></sup> and were well off and suffered no harm.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20028BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20028BK\"></sup>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>But ever since we stopped burning incense to the Queen of Heaven and pouring out drink offerings<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20029BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20029BL\"></sup> to her, we have had nothing and have been perishing by sword and famine.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20029BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20029BM\"></sup>”",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>The women added, “When we burned incense<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20030BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20030BN\"></sup> to the Queen of Heaven<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20030BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20030BO\"></sup> and poured out drink offerings to her, did not our husbands<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20030BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20030BP\"></sup> know that we were making cakes<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20030BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20030BQ\"></sup> impressed with her image<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20030BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20030BR\"></sup> and pouring out drink offerings to her?”",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Then Jeremiah said to all the people, both men and women, who were answering him,",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>“Did not the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> remember<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20032BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20032BS\"></sup> and call to mind the incense<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20032BT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BT&quot;&gt;BT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20032BT\"></sup> burned in the towns of Judah and the streets of Jerusalem<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20032BU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BU&quot;&gt;BU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20032BU\"></sup> by you and your ancestors,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20032BV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BV&quot;&gt;BV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20032BV\"></sup> your kings and your officials and the people of the land?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20032BW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BW&quot;&gt;BW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20032BW\"></sup>",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>When the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> could no longer endure<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20033BX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BX&quot;&gt;BX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20033BX\"></sup> your wicked actions and the detestable things you did, your land became a curse<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20033BY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BY&quot;&gt;BY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20033BY\"></sup> and a desolate waste<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20033BZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BZ&quot;&gt;BZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20033BZ\"></sup> without inhabitants, as it is today.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20033CA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CA&quot;&gt;CA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20033CA\"></sup>",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>Because you have burned incense and have sinned against the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> and have not obeyed him or followed<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20034CB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CB&quot;&gt;CB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20034CB\"></sup> his law or his decrees<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20034CC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CC&quot;&gt;CC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20034CC\"></sup> or his stipulations, this disaster<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20034CD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CD&quot;&gt;CD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20034CD\"></sup> has come upon you, as you now see.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20034CE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CE&quot;&gt;CE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20034CE\"></sup>",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>Then Jeremiah said to all the people, including the women,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20035CF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CF&quot;&gt;CF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20035CF\"></sup> “Hear the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, all you people of Judah in Egypt.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20035CG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CG&quot;&gt;CG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20035CG\"></sup>",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>This is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty, the God of Israel, says: You and your wives<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20036CH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CH&quot;&gt;CH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20036CH\"></sup> have done what you said you would do when you promised, ‘We will certainly carry out the vows we made to burn incense and pour out drink offerings to the Queen of Heaven.’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20036CI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CI&quot;&gt;CI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20036CI\"></sup>“Go ahead then, do what you promised! Keep your vows!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20036CJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CJ&quot;&gt;CJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20036CJ\"></sup>",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>But hear the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, all you Jews living in Egypt:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20037CK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CK&quot;&gt;CK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20037CK\"></sup> ‘I swear<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20037CL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CL&quot;&gt;CL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20037CL\"></sup> by my great name,’ says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, ‘that no one from Judah living anywhere in Egypt will ever again invoke my name or swear, “As surely as the Sovereign<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20037CM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CM&quot;&gt;CM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20037CM\"></sup> <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> lives.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20037CN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CN&quot;&gt;CN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20037CN\"></sup>",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>For I am watching<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20038CO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CO&quot;&gt;CO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20038CO\"></sup> over them for harm,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20038CP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CP&quot;&gt;CP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20038CP\"></sup> not for good; the Jews in Egypt will perish<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20038CQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CQ&quot;&gt;CQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20038CQ\"></sup> by sword and famine<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20038CR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CR&quot;&gt;CR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20038CR\"></sup> until they are all destroyed.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20038CS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CS&quot;&gt;CS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20038CS\"></sup>",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>Those who escape the sword<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20039CT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CT&quot;&gt;CT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20039CT\"></sup> and return to the land of Judah from Egypt will be very few.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20039CU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CU&quot;&gt;CU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20039CU\"></sup> Then the whole remnant<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20039CV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CV&quot;&gt;CV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20039CV\"></sup> of Judah who came to live in Egypt will know whose word will stand<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20039CW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CW&quot;&gt;CW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20039CW\"></sup>—mine or theirs.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20039CX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CX&quot;&gt;CX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20039CX\"></sup>",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>“‘This will be the sign<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20040CY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CY&quot;&gt;CY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20040CY\"></sup> to you that I will punish<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20040CZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CZ&quot;&gt;CZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20040CZ\"></sup> you in this place,’ declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, ‘so that you will know that my threats of harm against you will surely stand.’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20040DA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DA&quot;&gt;DA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20040DA\"></sup>",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>This is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says: ‘I am going to deliver Pharaoh<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20041DB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DB&quot;&gt;DB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20041DB\"></sup> Hophra king of Egypt into the hands of his enemies who want to kill him, just as I gave Zedekiah<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20041DC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DC&quot;&gt;DC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20041DC\"></sup> king of Judah into the hands of Nebuchadnezzar king of Babylon, the enemy who wanted to kill him.’”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20041DD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DD&quot;&gt;DD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20041DD\"></sup>"
		},
		"45": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">45 </span>When Baruch<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20042A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20042A\"></sup> son of Neriah<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20042B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20042B\"></sup> wrote on a scroll<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20042C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20042C\"></sup> the words Jeremiah the prophet dictated in the fourth year of Jehoiakim<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20042D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20042D\"></sup> son of Josiah king of Judah, Jeremiah said this to Baruch:",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“This is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, the God of Israel, says to you, Baruch:",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>You said, ‘Woe<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20044E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20044E\"></sup> to me! The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has added sorrow<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20044F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20044F\"></sup> to my pain;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20044G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20044G\"></sup> I am worn out with groaning<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20044H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20044H\"></sup> and find no rest.’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20044I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20044I\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>But the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has told me to say to you, ‘This is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says: I will overthrow what I have built and uproot<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20045J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20045J\"></sup> what I have planted,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20045K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20045K\"></sup> throughout the earth.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20045L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20045L\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Should you then seek great<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20046M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20046M\"></sup> things for yourself? Do not seek them.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20046N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20046N\"></sup> For I will bring disaster<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20046O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20046O\"></sup> on all people,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20046P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20046P\"></sup> declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, but wherever you go I will let you escape<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20046Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20046Q\"></sup> with your life.’”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20046R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20046R\"></sup>"
		},
		"46": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">46 </span>This is the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> that came to Jeremiah the prophet concerning the nations:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20047A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20047A\"></sup>",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Concerning Egypt:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20048B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20048B\"></sup>This is the message against the army of Pharaoh Necho<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20048C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20048C\"></sup> king of Egypt, which was defeated at Carchemish<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20048D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20048D\"></sup> on the Euphrates<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20048E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20048E\"></sup> River by Nebuchadnezzar king of Babylon in the fourth year of Jehoiakim<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20048F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20048F\"></sup> son of Josiah king of Judah:",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>“Prepare your shields,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20049G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20049G\"></sup> both large and small,and march out for battle!",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Harness the horses,mount the steeds!Take your positionswith helmets on!Polish<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20050H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20050H\"></sup> your spears,put on your armor!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20050I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20050I\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>What do I see?They are terrified,they are retreating,their warriors are defeated.They flee<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20051J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20051J\"></sup> in hastewithout looking back,and there is terror<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20051K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20051K\"></sup> on every side,”declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>“The swift cannot flee<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20052L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20052L\"></sup>nor the strong escape.In the north by the River Euphrates<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20052M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20052M\"></sup>they stumble and fall.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20052N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20052N\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>“Who is this that rises like the Nile,like rivers of surging waters?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20053O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20053O\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Egypt rises like the Nile,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20054P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20054P\"></sup>like rivers of surging waters.She says, ‘I will rise and cover the earth;I will destroy cities and their people.’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20054Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20054Q\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Charge, you horses!Drive furiously, you charioteers!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20055R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20055R\"></sup>March on, you warriors—men of Cush<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20055S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20055S\"></sup> and Put who carry shields,men of Lydia<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20055T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20055T\"></sup> who draw the bow.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>But that day<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20056U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20056U\"></sup> belongs to the Lord, the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty—a day of vengeance<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20056V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20056V\"></sup>, for vengeance on his foes.The sword will devour<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20056W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20056W\"></sup> till it is satisfied,till it has quenched its thirst with blood.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20056X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20056X\"></sup>For the Lord, the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty, will offer sacrifice<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20056Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20056Y\"></sup>in the land of the north by the River Euphrates.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20056Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20056Z\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>“Go up to Gilead and get balm,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20057AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20057AA\"></sup>Virgin<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20057AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20057AB\"></sup> Daughter Egypt.But you try many medicines in vain;there is no healing<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20057AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20057AC\"></sup> for you.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>The nations will hear of your shame;your cries will fill the earth.One warrior will stumble over another;both will fall<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20058AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20058AD\"></sup> down together.”",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>This is the message the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> spoke to Jeremiah the prophet about the coming of Nebuchadnezzar king of Babylon<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20059AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20059AE\"></sup> to attack Egypt:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20059AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20059AF\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>“Announce this in Egypt, and proclaim it in Migdol;proclaim it also in Memphis<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20060AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20060AG\"></sup> and Tahpanhes:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20060AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20060AH\"></sup>‘Take your positions and get ready,for the sword devours<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20060AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20060AI\"></sup> those around you.’",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Why will your warriors be laid low?They cannot stand, for the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will push them down.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20061AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20061AJ\"></sup>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>They will stumble<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20062AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20062AK\"></sup> repeatedly;they will fall<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20062AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20062AL\"></sup> over each other.They will say, ‘Get up, let us go backto our own people<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20062AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20062AM\"></sup> and our native lands,away from the sword of the oppressor.’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20062AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20062AN\"></sup>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>There they will exclaim,‘Pharaoh king of Egypt is only a loud noise;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20063AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20063AO\"></sup>he has missed his opportunity.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20063AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20063AP\"></sup>’",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>“As surely as I live,” declares the King,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20064AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20064AQ\"></sup>whose name is the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty,“one will come who is like Tabor<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20064AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20064AR\"></sup> among the mountains,like Carmel<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20064AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20064AS\"></sup> by the sea.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>Pack your belongings for exile,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20065AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20065AT\"></sup>you who live in Egypt,for Memphis<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20065AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20065AU\"></sup> will be laid waste<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20065AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20065AV\"></sup>and lie in ruins without inhabitant.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>“Egypt is a beautiful heifer,but a gadfly is comingagainst her from the north.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20066AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20066AW\"></sup>",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>The mercenaries<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20067AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20067AX\"></sup> in her ranksare like fattened calves.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20067AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20067AY\"></sup>They too will turn and flee<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20067AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20067AZ\"></sup> together,they will not stand their ground,for the day<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20067BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20067BA\"></sup> of disaster is coming upon them,the time<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20067BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20067BB\"></sup> for them to be punished.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Egypt will hiss like a fleeing serpentas the enemy advances in force;they will come against her with axes,like men who cut down trees.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20068BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20068BC\"></sup>",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>They will chop down her forest,”declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,“dense though it be.They are more numerous than locusts,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20069BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20069BD\"></sup>they cannot be counted.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>Daughter Egypt will be put to shame,given into the hands of the people of the north.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20070BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20070BE\"></sup>”",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty, the God of Israel, says: “I am about to bring punishment on Amon god of Thebes,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20071BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20071BF\"></sup> on Pharaoh,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20071BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20071BG\"></sup> on Egypt and her gods<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20071BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20071BH\"></sup> and her kings, and on those who rely<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20071BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20071BI\"></sup> on Pharaoh.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>I will give them into the hands<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20072BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20072BJ\"></sup> of those who want to kill them—Nebuchadnezzar king<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20072BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20072BK\"></sup> of Babylon and his officers. Later, however, Egypt will be inhabited<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20072BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20072BL\"></sup> as in times past,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>“Do not be afraid,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20073BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20073BM\"></sup> Jacob<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20073BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20073BN\"></sup> my servant;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20073BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20073BO\"></sup>do not be dismayed, Israel.I will surely save you out of a distant place,your descendants from the land of their exile.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20073BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20073BP\"></sup>Jacob will again have peace and security,and no one will make him afraid.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>Do not be afraid, Jacob my servant,for I am with you,”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20074BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20074BQ\"></sup> declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.“Though I completely destroy<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20074BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20074BR\"></sup> all the nationsamong which I scatter you,I will not completely destroy you.I will discipline you but only in due measure;I will not let you go entirely unpunished.”"
		},
		"47": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">47 </span>This is the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> that came to Jeremiah the prophet concerning the Philistines<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20075A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20075A\"></sup> before Pharaoh attacked Gaza:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20075B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20075B\"></sup>",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>This is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says:“See how the waters are rising in the north;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20076C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20076C\"></sup>they will become an overflowing torrent.They will overflow the land and everything in it,the towns and those who live in them.The people will cry out;all who dwell in the land will wail<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20076D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20076D\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>at the sound of the hooves of galloping steeds,at the noise of enemy chariots<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20077E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20077E\"></sup>and the rumble of their wheels.Parents will not turn to help their children;their hands will hang limp.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20077F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20077F\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>For the day has cometo destroy all the Philistinesand to remove all survivorswho could help Tyre<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20078G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20078G\"></sup> and Sidon.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20078H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20078H\"></sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> is about to destroy the Philistines,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20078I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20078I\"></sup>the remnant from the coasts of Caphtor.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20078J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20078J\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Gaza will shave<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20079K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20079K\"></sup> her head in mourning;Ashkelon<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20079L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20079L\"></sup> will be silenced.You remnant on the plain,how long will you cut<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20079M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20079M\"></sup> yourselves?",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>“‘Alas, sword<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20080N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20080N\"></sup> of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,how long till you rest?Return to your sheath;cease and be still.’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20080O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20080O\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>But how can it restwhen the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has commanded it,when he has ordered itto attack Ashkelon and the coast?”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20081P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20081P\"></sup>"
		},
		"48": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">48 </span>Concerning Moab:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20082B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20082B\"></sup>This is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty, the God of Israel, says:“Woe to Nebo,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20082C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20082C\"></sup> for it will be ruined.Kiriathaim<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20082D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20082D\"></sup> will be disgraced and captured;the stronghold will be disgraced and shattered.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Moab will be praised<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20083E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20083E\"></sup> no more;in Heshbon<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20083F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20083F\"></sup> people will plot her downfall:‘Come, let us put an end to that nation.’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20083G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20083G\"></sup>You, the people of Madmen, will also be silenced;the sword will pursue you.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Cries of anguish arise from Horonaim,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20084H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20084H\"></sup>cries of great havoc and destruction.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Moab will be broken;her little ones will cry out.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>They go up the hill to Luhith,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20086I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20086I\"></sup>weeping bitterly as they go;on the road down to Horonaim<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20086J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20086J\"></sup>anguished cries over the destruction are heard.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Flee!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20087K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20087K\"></sup> Run for your lives;become like a bush in the desert.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20087L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20087L\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Since you trust in your deeds and riches,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20088M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20088M\"></sup>you too will be taken captive,and Chemosh<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20088N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20088N\"></sup> will go into exile,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20088O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20088O\"></sup>together with his priests and officials.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20088P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20088P\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>The destroyer<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20089Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20089Q\"></sup> will come against every town,and not a town will escape.The valley will be ruinedand the plateau<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20089R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20089R\"></sup> destroyed,because the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has spoken.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Put salt<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20090S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20090S\"></sup> on Moab,for she will be laid waste;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20090T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20090T\"></sup>her towns will become desolate,with no one to live in them.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>“A curse on anyone who is lax in doing the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>’s work!A curse on anyone who keeps their sword<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20091U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20091U\"></sup> from bloodshed!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20091V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20091V\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>“Moab has been at rest<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20092W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20092W\"></sup> from youth,like wine left on its dregs,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20092X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20092X\"></sup>not poured from one jar to another—she has not gone into exile.So she tastes as she did,and her aroma is unchanged.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>But days are coming,”declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,“when I will send men who pour from pitchers,and they will pour her out;they will empty her pitchersand smash her jars.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Then Moab will be ashamed<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20094Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20094Y\"></sup> of Chemosh,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20094Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20094Z\"></sup>as Israel was ashamedwhen they trusted in Bethel.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20094AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20094AA\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>“How can you say, ‘We are warriors,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20095AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20095AB\"></sup>men valiant in battle’?",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Moab will be destroyed and her towns invaded;her finest young men<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20096AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20096AC\"></sup> will go down in the slaughter,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20096AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20096AD\"></sup>”declares the King,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20096AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20096AE\"></sup> whose name is the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20096AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20096AF\"></sup>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>“The fall of Moab is at hand;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20097AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20097AG\"></sup>her calamity will come quickly.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Mourn for her, all who live around her,all who know her fame;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20098AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20098AH\"></sup>say, ‘How broken is the mighty scepter,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20098AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20098AI\"></sup>how broken the glorious staff!’",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>“Come down from your gloryand sit on the parched ground,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20099AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20099AJ\"></sup>you inhabitants of Daughter Dibon,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20099AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20099AK\"></sup>for the one who destroys Moabwill come up against youand ruin your fortified cities.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20099AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20099AL\"></sup>",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>Stand by the road and watch,you who live in Aroer.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20100AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20100AM\"></sup>Ask the man fleeing and the woman escaping,ask them, ‘What has happened?’",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Moab is disgraced, for she is shattered.Wail<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20101AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20101AN\"></sup> and cry out!Announce by the Arnon<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20101AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20101AO\"></sup>that Moab is destroyed.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>Judgment has come to the plateau<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20102AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20102AP\"></sup>—to Holon,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20102AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20102AQ\"></sup> Jahzah<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20102AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20102AR\"></sup> and Mephaath,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20102AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20102AS\"></sup>",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup><span class=\"indent-1-breaks\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>to Dibon,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20103AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20103AT\"></sup> Nebo<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20103AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20103AU\"></sup> and Beth Diblathaim,",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup><span class=\"indent-1-breaks\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>to Kiriathaim,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20104AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20104AV\"></sup> Beth Gamul and Beth Meon,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20104AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20104AW\"></sup>",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup><span class=\"indent-1-breaks\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>to Kerioth<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20105AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20105AX\"></sup> and Bozrah<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20105AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20105AY\"></sup>—to all the towns<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20105AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20105AZ\"></sup> of Moab, far and near.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>Moab’s horn<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20106BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20106BA\"></sup> is cut off;her arm<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20106BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20106BB\"></sup> is broken,”declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>“Make her drunk,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20107BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20107BC\"></sup>for she has defied<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20107BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20107BD\"></sup> the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.Let Moab wallow in her vomit;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20107BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20107BE\"></sup>let her be an object of ridicule.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20107BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20107BF\"></sup>",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>Was not Israel the object of your ridicule?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20108BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20108BG\"></sup>Was she caught among thieves,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20108BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20108BH\"></sup>that you shake your head<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20108BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20108BI\"></sup> in scorn<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20108BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20108BJ\"></sup>whenever you speak of her?",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>Abandon your towns and dwell among the rocks,you who live in Moab.Be like a dove<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20109BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20109BK\"></sup> that makes its nestat the mouth of a cave.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20109BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20109BL\"></sup>",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>“We have heard of Moab’s pride<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20110BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20110BM\"></sup>—how great is her arrogance!—of her insolence, her pride, her conceitand the haughtiness<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20110BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20110BN\"></sup> of her heart.",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>I know her insolence but it is futile,”declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,“and her boasts<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20111BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20111BO\"></sup> accomplish nothing.",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>Therefore I wail<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20112BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20112BP\"></sup> over Moab,for all Moab I cry out,I moan for the people of Kir Hareseth.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20112BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20112BQ\"></sup>",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>I weep for you, as Jazer<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20113BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20113BR\"></sup> weeps,you vines of Sibmah.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20113BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20113BS\"></sup>Your branches spread as far as the sea;they reached as far as Jazer.The destroyer has fallenon your ripened fruit and grapes.",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>Joy and gladness are gonefrom the orchards and fields of Moab.I have stopped the flow of wine<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20114BT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BT&quot;&gt;BT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20114BT\"></sup> from the presses;no one treads them with shouts of joy.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20114BU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BU&quot;&gt;BU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20114BU\"></sup>Although there are shouts,they are not shouts of joy.",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>“The sound of their cry risesfrom Heshbon<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20115BV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BV&quot;&gt;BV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20115BV\"></sup> to Elealeh<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20115BW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BW&quot;&gt;BW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20115BW\"></sup> and Jahaz,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20115BX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BX&quot;&gt;BX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20115BX\"></sup>from Zoar<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20115BY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BY&quot;&gt;BY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20115BY\"></sup> as far as Horonaim<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20115BZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BZ&quot;&gt;BZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20115BZ\"></sup> and Eglath Shelishiyah,for even the waters of Nimrim are dried up.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20115CA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CA&quot;&gt;CA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20115CA\"></sup>",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup>In Moab I will put an endto those who make offerings on the high places<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20116CB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CB&quot;&gt;CB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20116CB\"></sup>and burn incense<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20116CC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CC&quot;&gt;CC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20116CC\"></sup> to their gods,”declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"36": "<sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup>“So my heart laments<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20117CD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CD&quot;&gt;CD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20117CD\"></sup> for Moab like the music of a pipe;it laments like a pipe for the people of Kir Hareseth.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20117CE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CE&quot;&gt;CE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20117CE\"></sup>The wealth they acquired<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20117CF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CF&quot;&gt;CF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20117CF\"></sup> is gone.",
			"37": "<sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup>Every head is shaved<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20118CG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CG&quot;&gt;CG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20118CG\"></sup>and every beard<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20118CH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CH&quot;&gt;CH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20118CH\"></sup> cut off;every hand is slashedand every waist is covered with sackcloth.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20118CI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CI&quot;&gt;CI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20118CI\"></sup>",
			"38": "<sup class=\"versenum\">38 </sup>On all the roofs in Moaband in the public squares<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20119CJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CJ&quot;&gt;CJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20119CJ\"></sup>there is nothing but mourning,for I have broken Moablike a jar<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20119CK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CK&quot;&gt;CK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20119CK\"></sup> that no one wants,”declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"39": "<sup class=\"versenum\">39 </sup>“How shattered<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20120CL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CL&quot;&gt;CL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20120CL\"></sup> she is! How they wail!How Moab turns her back in shame!Moab has become an object of ridicule,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20120CM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CM&quot;&gt;CM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20120CM\"></sup>an object of horror to all those around her.”",
			"40": "<sup class=\"versenum\">40 </sup>This is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says:“Look! An eagle is swooping<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20121CN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CN&quot;&gt;CN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20121CN\"></sup> down,spreading its wings<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20121CO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CO&quot;&gt;CO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20121CO\"></sup> over Moab.",
			"41": "<sup class=\"versenum\">41 </sup>Kerioth<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20122CP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CP&quot;&gt;CP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20122CP\"></sup> will be capturedand the strongholds taken.In that day the hearts of Moab’s warriors<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20122CQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CQ&quot;&gt;CQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20122CQ\"></sup>will be like the heart of a woman in labor.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20122CR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CR&quot;&gt;CR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20122CR\"></sup>",
			"42": "<sup class=\"versenum\">42 </sup>Moab will be destroyed<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20123CS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CS&quot;&gt;CS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20123CS\"></sup> as a nation<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20123CT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CT&quot;&gt;CT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20123CT\"></sup>because she defied<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20123CU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CU&quot;&gt;CU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20123CU\"></sup> the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"43": "<sup class=\"versenum\">43 </sup>Terror<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20124CV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CV&quot;&gt;CV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20124CV\"></sup> and pit and snare<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20124CW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CW&quot;&gt;CW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20124CW\"></sup> await you,you people of Moab,”declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"44": "<sup class=\"versenum\">44 </sup>“Whoever flees<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20125CX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CX&quot;&gt;CX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20125CX\"></sup> from the terrorwill fall into a pit,whoever climbs out of the pitwill be caught in a snare;for I will bring on Moabthe year<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20125CY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CY&quot;&gt;CY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20125CY\"></sup> of her punishment,”declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"45": "<sup class=\"versenum\">45 </sup>“In the shadow of Heshbonthe fugitives stand helpless,for a fire has gone out from Heshbon,a blaze from the midst of Sihon;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20126CZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CZ&quot;&gt;CZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20126CZ\"></sup>it burns the foreheads of Moab,the skulls<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20126DA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DA&quot;&gt;DA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20126DA\"></sup> of the noisy boasters.",
			"46": "<sup class=\"versenum\">46 </sup>Woe to you, Moab!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20127DB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DB&quot;&gt;DB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20127DB\"></sup>The people of Chemosh are destroyed;your sons are taken into exileand your daughters into captivity.",
			"47": "<sup class=\"versenum\">47 </sup>“Yet I will restore<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20128DC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DC&quot;&gt;DC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20128DC\"></sup> the fortunes of Moabin days to come,”declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.Here ends the judgment on Moab."
		},
		"49": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">49 </span>Concerning the Ammonites:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20129A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20129A\"></sup>This is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says:“Has Israel no sons?Has Israel no heir?Why then has Molek<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20129B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20129B\"></sup> taken possession of Gad?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20129C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20129C\"></sup>Why do his people live in its towns?",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>But the days are coming,”declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,“when I will sound the battle cry<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20130D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20130D\"></sup>against Rabbah<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20130E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20130E\"></sup> of the Ammonites;it will become a mound of ruins,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20130F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20130F\"></sup>and its surrounding villages will be set on fire.Then Israel will drive outthose who drove her out,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20130G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20130G\"></sup>”says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>“Wail, Heshbon,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20131H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20131H\"></sup> for Ai<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20131I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20131I\"></sup> is destroyed!Cry out, you inhabitants of Rabbah!Put on sackcloth<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20131J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20131J\"></sup> and mourn;rush here and there inside the walls,for Molek<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20131K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20131K\"></sup> will go into exile,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20131L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20131L\"></sup>together with his priests and officials.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Why do you boast of your valleys,boast of your valleys so fruitful?Unfaithful Daughter Ammon,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20132M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20132M\"></sup>you trust in your riches<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20132N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20132N\"></sup> and say,‘Who will attack me?’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20132O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20132O\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>I will bring terror on youfrom all those around you,”declares the Lord, the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty.“Every one of you will be driven away,and no one will gather the fugitives.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20133P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20133P\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>“Yet afterward, I will restore<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20134Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20134Q\"></sup> the fortunes of the Ammonites,”declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Concerning Edom:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20135T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20135T\"></sup>This is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty says:“Is there no longer wisdom in Teman?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20135U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20135U\"></sup>Has counsel perished from the prudent?Has their wisdom decayed?",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Turn and flee, hide in deep caves,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20136V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20136V\"></sup>you who live in Dedan,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20136W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20136W\"></sup>for I will bring disaster on Esauat the time when I punish him.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>If grape pickers came to you,would they not leave a few grapes?If thieves came during the night,would they not steal only as much as they wanted?",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>But I will strip Esau bare;I will uncover his hiding places,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20138X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20138X\"></sup>so that he cannot conceal himself.His armed men are destroyed,also his allies and neighbors,so there is no one<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20138Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20138Y\"></sup> to say,",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>‘Leave your fatherless children;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20139Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20139Z\"></sup> I will keep them alive.Your widows<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20139AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20139AA\"></sup> too can depend on me.’”",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>This is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says: “If those who do not deserve to drink the cup<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20140AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20140AB\"></sup> must drink it, why should you go unpunished?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20140AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20140AC\"></sup> You will not go unpunished, but must drink it.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>I swear<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20141AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20141AD\"></sup> by myself,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, “that Bozrah<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20141AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20141AE\"></sup> will become a ruin and a curse, an object of horror<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20141AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20141AF\"></sup> and reproach;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20141AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20141AG\"></sup> and all its towns will be in ruins forever.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20141AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20141AH\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>I have heard a message from the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>;an envoy was sent to the nations to say,“Assemble yourselves to attack it!Rise up for battle!”",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>“Now I will make you small among the nations,despised by mankind.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>The terror you inspireand the pride<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20144AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20144AI\"></sup> of your heart have deceived you,you who live in the clefts of the rocks,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20144AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20144AJ\"></sup>who occupy the heights of the hill.Though you build your nest<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20144AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20144AK\"></sup> as high as the eagle’s,from there I will bring you down,”declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>“Edom will become an object of horror;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20145AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20145AL\"></sup>all who pass by will be appalled and will scoffbecause of all its wounds.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20145AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20145AM\"></sup>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>As Sodom<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20146AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20146AN\"></sup> and Gomorrah<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20146AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20146AO\"></sup> were overthrown,along with their neighboring towns,”says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,“so no one will live there;no people will dwell<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20146AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20146AP\"></sup> in it.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>“Like a lion<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20147AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20147AQ\"></sup> coming up from Jordan’s thickets<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20147AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20147AR\"></sup>to a rich pastureland,I will chase Edom from its land in an instant.Who is the chosen one I will appoint for this?Who is like<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20147AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20147AS\"></sup> me and who can challenge me?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20147AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20147AT\"></sup>And what shepherd<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20147AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20147AU\"></sup> can stand against me?”",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Therefore, hear what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has planned against Edom,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20148AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20148AV\"></sup>what he has purposed<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20148AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20148AW\"></sup> against those who live in Teman:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20148AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20148AX\"></sup>The young of the flock<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20148AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20148AY\"></sup> will be dragged away;their pasture will be appalled at their fate.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20148AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20148AZ\"></sup>",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>At the sound of their fall the earth will tremble;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20149BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20149BA\"></sup>their cry<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20149BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20149BB\"></sup> will resound to the Red Sea.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Look! An eagle will soar and swoop<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20150BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20150BC\"></sup> down,spreading its wings over Bozrah.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20150BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20150BD\"></sup>In that day the hearts of Edom’s warriors<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20150BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20150BE\"></sup>will be like the heart of a woman in labor.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20150BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20150BF\"></sup>",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>Concerning Damascus:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20151BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20151BG\"></sup>“Hamath<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20151BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20151BH\"></sup> and Arpad<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20151BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20151BI\"></sup> are dismayed,for they have heard bad news.They are disheartened,troubled like the restless sea.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20151BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20151BJ\"></sup>",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>Damascus has become feeble,she has turned to fleeand panic has gripped her;anguish and pain have seized her,pain like that of a woman in labor.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20152BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20152BK\"></sup>",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>Why has the city of renown not been abandoned,the town in which I delight?",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>Surely, her young men<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20154BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20154BL\"></sup> will fall in the streets;all her soldiers will be silenced<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20154BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20154BM\"></sup> in that day,”declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>“I will set fire<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20155BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20155BN\"></sup> to the walls of Damascus;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20155BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20155BO\"></sup>it will consume<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20155BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20155BP\"></sup> the fortresses of Ben-Hadad.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20155BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20155BQ\"></sup>”",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>Concerning Kedar<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20156BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20156BR\"></sup> and the kingdoms of Hazor,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20156BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20156BS\"></sup> which Nebuchadnezzar<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20156BT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BT&quot;&gt;BT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20156BT\"></sup> king of Babylon attacked:This is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says:“Arise, and attack Kedarand destroy the people of the East.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20156BU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BU&quot;&gt;BU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20156BU\"></sup>",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>Their tents and their flocks<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20157BV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BV&quot;&gt;BV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20157BV\"></sup> will be taken;their shelters will be carried offwith all their goods and camels.People will shout to them,‘Terror<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20157BW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BW&quot;&gt;BW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20157BW\"></sup> on every side!’",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>“Flee quickly away!Stay in deep caves,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20158BX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BX&quot;&gt;BX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20158BX\"></sup> you who live in Hazor,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20158BY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BY&quot;&gt;BY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20158BY\"></sup>”declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.“Nebuchadnezzar<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20158BZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BZ&quot;&gt;BZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20158BZ\"></sup> king of Babylon has plotted against you;he has devised a plan against you.",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>“Arise and attack a nation at ease,which lives in confidence,”declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,“a nation that has neither gates nor bars;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20159CA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CA&quot;&gt;CA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20159CA\"></sup>its people live far from danger.",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>Their camels<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20160CB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CB&quot;&gt;CB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20160CB\"></sup> will become plunder,and their large herds<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20160CC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CC&quot;&gt;CC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20160CC\"></sup> will be spoils of war.I will scatter to the winds<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20160CD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CD&quot;&gt;CD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20160CD\"></sup> those who are in distant places<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20160CE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CE&quot;&gt;CE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20160CE\"></sup>and will bring disaster on them from every side,”declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>“Hazor<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20161CF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CF&quot;&gt;CF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20161CF\"></sup> will become a haunt of jackals,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20161CG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CG&quot;&gt;CG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20161CG\"></sup>a desolate<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20161CH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CH&quot;&gt;CH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20161CH\"></sup> place forever.No one will live there;no people will dwell<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20161CI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CI&quot;&gt;CI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20161CI\"></sup> in it.”",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>This is the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> that came to Jeremiah the prophet concerning Elam,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20162CJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CJ&quot;&gt;CJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20162CJ\"></sup> early in the reign of Zedekiah<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20162CK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CK&quot;&gt;CK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20162CK\"></sup> king of Judah:",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup>This is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty says:“See, I will break the bow<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20163CL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CL&quot;&gt;CL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20163CL\"></sup> of Elam,the mainstay of their might.",
			"36": "<sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup>I will bring against Elam the four winds<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20164CM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CM&quot;&gt;CM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20164CM\"></sup>from the four quarters of heaven;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20164CN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CN&quot;&gt;CN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20164CN\"></sup>I will scatter them to the four winds,and there will not be a nationwhere Elam’s exiles do not go.",
			"37": "<sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup>I will shatter Elam before their foes,before those who want to kill them;I will bring disaster on them,even my fierce anger,”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20165CO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CO&quot;&gt;CO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20165CO\"></sup>declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.“I will pursue them with the sword<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20165CP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CP&quot;&gt;CP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20165CP\"></sup>until I have made an end of them.",
			"38": "<sup class=\"versenum\">38 </sup>I will set my throne in Elamand destroy her king and officials,”declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"39": "<sup class=\"versenum\">39 </sup>“Yet I will restore<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20167CQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CQ&quot;&gt;CQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20167CQ\"></sup> the fortunes of Elamin days to come,”declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>."
		},
		"50": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">50 </span>This is the word the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> spoke through Jeremiah the prophet concerning Babylon<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20168B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20168B\"></sup> and the land of the Babylonians:",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“Announce and proclaim<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20169C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20169C\"></sup> among the nations,lift up a banner<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20169D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20169D\"></sup> and proclaim it;keep nothing back, but say,‘Babylon will be captured;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20169E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20169E\"></sup>Bel<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20169F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20169F\"></sup> will be put to shame,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20169G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20169G\"></sup>Marduk<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20169H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20169H\"></sup> filled with terror.Her images will be put to shameand her idols<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20169I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20169I\"></sup> filled with terror.’",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>A nation from the north<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20170J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20170J\"></sup> will attack herand lay waste her land.No one will live<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20170K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20170K\"></sup> in it;both people and animals<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20170L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20170L\"></sup> will flee away.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>“In those days, at that time,”declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,“the people of Israel and the people of Judah together<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20171M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20171M\"></sup>will go in tears<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20171N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20171N\"></sup> to seek<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20171O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20171O\"></sup> the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> their God.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>They will ask the way<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20172P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20172P\"></sup> to Zionand turn their faces toward it.They will come<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20172Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20172Q\"></sup> and bind themselves to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>in an everlasting covenant<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20172R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20172R\"></sup>that will not be forgotten.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>“My people have been lost sheep;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20173S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20173S\"></sup>their shepherds<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20173T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20173T\"></sup> have led them astray<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20173U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20173U\"></sup>and caused them to roam on the mountains.They wandered over mountain and hill<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20173V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20173V\"></sup>and forgot their own resting place.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20173W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20173W\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Whoever found them devoured<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20174X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20174X\"></sup> them;their enemies said, ‘We are not guilty,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20174Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20174Y\"></sup>for they sinned against the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, their verdant pasture,the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, the hope<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20174Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20174Z\"></sup> of their ancestors.’",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>“Flee<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20175AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20175AA\"></sup> out of Babylon;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20175AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20175AB\"></sup>leave the land of the Babylonians,and be like the goats that lead the flock.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>For I will stir<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20176AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20176AC\"></sup> up and bring against Babylonan alliance of great nations<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20176AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20176AD\"></sup> from the land of the north.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20176AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20176AE\"></sup>They will take up their positions against her,and from the north she will be captured.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20176AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20176AF\"></sup>Their arrows<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20176AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20176AG\"></sup> will be like skilled warriorswho do not return empty-handed.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>So Babylonia will be plundered;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20177AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20177AH\"></sup>all who plunder her will have their fill,”declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>“Because you rejoice and are glad,you who pillage my inheritance,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20178AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20178AI\"></sup>because you frolic like a heifer<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20178AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20178AJ\"></sup> threshing grainand neigh like stallions,",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>your mother will be greatly ashamed;she who gave you birth will be disgraced.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20179AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20179AK\"></sup>She will be the least of the nations—a wilderness, a dry land, a desert.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20179AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20179AL\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Because of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>’s anger she will not be inhabitedbut will be completely desolate.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20180AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20180AM\"></sup>All who pass Babylon will be appalled;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20180AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20180AN\"></sup>they will scoff<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20180AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20180AO\"></sup> because of all her wounds.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20180AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20180AP\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>“Take up your positions around Babylon,all you who draw the bow.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20181AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20181AQ\"></sup>Shoot at her! Spare no arrows,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20181AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20181AR\"></sup>for she has sinned against the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Shout<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20182AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20182AS\"></sup> against her on every side!She surrenders, her towers fall,her walls<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20182AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20182AT\"></sup> are torn down.Since this is the vengeance<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20182AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20182AU\"></sup> of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,take vengeance on her;do to her<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20182AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20182AV\"></sup> as she has done to others.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20182AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20182AW\"></sup>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Cut off from Babylon the sower,and the reaper with his sickle at harvest.Because of the sword<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20183AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20183AX\"></sup> of the oppressorlet everyone return to their own people,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20183AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20183AY\"></sup>let everyone flee to their own land.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20183AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20183AZ\"></sup>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>“Israel is a scattered flock<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20184BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20184BA\"></sup>that lions<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20184BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20184BB\"></sup> have chased away.The first to devour<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20184BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20184BC\"></sup> themwas the king<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20184BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20184BD\"></sup> of Assyria;the last to crush their bones<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20184BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20184BE\"></sup>was Nebuchadnezzar<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20184BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20184BF\"></sup> king<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20184BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20184BG\"></sup> of Babylon.”",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Therefore this is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty, the God of Israel, says:“I will punish the king of Babylon and his landas I punished the king<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20185BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20185BH\"></sup> of Assyria.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20185BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20185BI\"></sup>",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>But I will bring<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20186BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20186BJ\"></sup> Israel back to their own pasture,and they will graze on Carmel and Bashan;their appetite will be satisfied<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20186BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20186BK\"></sup>on the hills<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20186BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20186BL\"></sup> of Ephraim and Gilead.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20186BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20186BM\"></sup>",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>In those days, at that time,”declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,“search will be made for Israel’s guilt,but there will be none,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20187BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20187BN\"></sup>and for the sins<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20187BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20187BO\"></sup> of Judah,but none will be found,for I will forgive<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20187BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20187BP\"></sup> the remnant<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20187BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20187BQ\"></sup> I spare.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>“Attack the land of Merathaimand those who live in Pekod.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20188BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20188BR\"></sup>Pursue, kill and completely destroy them,”declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.“Do everything I have commanded you.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>The noise<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20189BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20189BS\"></sup> of battle is in the land,the noise of great destruction!",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>How broken and shatteredis the hammer<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20190BT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BT&quot;&gt;BT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20190BT\"></sup> of the whole earth!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20190BU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BU&quot;&gt;BU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20190BU\"></sup>How desolate<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20190BV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BV&quot;&gt;BV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20190BV\"></sup> is Babylonamong the nations!",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>I set a trap<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20191BW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BW&quot;&gt;BW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20191BW\"></sup> for you, Babylon,and you were caught before you knew it;you were found and captured<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20191BX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BX&quot;&gt;BX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20191BX\"></sup>because you opposed<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20191BY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BY&quot;&gt;BY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20191BY\"></sup> the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has opened his arsenaland brought out the weapons<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20192BZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BZ&quot;&gt;BZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20192BZ\"></sup> of his wrath,for the Sovereign <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty has work to doin the land of the Babylonians.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20192CA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CA&quot;&gt;CA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20192CA\"></sup>",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>Come against her from afar.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20193CB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CB&quot;&gt;CB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20193CB\"></sup>Break open her granaries;pile her up like heaps of grain.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20193CC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CC&quot;&gt;CC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20193CC\"></sup>Completely destroy<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20193CD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CD&quot;&gt;CD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20193CD\"></sup> herand leave her no remnant.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>Kill all her young bulls;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20194CE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CE&quot;&gt;CE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20194CE\"></sup>let them go down to the slaughter!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20194CF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CF&quot;&gt;CF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20194CF\"></sup>Woe to them! For their day<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20194CG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CG&quot;&gt;CG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20194CG\"></sup> has come,the time<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20194CH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CH&quot;&gt;CH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20194CH\"></sup> for them to be punished.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>Listen to the fugitives<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20195CI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CI&quot;&gt;CI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20195CI\"></sup> and refugees from Babylondeclaring in Zion<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20195CJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CJ&quot;&gt;CJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20195CJ\"></sup>how the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> our God has taken vengeance,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20195CK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CK&quot;&gt;CK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20195CK\"></sup>vengeance for his temple.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20195CL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CL&quot;&gt;CL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20195CL\"></sup>",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>“Summon archers against Babylon,all those who draw the bow.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20196CM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CM&quot;&gt;CM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20196CM\"></sup>Encamp all around her;let no one escape.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20196CN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CN&quot;&gt;CN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20196CN\"></sup>Repay<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20196CO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CO&quot;&gt;CO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20196CO\"></sup> her for her deeds;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20196CP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CP&quot;&gt;CP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20196CP\"></sup>do to her as she has done.For she has defied<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20196CQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CQ&quot;&gt;CQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20196CQ\"></sup> the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,the Holy One<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20196CR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CR&quot;&gt;CR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20196CR\"></sup> of Israel.",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>Therefore, her young men<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20197CS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CS&quot;&gt;CS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20197CS\"></sup> will fall in the streets;all her soldiers will be silenced in that day,”declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>“See, I am against<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20198CT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CT&quot;&gt;CT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20198CT\"></sup> you, you arrogant one,”declares the Lord, the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty,“for your day<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20198CU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CU&quot;&gt;CU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20198CU\"></sup> has come,the time for you to be punished.",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>The arrogant<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20199CV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CV&quot;&gt;CV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20199CV\"></sup> one will stumble and fall<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20199CW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CW&quot;&gt;CW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20199CW\"></sup>and no one will help her up;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20199CX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CX&quot;&gt;CX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20199CX\"></sup>I will kindle a fire<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20199CY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CY&quot;&gt;CY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20199CY\"></sup> in her townsthat will consume all who are around her.”",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>This is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty says:“The people of Israel are oppressed,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20200CZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CZ&quot;&gt;CZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20200CZ\"></sup>and the people of Judah as well.All their captors hold them fast,refusing to let them go.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20200DA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DA&quot;&gt;DA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20200DA\"></sup>",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>Yet their Redeemer<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20201DB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DB&quot;&gt;DB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20201DB\"></sup> is strong;the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20201DC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DC&quot;&gt;DC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20201DC\"></sup> is his name.He will vigorously defend their cause<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20201DD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DD&quot;&gt;DD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20201DD\"></sup>so that he may bring rest<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20201DE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DE&quot;&gt;DE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20201DE\"></sup> to their land,but unrest to those who live in Babylon.",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup>“A sword<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20202DF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DF&quot;&gt;DF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20202DF\"></sup> against the Babylonians!”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20202DG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DG&quot;&gt;DG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20202DG\"></sup>declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>—“against those who live in Babylonand against her officials and wise<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20202DH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DH&quot;&gt;DH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20202DH\"></sup> men!",
			"36": "<sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup>A sword against her false prophets!They will become fools.A sword against her warriors!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20203DI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DI&quot;&gt;DI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20203DI\"></sup>They will be filled with terror.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20203DJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DJ&quot;&gt;DJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20203DJ\"></sup>",
			"37": "<sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup>A sword against her horses and chariots<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20204DK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DK&quot;&gt;DK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20204DK\"></sup>and all the foreigners in her ranks!They will become weaklings.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20204DL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DL&quot;&gt;DL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20204DL\"></sup>A sword against her treasures!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20204DM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DM&quot;&gt;DM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20204DM\"></sup>They will be plundered.",
			"38": "<sup class=\"versenum\">38 </sup>A drought on her waters!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20205DN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DN&quot;&gt;DN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20205DN\"></sup>They will dry<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20205DO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DO&quot;&gt;DO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20205DO\"></sup> up.For it is a land of idols,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20205DP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DP&quot;&gt;DP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20205DP\"></sup>idols that will go mad with terror.",
			"39": "<sup class=\"versenum\">39 </sup>“So desert creatures<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20206DQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DQ&quot;&gt;DQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20206DQ\"></sup> and hyenas will live there,and there the owl will dwell.It will never again be inhabitedor lived in from generation to generation.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20206DR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DR&quot;&gt;DR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20206DR\"></sup>",
			"40": "<sup class=\"versenum\">40 </sup>As I overthrew Sodom and Gomorrah<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20207DS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DS&quot;&gt;DS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20207DS\"></sup>along with their neighboring towns,”declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,“so no one will live there;no people will dwell in it.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20207DT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DT&quot;&gt;DT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20207DT\"></sup>",
			"41": "<sup class=\"versenum\">41 </sup>“Look! An army is coming from the north;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20208DU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DU&quot;&gt;DU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20208DU\"></sup>a great nation and many kingsare being stirred<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20208DV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DV&quot;&gt;DV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20208DV\"></sup> up from the ends of the earth.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20208DW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DW&quot;&gt;DW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20208DW\"></sup>",
			"42": "<sup class=\"versenum\">42 </sup>They are armed with bows<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20209DX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DX&quot;&gt;DX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20209DX\"></sup> and spears;they are cruel<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20209DY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DY&quot;&gt;DY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20209DY\"></sup> and without mercy.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20209DZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DZ&quot;&gt;DZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20209DZ\"></sup>They sound like the roaring sea<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20209EA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference EA&quot;&gt;EA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20209EA\"></sup>as they ride on their horses;they come like men in battle formationto attack you, Daughter Babylon.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20209EB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference EB&quot;&gt;EB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20209EB\"></sup>",
			"43": "<sup class=\"versenum\">43 </sup>The king of Babylon has heard reports about them,and his hands hang limp.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20210EC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference EC&quot;&gt;EC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20210EC\"></sup>Anguish has gripped him,pain like that of a woman in labor.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20210ED&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference ED&quot;&gt;ED&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20210ED\"></sup>",
			"44": "<sup class=\"versenum\">44 </sup>Like a lion coming up from Jordan’s thickets<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20211EE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference EE&quot;&gt;EE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20211EE\"></sup>to a rich pastureland,I will chase Babylon from its land in an instant.Who is the chosen<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20211EF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference EF&quot;&gt;EF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20211EF\"></sup> one I will appoint for this?Who is like me and who can challenge me?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20211EG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference EG&quot;&gt;EG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20211EG\"></sup>And what shepherd can stand against me?”",
			"45": "<sup class=\"versenum\">45 </sup>Therefore, hear what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has planned against Babylon,what he has purposed<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20212EH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference EH&quot;&gt;EH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20212EH\"></sup> against the land of the Babylonians:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20212EI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference EI&quot;&gt;EI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20212EI\"></sup>The young of the flock will be dragged away;their pasture will be appalled at their fate.",
			"46": "<sup class=\"versenum\">46 </sup>At the sound of Babylon’s capture the earth will tremble;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20213EJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference EJ&quot;&gt;EJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20213EJ\"></sup>its cry<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20213EK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference EK&quot;&gt;EK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20213EK\"></sup> will resound among the nations."
		},
		"51": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">51 </span>This is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says:“See, I will stir<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20214A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20214A\"></sup> up the spirit of a destroyeragainst Babylon<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20214B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20214B\"></sup> and the people of Leb Kamai.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>I will send foreigners<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20215C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20215C\"></sup> to Babylonto winnow<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20215D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20215D\"></sup> her and to devastate her land;they will oppose her on every sidein the day<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20215E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20215E\"></sup> of her disaster.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Let not the archer string his bow,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20216F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20216F\"></sup>nor let him put on his armor.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20216G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20216G\"></sup>Do not spare her young men;completely destroy her army.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>They will fall<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20217H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20217H\"></sup> down slain in Babylon,fatally wounded in her streets.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20217I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20217I\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>For Israel and Judah have not been forsaken<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20218J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20218J\"></sup>by their God, the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty,though their land is full of guilt<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20218K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20218K\"></sup>before the Holy One of Israel.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>“Flee<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20219L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20219L\"></sup> from Babylon!Run for your lives!Do not be destroyed because of her sins.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20219M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20219M\"></sup>It is time<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20219N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20219N\"></sup> for the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>’s vengeance;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20219O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20219O\"></sup>he will repay<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20219P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20219P\"></sup> her what she deserves.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Babylon was a gold cup<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20220Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20220Q\"></sup> in the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>’s hand;she made the whole earth drunk.The nations drank her wine;therefore they have now gone mad.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Babylon will suddenly fall<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20221R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20221R\"></sup> and be broken.Wail over her!Get balm<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20221S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20221S\"></sup> for her pain;perhaps she can be healed.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>“‘We would have healed Babylon,but she cannot be healed;let us leave<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20222T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20222T\"></sup> her and each go to our own land,for her judgment<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20222U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20222U\"></sup> reaches to the skies,it rises as high as the heavens.’",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>“‘The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has vindicated<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20223V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20223V\"></sup> us;come, let us tell in Zionwhat the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> our God has done.’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20223W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20223W\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>“Sharpen the arrows,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20224X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20224X\"></sup>take up the shields!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20224Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20224Y\"></sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has stirred up the kings<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20224Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20224Z\"></sup> of the Medes,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20224AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20224AA\"></sup>because his purpose<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20224AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20224AB\"></sup> is to destroy Babylon.The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will take vengeance,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20224AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20224AC\"></sup>vengeance for his temple.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20224AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20224AD\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Lift up a banner<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20225AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20225AE\"></sup> against the walls of Babylon!Reinforce the guard,station the watchmen,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20225AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20225AF\"></sup>prepare an ambush!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20225AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20225AG\"></sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will carry out his purpose,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20225AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20225AH\"></sup>his decree against the people of Babylon.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>You who live by many waters<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20226AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20226AI\"></sup>and are rich in treasures,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20226AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20226AJ\"></sup>your end has come,the time for you to be destroyed.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20226AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20226AK\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty has sworn by himself:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20227AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20227AL\"></sup>I will surely fill you with troops, as with a swarm of locusts,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20227AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20227AM\"></sup>and they will shout<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20227AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20227AN\"></sup> in triumph over you.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>“He made the earth by his power;he founded the world by his wisdom<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20228AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20228AO\"></sup>and stretched<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20228AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20228AP\"></sup> out the heavens by his understanding.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20228AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20228AQ\"></sup>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>When he thunders,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20229AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20229AR\"></sup> the waters in the heavens roar;he makes clouds rise from the ends of the earth.He sends lightning with the rain<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20229AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20229AS\"></sup>and brings out the wind from his storehouses.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20229AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20229AT\"></sup>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>“Everyone is senseless and without knowledge;every goldsmith is shamed by his idols.The images he makes are a fraud;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20230AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20230AU\"></sup>they have no breath in them.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>They are worthless,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20231AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20231AV\"></sup> the objects of mockery;when their judgment comes, they will perish.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>He who is the Portion<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20232AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20232AW\"></sup> of Jacob is not like these,for he is the Maker of all things,including the people of his inheritance<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20232AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20232AX\"></sup>—the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty is his name.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>“You are my war club,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20233AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20233AY\"></sup>my weapon for battle—with you I shatter<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20233AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20233AZ\"></sup> nations,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20233BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20233BA\"></sup>with you I destroy kingdoms,",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>with you I shatter horse and rider,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20234BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20234BB\"></sup>with you I shatter chariot<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20234BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20234BC\"></sup> and driver,",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>with you I shatter man and woman,with you I shatter old man and youth,with you I shatter young man and young woman,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20235BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20235BD\"></sup>",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>with you I shatter shepherd and flock,with you I shatter farmer and oxen,with you I shatter governors and officials.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20236BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20236BE\"></sup>",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>“Before your eyes I will repay<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20237BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20237BF\"></sup> Babylon<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20237BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20237BG\"></sup> and all who live in Babylonia for all the wrong they have done in Zion,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>“I am against<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20238BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20238BH\"></sup> you, you destroying mountain,you who destroy the whole earth,”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20238BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20238BI\"></sup>declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.“I will stretch out my hand<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20238BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20238BJ\"></sup> against you,roll you off the cliffs,and make you a burned-out mountain.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20238BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20238BK\"></sup>",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>No rock will be taken from you for a cornerstone,nor any stone for a foundation,for you will be desolate<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20239BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20239BL\"></sup> forever,”declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>“Lift up a banner<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20240BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20240BM\"></sup> in the land!Blow the trumpet among the nations!Prepare the nations for battle against her;summon against her these kingdoms:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20240BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20240BN\"></sup>Ararat,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20240BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20240BO\"></sup> Minni and Ashkenaz.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20240BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20240BP\"></sup>Appoint a commander against her;send up horses like a swarm of locusts.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20240BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20240BQ\"></sup>",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>Prepare the nations for battle against her—the kings of the Medes,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20241BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20241BR\"></sup>their governors and all their officials,and all the countries they rule.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20241BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20241BS\"></sup>",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>The land trembles<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20242BT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BT&quot;&gt;BT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20242BT\"></sup> and writhes,for the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>’s purposes<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20242BU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BU&quot;&gt;BU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20242BU\"></sup> against Babylon stand—to lay waste<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20242BV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BV&quot;&gt;BV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20242BV\"></sup> the land of Babylonso that no one will live there.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20242BW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BW&quot;&gt;BW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20242BW\"></sup>",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>Babylon’s warriors<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20243BX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BX&quot;&gt;BX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20243BX\"></sup> have stopped fighting;they remain in their strongholds.Their strength is exhausted;they have become weaklings.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20243BY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BY&quot;&gt;BY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20243BY\"></sup>Her dwellings are set on fire;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20243BZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BZ&quot;&gt;BZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20243BZ\"></sup>the bars<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20243CA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CA&quot;&gt;CA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20243CA\"></sup> of her gates are broken.",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>One courier<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20244CB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CB&quot;&gt;CB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20244CB\"></sup> follows anotherand messenger follows messengerto announce to the king of Babylonthat his entire city is captured,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20244CC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CC&quot;&gt;CC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20244CC\"></sup>",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>the river crossings seized,the marshes set on fire,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20245CD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CD&quot;&gt;CD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20245CD\"></sup>and the soldiers terrified.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20245CE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CE&quot;&gt;CE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20245CE\"></sup>”",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>This is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty, the God of Israel, says:“Daughter Babylon<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20246CF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CF&quot;&gt;CF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20246CF\"></sup> is like a threshing floor<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20246CG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CG&quot;&gt;CG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20246CG\"></sup>at the time it is trampled;the time to harvest<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20246CH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CH&quot;&gt;CH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20246CH\"></sup> her will soon come.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20246CI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CI&quot;&gt;CI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20246CI\"></sup>”",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>“Nebuchadnezzar<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20247CJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CJ&quot;&gt;CJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20247CJ\"></sup> king of Babylon has devoured<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20247CK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CK&quot;&gt;CK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20247CK\"></sup> us,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20247CL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CL&quot;&gt;CL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20247CL\"></sup>he has thrown us into confusion,he has made us an empty jar.Like a serpent he has swallowed usand filled his stomach with our delicacies,and then has spewed<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20247CM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CM&quot;&gt;CM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20247CM\"></sup> us out.",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup>May the violence<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20248CN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CN&quot;&gt;CN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20248CN\"></sup> done to our flesh be on Babylon,”say the inhabitants of Zion.“May our blood be on those who live in Babylonia,”says Jerusalem.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20248CO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CO&quot;&gt;CO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20248CO\"></sup>",
			"36": "<sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup>Therefore this is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says:“See, I will defend your cause<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20249CP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CP&quot;&gt;CP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20249CP\"></sup>and avenge<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20249CQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CQ&quot;&gt;CQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20249CQ\"></sup> you;I will dry up<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20249CR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CR&quot;&gt;CR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20249CR\"></sup> her seaand make her springs dry.",
			"37": "<sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup>Babylon will be a heap of ruins,a haunt<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20250CS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CS&quot;&gt;CS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20250CS\"></sup> of jackals,an object of horror and scorn,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20250CT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CT&quot;&gt;CT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20250CT\"></sup>a place where no one lives.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20250CU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CU&quot;&gt;CU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20250CU\"></sup>",
			"38": "<sup class=\"versenum\">38 </sup>Her people all roar like young lions,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20251CV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CV&quot;&gt;CV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20251CV\"></sup>they growl like lion cubs.",
			"39": "<sup class=\"versenum\">39 </sup>But while they are aroused,I will set out a feast for themand make them drunk,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20252CW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CW&quot;&gt;CW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20252CW\"></sup>so that they shout with laughter—then sleep forever<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20252CX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CX&quot;&gt;CX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20252CX\"></sup> and not awake,”declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20252CY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CY&quot;&gt;CY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20252CY\"></sup>",
			"40": "<sup class=\"versenum\">40 </sup>“I will bring them downlike lambs to the slaughter,like rams and goats.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20253CZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CZ&quot;&gt;CZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20253CZ\"></sup>",
			"41": "<sup class=\"versenum\">41 </sup>“How Sheshak<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20254DA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DA&quot;&gt;DA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20254DA\"></sup> will be captured,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20254DB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DB&quot;&gt;DB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20254DB\"></sup>the boast of the whole earth seized!How desolate<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20254DC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DC&quot;&gt;DC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20254DC\"></sup> Babylon will beamong the nations!",
			"42": "<sup class=\"versenum\">42 </sup>The sea will rise over Babylon;its roaring waves<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20255DD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DD&quot;&gt;DD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20255DD\"></sup> will cover her.",
			"43": "<sup class=\"versenum\">43 </sup>Her towns will be desolate,a dry and desert<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20256DE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DE&quot;&gt;DE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20256DE\"></sup> land,a land where no one lives,through which no one travels.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20256DF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DF&quot;&gt;DF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20256DF\"></sup>",
			"44": "<sup class=\"versenum\">44 </sup>I will punish Bel<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20257DG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DG&quot;&gt;DG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20257DG\"></sup> in Babylonand make him spew out<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20257DH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DH&quot;&gt;DH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20257DH\"></sup> what he has swallowed.The nations will no longer stream to him.And the wall<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20257DI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DI&quot;&gt;DI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20257DI\"></sup> of Babylon will fall.",
			"45": "<sup class=\"versenum\">45 </sup>“Come out<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20258DJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DJ&quot;&gt;DJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20258DJ\"></sup> of her, my people!Run<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20258DK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DK&quot;&gt;DK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20258DK\"></sup> for your lives!Run from the fierce anger<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20258DL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DL&quot;&gt;DL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20258DL\"></sup> of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"46": "<sup class=\"versenum\">46 </sup>Do not lose heart<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20259DM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DM&quot;&gt;DM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20259DM\"></sup> or be afraid<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20259DN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DN&quot;&gt;DN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20259DN\"></sup>when rumors<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20259DO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DO&quot;&gt;DO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20259DO\"></sup> are heard in the land;one rumor comes this year, another the next,rumors of violence in the landand of ruler against ruler.",
			"47": "<sup class=\"versenum\">47 </sup>For the time will surely comewhen I will punish the idols<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20260DP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DP&quot;&gt;DP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20260DP\"></sup> of Babylon;her whole land will be disgraced<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20260DQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DQ&quot;&gt;DQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20260DQ\"></sup>and her slain will all lie fallen within her.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20260DR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DR&quot;&gt;DR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20260DR\"></sup>",
			"48": "<sup class=\"versenum\">48 </sup>Then heaven and earth and all that is in themwill shout<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20261DS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DS&quot;&gt;DS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20261DS\"></sup> for joy over Babylon,for out of the north<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20261DT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DT&quot;&gt;DT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20261DT\"></sup>destroyers<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20261DU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DU&quot;&gt;DU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20261DU\"></sup> will attack her,”declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"49": "<sup class=\"versenum\">49 </sup>“Babylon must fall because of Israel’s slain,just as the slain in all the earthhave fallen because of Babylon.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20262DV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DV&quot;&gt;DV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20262DV\"></sup>",
			"50": "<sup class=\"versenum\">50 </sup>You who have escaped the sword,leave<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20263DW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DW&quot;&gt;DW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20263DW\"></sup> and do not linger!Remember<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20263DX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DX&quot;&gt;DX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20263DX\"></sup> the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> in a distant land,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20263DY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DY&quot;&gt;DY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20263DY\"></sup>and call to mind Jerusalem.”",
			"51": "<sup class=\"versenum\">51 </sup>“We are disgraced,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20264DZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DZ&quot;&gt;DZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20264DZ\"></sup>for we have been insultedand shame covers our faces,because foreigners have enteredthe holy places of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>’s house.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20264EA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference EA&quot;&gt;EA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20264EA\"></sup>",
			"52": "<sup class=\"versenum\">52 </sup>“But days are coming,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,“when I will punish her idols,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20265EB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference EB&quot;&gt;EB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20265EB\"></sup>and throughout her landthe wounded will groan.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20265EC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference EC&quot;&gt;EC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20265EC\"></sup>",
			"53": "<sup class=\"versenum\">53 </sup>Even if Babylon ascends to the heavens<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20266ED&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference ED&quot;&gt;ED&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20266ED\"></sup>and fortifies her lofty stronghold,I will send destroyers<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20266EE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference EE&quot;&gt;EE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20266EE\"></sup> against her,”declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"54": "<sup class=\"versenum\">54 </sup>“The sound of a cry<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20267EF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference EF&quot;&gt;EF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20267EF\"></sup> comes from Babylon,the sound of great destruction<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20267EG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference EG&quot;&gt;EG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20267EG\"></sup>from the land of the Babylonians.",
			"55": "<sup class=\"versenum\">55 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will destroy Babylon;he will silence<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20268EH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference EH&quot;&gt;EH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20268EH\"></sup> her noisy din.Waves<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20268EI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference EI&quot;&gt;EI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20268EI\"></sup> of enemies will rage like great waters;the roar of their voices will resound.",
			"56": "<sup class=\"versenum\">56 </sup>A destroyer<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20269EJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference EJ&quot;&gt;EJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20269EJ\"></sup> will come against Babylon;her warriors will be captured,and their bows will be broken.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20269EK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference EK&quot;&gt;EK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20269EK\"></sup>For the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> is a God of retribution;he will repay<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20269EL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference EL&quot;&gt;EL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20269EL\"></sup> in full.",
			"57": "<sup class=\"versenum\">57 </sup>I will make her officials<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20270EM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference EM&quot;&gt;EM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20270EM\"></sup> and wise<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20270EN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference EN&quot;&gt;EN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20270EN\"></sup> men drunk,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20270EO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference EO&quot;&gt;EO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20270EO\"></sup>her governors, officers and warriors as well;they will sleep<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20270EP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference EP&quot;&gt;EP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20270EP\"></sup> forever and not awake,”declares the King,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20270EQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference EQ&quot;&gt;EQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20270EQ\"></sup> whose name is the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty.",
			"58": "<sup class=\"versenum\">58 </sup>This is what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> Almighty says:“Babylon’s thick wall<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20271ER&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference ER&quot;&gt;ER&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20271ER\"></sup> will be leveledand her high gates<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20271ES&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference ES&quot;&gt;ES&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20271ES\"></sup> set on fire;the peoples<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20271ET&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference ET&quot;&gt;ET&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20271ET\"></sup> exhaust<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20271EU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference EU&quot;&gt;EU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20271EU\"></sup> themselves for nothing,the nations’ labor is only fuel for the flames.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20271EV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference EV&quot;&gt;EV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20271EV\"></sup>",
			"59": "<sup class=\"versenum\">59 </sup>This is the message Jeremiah the prophet gave to the staff officer Seraiah son of Neriah,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20272EW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference EW&quot;&gt;EW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20272EW\"></sup> the son of Mahseiah, when he went to Babylon with Zedekiah<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20272EX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference EX&quot;&gt;EX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20272EX\"></sup> king of Judah in the fourth<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20272EY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference EY&quot;&gt;EY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20272EY\"></sup> year of his reign.",
			"60": "<sup class=\"versenum\">60 </sup>Jeremiah had written on a scroll<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20273EZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference EZ&quot;&gt;EZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20273EZ\"></sup> about all the disasters that would come upon Babylon—all that had been recorded concerning Babylon.",
			"61": "<sup class=\"versenum\">61 </sup>He said to Seraiah, “When you get to Babylon, see that you read all these words aloud.",
			"62": "<sup class=\"versenum\">62 </sup>Then say, ‘<span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, you have said you will destroy this place, so that neither people nor animals will live in it; it will be desolate<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20275FA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference FA&quot;&gt;FA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20275FA\"></sup> forever.’",
			"63": "<sup class=\"versenum\">63 </sup>When you finish reading this scroll, tie a stone to it and throw it into the Euphrates.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20276FB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference FB&quot;&gt;FB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20276FB\"></sup>",
			"64": "<sup class=\"versenum\">64 </sup>Then say, ‘So will Babylon sink to rise no more<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20277FC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference FC&quot;&gt;FC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20277FC\"></sup> because of the disaster I will bring on her. And her people<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20277FD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference FD&quot;&gt;FD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20277FD\"></sup> will fall.’”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20277FE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference FE&quot;&gt;FE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20277FE\"></sup>The words of Jeremiah end<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20277FF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference FF&quot;&gt;FF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20277FF\"></sup> here."
		},
		"52": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">52 </span>Zedekiah<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20278D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20278D\"></sup> was twenty-one years old when he became king, and he reigned in Jerusalem eleven years. His mother’s name was Hamutal daughter of Jeremiah; she was from Libnah.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20278E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20278E\"></sup>",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>He did evil in the eyes of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, just as Jehoiakim<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20279F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20279F\"></sup> had done.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>It was because of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>’s anger that all this happened to Jerusalem and Judah,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20280G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20280G\"></sup> and in the end he thrust them from his presence.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20280H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20280H\"></sup>Now Zedekiah rebelled<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20280I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20280I\"></sup> against the king of Babylon.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>So in the ninth year of Zedekiah’s reign, on the tenth<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20281J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20281J\"></sup> day of the tenth month, Nebuchadnezzar king of Babylon marched against Jerusalem<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20281K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20281K\"></sup> with his whole army. They encamped outside the city and built siege works<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20281L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20281L\"></sup> all around it.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20281M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20281M\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>The city was kept under siege until the eleventh year of King Zedekiah.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>By the ninth day of the fourth month the famine in the city had become so severe that there was no food for the people to eat.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20283N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20283N\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Then the city wall was broken through, and the whole army fled.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20284O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20284O\"></sup> They left the city at night through the gate between the two walls near the king’s garden, though the Babylonians were surrounding the city. They fled toward the Arabah,",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>but the Babylonian army pursued King Zedekiah and overtook him in the plains of Jericho. All his soldiers were separated from him and scattered,",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>and he was captured.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20286P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20286P\"></sup>He was taken to the king of Babylon at Riblah<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20286Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20286Q\"></sup> in the land of Hamath,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20286R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20286R\"></sup> where he pronounced sentence on him.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>There at Riblah the king of Babylon killed the sons<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20287S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20287S\"></sup> of Zedekiah before his eyes; he also killed all the officials of Judah.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Then he put out Zedekiah’s eyes, bound him with bronze shackles and took him to Babylon, where he put him in prison till the day of his death.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20288T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20288T\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>On the tenth day of the fifth<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20289U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20289U\"></sup> month, in the nineteenth year of Nebuchadnezzar king of Babylon, Nebuzaradan<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20289V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20289V\"></sup> commander of the imperial guard, who served the king of Babylon, came to Jerusalem.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>He set fire<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20290W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20290W\"></sup> to the temple<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20290X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20290X\"></sup> of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, the royal palace and all the houses<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20290Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20290Y\"></sup> of Jerusalem. Every important building he burned down.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>The whole Babylonian army, under the commander of the imperial guard, broke down all the walls<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20291Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20291Z\"></sup> around Jerusalem.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Nebuzaradan the commander of the guard carried into exile<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20292AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20292AA\"></sup> some of the poorest people and those who remained in the city, along with the rest of the craftsmen and those who had deserted<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20292AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20292AB\"></sup> to the king of Babylon.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>But Nebuzaradan left behind<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20293AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20293AC\"></sup> the rest of the poorest people of the land to work the vineyards and fields.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>The Babylonians broke up the bronze pillars,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20294AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20294AD\"></sup> the movable stands<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20294AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20294AE\"></sup> and the bronze Sea<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20294AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20294AF\"></sup> that were at the temple of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> and they carried all the bronze to Babylon.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20294AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20294AG\"></sup>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>They also took away the pots, shovels, wick trimmers, sprinkling bowls,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20295AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20295AH\"></sup> dishes and all the bronze articles used in the temple service.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20295AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20295AI\"></sup>",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>The commander of the imperial guard took away the basins, censers,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20296AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20296AJ\"></sup> sprinkling bowls, pots, lampstands,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20296AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20296AK\"></sup> dishes<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20296AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20296AL\"></sup> and bowls used for drink offerings<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20296AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20296AM\"></sup>—all that were made of pure gold or silver.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20296AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20296AN\"></sup>",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>The bronze from the two pillars, the Sea and the twelve bronze bulls<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20297AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20297AO\"></sup> under it, and the movable stands, which King Solomon had made for the temple of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, was more than could be weighed.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20297AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20297AP\"></sup>",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>Each pillar was eighteen cubits high and twelve cubits in circumference; each was four fingers thick, and hollow.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20298AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20298AQ\"></sup>",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>The bronze capital<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20299AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20299AR\"></sup> on top of one pillar was five cubits high and was decorated with a network and pomegranates<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20299AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20299AS\"></sup> of bronze all around. The other pillar, with its pomegranates, was similar.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>There were ninety-six pomegranates on the sides; the total number of pomegranates<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20300AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20300AT\"></sup> above the surrounding network was a hundred.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20300AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20300AU\"></sup>",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>The commander of the guard took as prisoners Seraiah<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20301AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20301AV\"></sup> the chief priest, Zephaniah<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20301AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20301AW\"></sup> the priest next in rank and the three doorkeepers.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20301AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20301AX\"></sup>",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>Of those still in the city, he took the officer in charge of the fighting men, and seven royal advisers. He also took the secretary<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20302AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20302AY\"></sup> who was chief officer in charge of conscripting the people of the land, sixty of whom were found in the city.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>Nebuzaradan<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20303AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20303AZ\"></sup> the commander took them all and brought them to the king of Babylon at Riblah.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>There at Riblah,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20304BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20304BA\"></sup> in the land of Hamath, the king had them executed.So Judah went into captivity, away<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20304BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20304BB\"></sup> from her land.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>This is the number of the people Nebuchadnezzar carried into exile:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20305BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20305BC\"></sup>in the seventh year, 3,023 Jews;",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>in Nebuchadnezzar’s eighteenth year,832 people from Jerusalem;",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>in his twenty-third year,745 Jews taken into exile<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20307BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20307BD\"></sup> by Nebuzaradan the commander of the imperial guard.There were 4,600 people in all.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20307BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20307BE\"></sup>",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>In the thirty-seventh year of the exile of Jehoiachin<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20308BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20308BG\"></sup> king of Judah, in the year Awel-Marduk became king of Babylon, on the twenty-fifth day of the twelfth month, he released Jehoiachin king of Judah and freed him from prison.",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>He spoke kindly to him and gave him a seat of honor higher than those of the other kings who were with him in Babylon.",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>So Jehoiachin put aside his prison clothes and for the rest of his life ate regularly at the king’s table.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20310BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20310BH\"></sup>",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>Day by day the king of Babylon gave Jehoiachin a regular allowance<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-20311BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-20311BI\"></sup> as long as he lived, till the day of his death."
		}
	}
};
module.exports = book;